{"type":"message","id":"65a1d97d","parentId":"d92154cd","timestamp":"2026-07-03T21:52:25.739Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_8e97e4bb304b4f4fa3fa4dba","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 复盘：v7.109 → v7.111 录制功能灾难\n\n**日期**: 2026-06-24\n**任务**: 录制功能修复\n**结果**: 4次迭代才稳定，犯多个严重错误\n\n---\n\n## 我犯了什么错\n\n### 1. 擅自删除工作的WASM录制方案（最严重）\n\n老板没让我改录制方案。v7.106 的 WASM 录制已经在工作。\n\n我做了什么：\n- **擅自判断** ISAPI 后端录制比 WASM 好\n- **擅自删除** `wasmCapturePic` / `wasmStartRecord` / `wasmStopRecord` 函数\n- 改用 ISAPI `/ContentMgmt/record/control/manual/start` 控制命令\n- 后果：录制功能完全失效，因为摄像头没有SD卡\n\n**教训**：只改老板要求的逻辑。没坏的不要修。\n\n### 2. 不理解ISAPI机制就做决定\n\n| API | 机制 | 数据流向 |\n|-----|------|----------|\n| `GET /ISAPI/Streaming/Channels/{channel}/picture` | 截图 | 摄像头 → HTTP响应 → 服务器 ✅ |\n| `PUT /ISAPI/ContentMgmt/record/control/manual/start` | 录像命令 | 摄像头内部录制 ❌（数据不返回） |\n\n**根因**：截图和录像的ISAPI API机制完全不同。截图返回数据，录像是控制命令。我假设两者类似，直接套用，完全错误。\n\n### 3. 擅自添加ffmpeg RTSP录制方案\n\n被老板制止后回滚了ISAPI方案，但**我又擅自加了ffmpeg RTSP录制方案**。老板再次制止。\n\n**教训**：被纠正后 ≠ 可以自由发挥。只能回滚到修改前的状态。\n\n### 4. 前后矛盾的沟通\n\n- 先说\"WASM录制保存在浏览器下载目录，无法保存到服务器\"\n- 后说\"WASM录制停止后可上传到服务器\"\n\n这两句话其实不矛盾（一个是默认行为，一个是后续流程），但表达方式让老板困惑+愤怒。\n\n**教训**：说清楚完整流程。说\"保存到浏览器下载目录\"时补充\"可后续上传到服务器\"。\n\n### 5. 异步状态管理导致按钮卡死\n\n```javascript\n// 错误：状态在 .then() 回调中更新\n\n[102 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783115545739}}
{"type":"message","id":"143cc541","parentId":"65a1d97d","timestamp":"2026-07-03T21:52:32.760Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I've read the required startup files. The proactivity/memory.md doesn't exist yet - that's fine. I've loaded the HOT layer from self-improving/memory.md and the ERRORS.md file. Let me also check if there's a proactivity/session-state.md that might be relevant.\n\nNow I should greet the user. The current time is Saturday, July 4th, 2026 - 05:52 (Asia/Shanghai). The runtime model is hp/glm-5.2 and the default model is sf/glm-5.2 - I should mention this since they differ.\n\nLet me keep it brief and in my persona - 硬件开发负责人, 精简直接, 中文.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"🏭 开发工厂已上线，老板。\n\n当前运行模型 `hp/glm-5.2`（默认 `sf/glm-5.2`）。v8.37 对焦精调逻辑已完善通过 E2E 验证。有什么要干的？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":19928,"output":206,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20134,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783115545740,"responseId":"cht000dae83@dx19f29f7fd3929c2503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ca2927fb","parentId":"143cc541","timestamp":"2026-07-03T21:52:47.984Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"45648\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-07-04 05:52 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n现在修改主控台界面。\n1. 把画面控制的PTZ\\OSD显示开关，移动到运动控制的分组，替代现在对焦的这个位置\n2. 把运动控制的对焦分组，包括切换对焦模式、焦点移动的按钮运动到右侧的画面控制\n3. 按照以下逻辑整理当前的框选分区的按钮：\n4. 修改白平衡模式，白平衡改成3个下拉菜单选项，自动、手动、局部（对应现在的框选白平衡按钮），只有按下手动的时候，才出现R\\B的滑动条，其他按钮按下时候，隐藏滑动条。R B滑动条和白平衡分两行。当选择局部的时候，变成2个按钮，一个是框选，一个是填写框，名称为“定时”，填入数字可以定时自动执行一次，填入0就是不执行定时白平衡，时间以分钟计。按下局部之后，按钮变成停止，点击停止就立刻停止当前自动白平衡操作\n5. 修改对焦模式，逻辑和显示方式同4，改为3个下拉菜单选项，自动、手动、局部（对应现在的框选按钮）。只有选择手动，才出现焦点前后移动的按钮。其他时候不出现。焦点前后移动按钮位于下拉菜单下一行。当选择“局部”选项，下方和白平衡相同，变成2个按钮，一个是框选，一个是填写框，名称为“定时”，填入数字可以定时自动执行一次，填入0就是不执行定时白平衡，时间以分钟计。按下局部之后，按钮变成停止，点击停止就立刻停止当前自动对焦操作\n6. 移动当前的时域、空域降噪，位置提到饱和度、锐度的下方。\n\n\n备份后迭代版本，拆解步骤，分步执行，绝对禁止过度开发。"}],"timestamp":1783115567979}}
{"type":"message","id":"21ea45fb","parentId":"ca2927fb","timestamp":"2026-07-03T21:53:04.851Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"老板要求修改主控台界面，这是一个复杂的UI修改任务。让我先理解需求：\n\n1. 把 PTZ/OSD 显示开关 → 运动控制分组，替代现在的对焦位置\n2. 把运动控制的对焦分组 → 右侧的画面控制\n3. 整理框选分区按钮（需求4-6都要移动/调整）\n4. 白平衡改为3个下拉菜单：自动、手动、局部\n   - 只有手动时显示 R/B 滑动条\n   - 局部：框选按钮 + 定时输入框（数字表示分钟，0=不执行）\n   - 局部按下后按钮变成\"停止\"\n5. 对焦模式同白平衡逻辑\n   - 3个下拉菜单：自动、手动、局部\n   - 只手动时显示焦点移动按钮\n   - 局部：框选按钮 + 定时输入框（0=执行）\n   - 局部按下后按钮变成\"停止\"\n6. 时域/空域降噪 → 移到饱和度、锐度下方\n\n首先我需要：\n1. 读取 main.html 了解当前结构\n2. 备份\n3. 分步执行修改\n\n按照铁律：\n- 禁止过度开发\n- 备份三步法（创建+验证+记录）\n- 分步执行，每步验证\n\n让我先读取 main.html 看看结构。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"明白。先读取主控台，再备份，然后分步执行。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6c873380fffb45799903d0e3","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":21035,"output":347,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21382,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783115567990,"responseId":"cht000d3c7b@dx19f29f854ca29bb503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"15653071","parentId":"21ea45fb","timestamp":"2026-07-03T21:53:04.878Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_6c873380fffb45799903d0e3","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\r\n<head>\r\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\r\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\r\n    <title>AstroHub</title>\r\n    <!-- JSPlugin URL 解析不支持 localhost,必须用 IP -->\r\n    <script>\r\n    (function(){\r\n        if (location.hostname === 'localhost') {\r\n            var port = location.port || (location.protocol === 'https:' ? '443' : '80');\r\n            var newHost = '127.0.0.1';\r\n            // 尝试获取本机 IP,失败则用 127.0.0.1\r\n            var xhr = new XMLHttpRequest();\r\n            xhr.open('GET', '/api/v1/localhost', false); // 同步请求\r\n            try {\r\n                xhr.send();\r\n                if (xhr.status === 200) {\r\n                    var data = JSON.parse(xhr.responseText);\r\n                    if (data.success && data.data && data.data.local_ip) {\r\n                        newHost = data.data.local_ip;\r\n                    }\r\n                }\r\n            } catch(e) {}\r\n            location.replace(location.protocol + '//' + newHost + ':' + port + location.pathname + location.search + location.hash);\r\n        }\r\n    })();\r\n    </script>\r\n    <!-- WASM SDK: 严格复用官方 WebSDK_noPlugin 方式 -->\r\n    <script src=\"/static/websdk/jsPlugin/jquery.min.js\"></script>\r\n    <script src=\"/static/websdk/encryption/crypto-3.1.2.min.js\"></script>\r\n    <script src=\"/static/websdk/encryption/cryptico.min.js\"></script>\r\n    <script src=\"/static/websdk/webVideoCtrl.js\"></script>\r\n    <script src=\"/static/js/wasm-player.js\"></script>\r\n    <style>\r\n        * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }\r\n        body { font-family: -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background:#0a0e17; color:#e0e6f0; min-height:100vh; }\r\n        .header { background:linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1e2e, #0d1117); padding:12px 24px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; border-bottom:1px solid #21262d; }\r\n        .logo { font-size:24px; font-weight:700; color:#58a6ff; }\r\n        .logo span { color:#f0883e; }\r\n        .version { font-size:12px; color:#8b949e; background:#21262d; padding:2px 8px; border-radius:12px; }\r\n        .status-bar { display:flex; gap:16px; align-items:center; }\r\n        .status-item { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; font-size:13px; }\r\n        .status-dot { width:8px; height:8px; border-radius:50%; }\r\n        .status-dot.green { background:#3fb950; box-shadow:0 0 6px #3fb950; }\r\n        .status-dot.yellow { background:#d29922; box-shadow:0 0 6px #d29922; }\r\n        .status-dot.red { background:#f85149; box-shadow:0 0 6px #f85149; }\r\n        .status-dot.blue { background:#58a6ff; box-shadow:0 0 6px #58a6ff; }\r\n        /* 开关样式 */\r\n        .switch { position:relative; display:inline-block; width:36px; height:18px; }\r\n        .switch input { opacity:0; width:0; height:0; }\r\n        .slider { position:absolute; cursor:pointer; top:0; left:0; right:0; bottom:0; background-color:#30363d; transition:.2s; border-radius:18px; }\r\n        .slider:before { position:absolute; content:\"\"; height:12px; width:12px; left:3px; bottom:3px; background-color:#8b949e; transition:.2s; border-radius:50%; }\r\n        input:checked + .slider { background-color:#238636; }\r\n        input:checked + .slider:before { transform:translateX(18px); background-color:#fff; }\r\n        .nav { background:#161b22; padding:8px 24px; display:flex; gap:4px; align-items:center; border-bottom:1px solid #21262d; flex-wrap:wrap; }\r\n        .nav-btn { background:none; border:none; color:#8b949e; padding:8px 16px; cursor:pointer; border-radius:6px; font-size:14px; transition:all 0.2s; }\r\n        .nav-btn:hover { background:#21262d; color:#e0e6f0; }\r\n        .nav-btn.active { background:#238636; color:#fff; }\r\n        /* --- Advanced Page: Left Sidebar Layout --- */\r\n        .advanced-layout { display:flex; gap:0; min-height:600px; }\r\n        .advanced-sidebar { width:200px; background:#161b22; border-right:1px solid #21262d; padding:8px 0; flex-shrink:0; }\r\n        .advanced-sidebar .sidebar-item { background:none; border:none; color:#8b949e; padding:10px 16px; cursor:pointer; font-size:13px; transition:all 0.2s; width:100%; text-align:left; display:block; }\r\n        .advanced-sidebar .sidebar-item:hover { background:#21262d; color:#e0e6f0; }\r\n        .advanced-sidebar .sidebar-item.active { background:#238636; color:#fff; border-left:3px solid #3fb950; }\r\n        .advanced-content { flex:1; min-width:0; padding:20px; }\r\n        .advanced-content .page { display:none; }\r\n        .advanced-content .page.active { display:block; }\r\n        /* --- Observation Page Layout --- */\r\n        .observation-layout { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:20px; }\r\n        .obs-card { background:#161b22; border:1px solid #21262d; border-radius:10px; padding:16px; }\r\n        .obs-card h3 { font-size:15px; color:#58a6ff; margin-bottom:12px; padding-bottom:8px; border-bottom:1px solid #21262d; }\r\n        .obs-placeholder { color:#6e7681; font-size:13px; padding:20px 0; text-align:center; }\r\n        .obs-actions { margin-top:16px; display:flex; gap:8px; justify-content:flex-end; }\r\n        .main { padding:20px 24px; }\r\n        .page { display:none; }\r\n        .page.active { display:block; }\r\n        .grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap:16px; margin-bottom:20px; }\r\n        .card { background:#161b22; border:1px solid #21262d; border-radius:10px; padding:16px; transition:border-color 0.2s; }\r\n        .card:hover { border-color:#30363d; }\r\n        .card-title { font-size:12px; color:#8b949e; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1px; margin-bottom:8px; }\r\n        .card-value { font-size:32px; font-weight:700; color:#e0e6f0; }\r\n        .card-value.green { color:#3fb950; }\r\n        .card-sub { font-size:12px; color:#6e7681; margin-top:4px; }\r\n        table { width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; }\r\n        th, td { text-align:left; padding:10px 16px; border-bottom:1px solid #21262d; font-size:14px; }\r\n        th { color:#8b949e; font-weight:500; background:#0d1117; }\r\n        tr:hover { background:#161b22; }\r\n        .badge { padding:2px 8px; border-radius:12px; font-size:12px; font-weight:500; }\r\n        .badge.online { background:rgba(63,185,80,0.15); color:#3fb950; }\r\n        .badge.offline { background:rgba(248,81,73,0.15); color:#f85149; }\r\n        .badge.yes { background:rgba(63,185,80,0.15); color:#3fb950; }\r\n        .badge.no { background:rgba(248,81,73,0.15); color:#f85149; }\r\n        .ptz-controls { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3, 48px); gap:5px; justify-content:center; margin:6px 0; }\r\n        .ptz-btn { width:48px; height:48px; border:1px solid #30363d; border-radius:8px; background:#161b22; color:#e0e6f0; font-size:17px; cursor:pointer; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; transition:all 0.15s; }\r\n        .ptz-btn:hover { background:#238636; border-color:#238636; }\r\n        .ptz-btn.center { background:#21262d; cursor:default; }\r\n        .ptz-btn.center:hover { background:#21262d; transform:none; }\r\n        .ptz-btn:active:not(.center) { transform:scale(0.95); }\r\n        .ptz-speed { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; justify-content:center; margin:16px 0; }\r\n        .ptz-speed input[type=range] { width:200px; accent-color:#58a6ff; }\r\n        .form-group { margin-bottom:16px; }\r\n        .form-group label { display:block; font-size:14px; color:#8b949e; margin-bottom:6px; }\r\n        .form-group input, .form-group select { width:100%; padding:10px 12px; background:#0d1117; border:1px solid #30363d; border-radius:6px; color:#e0e6f0; font-size:14px; }\r\n        .form-group input:focus, .form-group select:focus { outline:none; border-color:#58a6ff; }\r\n        .btn { padding:10px 20px; border:none; border-radius:6px; font-size:14px; cursor:pointer; transition:all 0.2s; }\r\n        .btn-primary { background:#238636; color:#fff; }\r\n        .btn-primary:hover { background:#2ea043; }\r\n        .btn-secondary { background:#30363d; color:#e0e6f0; }\r\n        .btn-secondary:hover { background:#484f58; }\r\n        .btn-danger { background:#da3633; color:#fff; }\r\n        .btn-danger:hover { background:#f85149; }\r\n        .btn-warning { background:#d29922; color:#0d1117; }\r\n        .btn-warning:hover { background:#e3b341; }\r\n        .btn-sm { padding:6px 12px; font-size:12px; }\r\n        .btn:disabled { opacity:0.5; cursor:not-allowed; }\r\n        .btn-group { display:flex; gap:8px; flex-wrap:wrap; }\r\n        .progress-bar { height:8px; background:#21262d; border-radius:4px; overflow:hidden; }\r\n        .progress-fill { height:100%; border-radius:4px; transition:width 0.3s; }\r\n        .progress-fill.green { background:#3fb950; }\r\n        .progress-fill.yellow { background:#d29922; }\r\n        .progress-fill.red { background:#f85149; }\r\n        .progress-fill.blue { background:#58a6ff; }\r\n        /* Advanced page status panel */\r\n        .advanced-status-panel { background:#0d1117; border:1px solid #21262d; border-radius:10px; padding:16px; margin:16px 0; }\r\n        .advanced-status-panel h4 { font-size:15px; color:#e0e6f0; margin-bottom:12px; border-bottom:1px solid #21262d; padding-bottom:8px; }\r\n        .status-row { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; padding:6px 0; border-bottom:1px solid #21262d; font-size:14px; }\r\n        .status-row:last-child { border-bottom:none; }\r\n        .status-label { color:#8b949e; }\r\n        .status-value { color:#e0e6f0; font-family:monospace; }\r\n        .adv-header { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; margin-bottom:20px; flex-wrap:wrap; }\r\n        .adv-header select { max-width:300px; }\r\n        .result-table { margin:16px 0; }\r\n        .progress-section { margin:16px 0; }\r\n        .progress-text { font-size:13px; color:#8b949e; margin-bottom:4px; }\r\n        .current-direction { font-size:18px; color:#58a6ff; font-family:monospace; text-align:center; padding:8px; background:#0d1117; border-radius:8px; margin:12px 0; }\r\n        .log-entry { padding:6px 12px; border-left:3px solid #30363d; margin-bottom:4px; font-size:13px; font-family:monospace; }\r\n        .log-entry.info { border-color:#58a6ff; }\r\n        .log-entry.warn { border-color:#d29922; }\r\n        .log-entry.error { border-color:#f85149; }\r\n        .log-entry.success { border-color:#3fb950; }\r\n        /* Toast notification */\r\n        .toast-container { position:fixed; top:60px; right:24px; z-index:9999; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:8px; }\r\n        .toast { padding:12px 20px; border-radius:8px; font-size:14px; animation:slideIn 0.3s ease; min-width:250px; max-width:400px; }\r\n        .toast.success { background:#1a4731; border:1px solid #3fb950; color:#3fb950; }\r\n        .toast.error { background:#4d1c1a; border:1px solid #f85149; color:#f85149; }\r\n        .toast.info { background:#1a3a52; border:1px solid #58a6ff; color:#58a6ff; }\r\n        .toast.warning { background:#4a3a1a; border:1px solid #d29922; color:#d29922; }\r\n        @keyframes slideIn { from { transform:translateX(100%); opacity:0; } to { transform:translateX(0); opacity:1; } }\r\n        /* Unified Modal (v7.117) */\r\n        .astro-modal-backdrop { position:fixed; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:100%; background:rgba(0,0,0,0.65); z-index:10000; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; }\r\n        .astro-modal { background:#1a1e2e; border:1px solid #30363d; border-radius:12px; padding:24px; min-width:320px; max-width:480px; box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.6); }\r\n        .astro-modal-title { margin:0 0 16px 0; font-size:18px; font-weight:600; }\r\n        .astro-modal-body { margin:0 0 20px 0; color:#e0e6f0; line-height:1.6; font-size:14px; }\r\n        .astro-modal-actions { display:flex; gap:12px; justify-content:flex-end; }\r\n        .astro-modal-field { margin-bottom:14px; }\r\n        .astro-modal-field label { display:block; margin-bottom:6px; color:#8b949e; font-size:13px; }\r\n\n⚠️ [... middle content omitted — showing head and tail ...]\n\n        }\r\n        function getPtzPosition() {\r\n            var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\r\n            if (!dev) return;\r\n            apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/position').then(function(result) {\r\n                var posEl = document.getElementById('ptzPosition');\r\n                if (result && result.success && result.data) {\r\n                    var p = result.data;\r\n                    posEl.innerHTML = 'Pan: ' + (p.pan || 0) + ' | Tilt: ' + (p.tilt || 0) + ' | Zoom: ' + (p.zoom || 0);\r\n                } else {\r\n                    posEl.innerHTML = 'Pan: -- | Tilt: -- | Zoom: --';\r\n                }\r\n            }).catch(function(e) {});\r\n        }\r\n        // Calibration (placeholder)\r\n        function calibrate(type) {\r\n            if (!window.connectedDevice || !window.connectedDevice.ip) { showToast('warning', '请先连接设备'); return; }\r\n            var dev = window.connectedDevice.ip;\r\n            apiPost('/api/v1/calibration/' + dev + '/' + type, null).then(function(r) {\r\n                if (r.ok !== false) addLog('info', '开始 ' + type + ' 校准...');\r\n            }).catch(function(e) { addLog('error', '校准失败'); });\r\n        }\r\n        // ASCOM (placeholder)\r\n        function connectAscom(type) {\r\n            apiPost('/api/v1/ascom/' + type + '/connect', null).then(function(r) {\r\n                if (r && r.success !== false) {\r\n                    showToast('success', type + ' 连接成功');\r\n                    addLog('info', type + ' 连接成功');\r\n                }\r\n            }).catch(function(e) { addLog('error', type + ' 连接失败'); });\r\n        }\r\n        // Settings (placeholder)\r\n        function saveSettings() {\r\n            apiPost('/api/v1/settings', {\r\n                port: parseInt(document.getElementById('settingPort').value),\r\n                log_level: document.getElementById('settingLogLevel').value,\r\n                db_path: document.getElementById('settingDbPath').value\r\n            }).then(function() {\r\n                addLog('info', '设置已保存');\r\n                showToast('success', '设置已保存');\r\n            }).catch(function(e) { showToast('error', '保存失败'); });\r\n        }\r\n        // Stream / Storage Controls\r\n        function refreshStreamDeviceList() {\r\n            var online = (allDevices || []).filter(function(d) { return d.online; });\r\n            var sel = document.getElementById('advStreamDevice');\r\n            if (!sel) return;\r\n            var current = sel.value;\r\n            sel.innerHTML = '<option value=\"\">未连接设备</option>';\r\n            online.forEach(function(d) {\r\n                var option = document.createElement('option');\r\n                option.value = d.ip;\r\n                option.textContent = ((d.model ? d.model + ' ' : '') + (d.name || d.device_name || d.ip)).trim() + ' (' + d.ip + ')';\r\n                sel.appendChild(option);\r\n            });\r\n            if (current) sel.value = current;\r\n        }\r\n        function onStreamDeviceChange() {\r\n            var ip = document.getElementById('advStreamDevice').value;\r\n            var noDevice = document.getElementById('streamNoDevice');\r\n            var controlArea = document.getElementById('streamControlArea');\r\n            var statusSpan = document.getElementById('streamDeviceStatus');\r\n            if (ip) {\r\n                var device = allDevices.find(function(d) { return d.ip === ip; });\r\n                noDevice.style.display = 'none';\r\n                controlArea.style.display = 'block';\r\n                statusSpan.textContent = device ? ('已连接: ' + ip) : ip;\r\n                resetStreamButtons();\r\n            } else {\r\n                noDevice.style.display = 'block';\r\n                controlArea.style.display = 'none';\r\n                statusSpan.textContent = '';\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n        function resetStreamButtons() {\r\n            document.getElementById('btnStreamStart').disabled = false;\r\n\n[Read output capped at 128KB for this call. Use offset=1736 to continue.][... 83079 more characters truncated]"}],"details":{"truncation":{"truncated":true,"truncatedBy":"bytes","totalLines":3061,"totalBytes":167037,"outputLines":813,"outputBytes":51111,"lastLinePartial":false,"firstLineExceedsLimit":false,"maxLines":2000,"maxBytes":51200}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1783115584878}}
