{"type":"message","id":"79f0e95e","parentId":"b1e22e90","timestamp":"2026-07-03T21:54:30.292Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_bd2196c5cfd04a989ce5a18d","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[32;1mFilename    [0m[32;1m LineNumber[0m[32;1m Line[0m\r\n[32;1m--------    [0m [32;1m----------[0m [32;1m----[0m\r\nconsole.html         86                                     <select id=\"focusMode\" style=\"padding:4px 8px;background:#��\r\nindex.html         1371                             if (typeof loadFocusMode === 'function') {\r\nindex.html         1372                                 loadFocusMode();\r\nindex.html         2209         function ptzFocus(mode) {\r\nindex.html         2228         function setFocusMode(mode) {\r\nindex.html         2242         function loadFocusMode() {\r\nindex.html         2316             ptzZoom, ptzFocus, setFocusMode,"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":378,"aggregated":"[32;1mFilename    [0m[32;1m LineNumber[0m[32;1m Line[0m\r\n[32;1m--------    [0m [32;1m----------[0m [32;1m----[0m\r\nconsole.html         86                                     <select id=\"focusMode\" style=\"padding:4px 8px;background:#��\r\nindex.html         1371                             if (typeof loadFocusMode === 'function') {\r\nindex.html         1372                                 loadFocusMode();\r\nindex.html         2209         function ptzFocus(mode) {\r\nindex.html         2228         function setFocusMode(mode) {\r\nindex.html         2242         function loadFocusMode() {\r\nindex.html         2316             ptzZoom, ptzFocus, setFocusMode,","cwd":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1783115670292}}
{"type":"message","id":"f2adc241","parentId":"79f0e95e","timestamp":"2026-07-03T21:55:55.411Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the structure. The `ptzFocus`, `setFocusMode`, and `loadFocusMode` functions are defined in index.html, not console.html. Let me read those sections from index.html to understand how focus mode currently works.\n\nLet me now plan the changes needed:\n\n1. **运动控制 (console-left)**: \n   - Currently has PTZ direction controls + speed\n   - Has \"变焦/对焦\" section with focus buttons and focusMode select\n   - Need to move PTZ/OSD toggle here, replacing current focus position\n   - Move focus group (focus mode switch + focus move buttons) to right side image controls\n\n2. **画面控制 (console-right)**:\n   - Currently has brightness, contrast, saturation, sharpness\n   - White balance mode + R/B sliders\n   - Noise reduction (空域/时域)\n   - Exposure mode + shutter/iris\n   - Gain\n   - OSD controls (信息/PTZ)\n   \n   Need to add:\n   - Focus mode dropdown (3 options: auto, manual, local)\n   - Focus move buttons (only visible in manual mode)\n   - Local focus mode: box selection button + timer input (0 = no schedule)\n   - Stop button when local is active\n   - Move noise reduction below saturation/sharpness\n\nLet me re-read the user's requirements more carefully:\n\n1. Move PTZ/OSD display toggle → motion control group, replacing current focus position\n2. Move motion control's focus group (focus mode switch + focus move buttons) → right side image controls\n3. Reorganize region selection buttons\n4. White balance: 3 dropdown options (auto, manual, local). Only manual shows R/B sliders. Local becomes 2 buttons: box selection + timer input (minutes, 0=no schedule). Local pressed → stop button\n5. Focus mode: same pattern as white balance - 3 dropdowns (auto, manual, local). Manual shows focus move buttons. Local: box selection + timer input. Local pressed → stop button\n6. Move time/space domain noise reduction below saturation/sharpness\n\nNow let me think about the implementation:\n\nCurrent layout of console-left (运动控制):\n- Collapsible: PTZ控制\n  - Direction controls + speed\n  - Info block (光圈/快门/R/B/空域/时域/Pan/Tilt/Zoom)\n  - 码流控制\n  - 预置点\n  - 变焦/对焦 (焦距 + 对焦按钮 + focusMode select)\n- Collapsible: 媒体信息\n\nCurrent layout of console-right (画面控制):\n- Collapsible: 操作日志\n- Collapsible: 画面控制\n  - Brightness/contrast\n  - Saturation/sharpness\n  - 白平衡模式 + R/B sliders\n  - 降噪 (空域/时域)\n  - 曝光模式 + 快门/光圈\n  - 增益\n  - OSD 控制\n\nChanges needed:\n\n### Step 1: Move PTZ/OSD toggle to motion control group\nThe PTZ/OSD toggle should be added to the motion control section. Looking at the current code, there's no explicit PTZ/OSD toggle in the left panel. The OSD controls are in the right panel (infoOsdSwitch, ptzOsdSwitch). I need to add a PTZ OSD toggle to the motion control section.\n\nWait, let me re-read the requirement: \"把画面控制的PTZ\\OSD显示开关，移动到运动控制的分组，替代现在对焦的这个位置\"\n\nSo the PTZ/OSD display switch (currently in 画面控制 on the right) needs to be moved to the 运动控制 group, replacing where the focus controls currently are.\n\nCurrently in 运动控制, the last section is \"变焦/对焦\" which contains:\n- 焦距 buttons (+/-)\n- 对焦 buttons (远/近)\n- focusMode select\n\nThe PTZ/OSD switch should replace this section entirely. So the new 运动控制 will have:\n- PTZ direction controls + speed\n- Info block\n- 码流\n- 预置点\n- PTZ OSD toggle (replacing 变焦/对焦)\n\n### Step 2: Move focus group to right side\nThe focus group (focus mode switch + focus move buttons) should move from 运动控制 to 画面控制 on the right.\n\nIn 画面控制, after saturation/sharpness, we need to add:\n- Focus mode dropdown (3 options)\n- Focus move buttons (up/down or near/far) - only visible in manual mode\n- Local focus mode handling\n\n### Step 3: Reorganize region selection buttons\nThe user mentions \"按照以下逻辑整理当前的框选分区的按钮\" but doesn't specify what to do. This seems like it might be part of the whitebalance/focus local mode changes. Let me re-read...\n\nActually, looking at the requirements again:\n- Point 4: White balance local mode uses box selection + timer\n- Point 5: Focus mode local mode uses box selection + timer\n\nThese are the \"框选分区的按钮\" that need to be organized.\n\n### Step 4: White balance changes\n- Change from current 3 options (自动官方, 自动, 手动) to 3 options (自动, 手动, 局部)\n- In manual mode: show R/B sliders (already done)\n- In local mode: show 2 buttons - box selection + timer input (minutes, 0=no schedule)\n- Local pressed → stop button\n\n### Step 5: Focus mode changes\n- Change from 3 options (手动, 自动, 半自动) to 3 options (自动, 手动, 局部)\n- In manual mode: show focus move buttons (near/far)\n- In local mode: same as white balance - box selection + timer\n- Local pressed → stop button\n\n### Step 6: Move noise reduction below saturation/sharpness\nCurrently:\n```\n饱和度 | 锐度\n白平衡 | R | B\n降噪(空域) | 降噪(时域)\n曝光模式 | 快门 | 光圈\n增益\n```\n\nAfter change:\n```\n饱和度 | 锐度\n降噪(空域) | 降噪(时域)\n白平衡 | R | B\n曝光模式 | 快门 | 光圈\n增益\n```\n\nNow let me implement these changes step by step. First, let me backup.\n\nActually, wait. Let me re-read the user's requirements more carefully:\n\n\"3. 按照以下逻辑整理当前的框选分区的按钮\"\n\nThis point 3 seems to reference points 4 and 5 for the logic. So the \"框选分区的按钮\" refers to the box selection + timer buttons in local mode.\n\nLet me also check if there are any existing \"框选\" (region selection) buttons in the media controls section. Looking at the HTML, I see:\n```html\n<!-- v8.10: 框选区域 overlay（默认隐藏） -->\n<div id=\"regionOverlay\" style=\"display:none;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;cursor:crosshair;z-index:100\">\n    <div id=\"regionBox\" style=\"position:absolute;border:2px dashed #3fb950;background:rgba(63,185,80,0.15);display:none;pointer-events:none\"></div>\n</div>\n```\n\nAnd in media controls:\n```html\n<!-- v8.10: 框选分析 -->\n<div class=\"section-subtitle\">框选分析</div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap\">\n    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" id=\"btnRegionWB\" onclick=\"toggleRegionMode('whitebalance')\">🎨 白平衡</button>\n    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" id=\"btnRegionAF\" onclick=\"toggleRegionMode('focus')\">🔍 对焦</button>\n</div>\n```\n\nThese are the \"框选分区的按钮\". The user wants to organize them according to the logic in points 4 and 5.\n\nOK so the overall plan is clear. Let me start implementing.\n\nFirst, let me backup the file, then make the changes step by step.\n\nLet me think about the exact HTML changes needed:\n\n### Changes to console-left (运动控制):\n\n1. Remove \"变焦/对焦\" section (焦距 + 对焦按钮 + focusMode select)\n2. Add PTZ OSD toggle in its place\n\nNew 运动控制 structure:\n```html\n<!-- 指向控制 + 信息展示 -->\n[direction controls + info block]\n<!-- 码流控制 -->\n<!-- 预置点 -->\n<!-- PTZ OSD 开关 -->\n<div class=\"section-subtitle\">OSD</div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;gap:6px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap\">\n    <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:13px\">PTZ OSD</span>\n    <label class=\"switch\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"ptzOsdSwitch\" checked onchange=\"togglePtzOsdSwitch(this.checked)\">\n        <span class=\"slider\"></span>\n    </label>\n</div>\n```\n\n### Changes to console-right (画面控制):\n\nAdd focus mode section between saturation/sharpness and white balance:\n```html\n<!-- 饱和度 + 锐度 - keep as is -->\n<!-- 降噪 (moved from below white balance) -->\n<div class=\"form-group\" style=\"margin-bottom:4px\">\n    <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">对焦模式</label>\n    <select id=\"focusMode\" style=\"width:100%;padding:4px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:12px\" onchange=\"setFocusMode(this.value)\">\n        <option value=\"auto\">自动</option>\n        <option value=\"manual\">手动</option>\n        <option value=\"local\">局部</option>\n    </select>\n</div>\n<!-- 焦点移动按钮 (only in manual mode) -->\n<div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:4px\" id=\"focusMoveControls\" style=\"display:none\">\n    <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">焦点:</span>\n    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onmousedown=\"ptzFocus('far')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" ontouchstart=\"ptzFocus('far')\" ontouchend=\"ptzStop()\">远</button>\n    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onmousedown=\"ptzFocus('near')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" ontouchstart=\"ptzFocus('near')\" ontouchend=\"ptzStop()\">近</button>\n</div>\n<!-- 局部对焦模式 (only in local mode) -->\n<div id=\"focusLocalControls\" style=\"display:none\">\n    <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:4px\">\n        <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" id=\"btnFocusRegionSelect\" onclick=\"toggleRegionMode('focus')\">框选</button>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px\">\n            <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">定时:</span>\n            <input type=\"number\" id=\"focusTimerInput\" value=\"0\" min=\"0\" style=\"width:50px;padding:2px 4px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:11px\">\n            <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">分钟</span>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <button class=\"btn btn-danger btn-sm\" id=\"btnFocusLocalStop\" onclick=\"stopAutoFocus()\" style=\"display:none\">停止</button>\n</div>\n```\n\n### White balance changes:\n\nChange the dropdown from 3 options (自动官方, 自动, 手动) to 3 options (自动, 手动, 局部):\n```html\n<select id=\"wbMode\" ...>\n    <option value=\"auto\">自动</option>\n    <option value=\"manual\">手动</option>\n    <option value=\"local\">局部</option>\n</select>\n```\n\nAnd add local mode controls:\n```html\n<!-- 局部白平衡模式 -->\n<div id=\"wbLocalControls\" style=\"display:none\">\n    <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:4px\">\n        <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" id=\"btnWbRegionSelect\" onclick=\"toggleRegionMode('whitebalance')\">框选</button>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px\">\n            <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">定时:</span>\n            <input type=\"number\" id=\"wbTimerInput\" value=\"0\" min=\"0\" style=\"width:50px;padding:2px 4px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:11px\">\n            <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">分钟</span>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <button class=\"btn btn-danger btn-sm\" id=\"btnWbLocalStop\" onclick=\"stopAutoWhiteBalance()\" style=\"display:none\">停止</button>\n</div>\n```\n\n### Noise reduction movement:\n\nMove from below white balance to between saturation/sharpness:\n```html\n<!-- 降噪 -->\n<div class=\"form-group\" style=\"margin-bottom:4px\">\n    <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">降噪模式</label>\n    <select id=\"dnrMode\" ...>\n        <option value=\"off\">关闭</option>\n        <option value=\"spatial\">空域</option>\n        <option value=\"temporal\">时域</option>\n        <option value=\"both\">两者</option>\n    </select>\n</div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:4px\">\n    <div style=\"flex:1\">\n        <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">空域降噪 <span id=\"dnrSpatialVal\" style=\"color:#58a6ff\">--</span></label>\n        <input type=\"range\" id=\"dnrSpatial\" ...>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"flex:1\">\n        <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">时域降噪 <span id=\"dnrTemporalVal\" style=\"color:#58a6ff\">--</span></label>\n        <input type=\"range\" id=\"dnrTemporal\" ...>\n    </div>\n</div>\n```\n\nWait, actually the user said \"移动当前的时域、空域降噪，位置提到饱和度、锐度的下方\". So the noise reduction controls should move from below white balance to below saturation/sharpness. But the individual range sliders should stay where they are (below the label). Let me think about this more carefully.\n\nCurrently the layout is:\n```\n亮度 | 对比度\n饱和度 | 锐度\n白平衡模式 | R | B\n降噪(空域) | 降噪(时域)\n曝光模式 | 快门 | 光圈\n增益\n```\n\nAfter moving noise reduction below saturation/sharpness:\n```\n亮度 | 对比度\n饱和度 | 锐度\n降噪(空域) | 降噪(时域)\n白平衡模式 | R | B\n曝光模式 | 快门 | 光圈\n增益\n```\n\nThis means the noise reduction section moves up, and white balance + everything below it shifts down.\n\nNow let me also think about the JavaScript changes needed:\n\n1. `setWhiteBalanceMode` - needs to handle 'local' mode instead of 'auto_official'/'auto_astrohub'\n2. `setFocusMode` - needs to handle 'local' mode\n3. New functions: `stopAutoWhiteBalance()`, `stopAutoFocus()`\n4. Update `toggleRegionMode` to work with both WB and AF\n5. Update `loadWhiteBalance` to set default selected option based on device state\n\nLet me also check what `toggleRegionMode` does currently.<tool_call>现在我理解了整体结构。让我先备份文件，然后分步执行修改。<tool_call>exec<arg_key>command</arg_key><arg_value>$backupDir = \"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\backup_$(Get-Date -Format 'yyyyMMdd_HHmmss')\"; New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $backupDir -Force | Out-Null; Copy-Item \"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html\" \"$backupDir\\console.html\"; Write-Output \"Backup created at: $backupDir\"</arg_value></tool_call>","thinkingSignature":""}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":83560,"output":4304,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87864,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783115670293,"responseId":"cht000d43a5@dx19f29f9e40e2872503"}}
