{"type":"message","id":"afa36728","parentId":"7f91e151","timestamp":"2026-07-03T22:07:57.484Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d1a222393d4d4f3faa11aaee","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"                    <!-- 右: 操作日志 + 画面控制 -->\r\n                    <div class=\"console-right\">\r\n                        <!-- 操作日志（折叠，默认展开） -->\r\n                        <div class=\"collapsible-section\" id=\"logControlSection\">\r\n                            <div class=\"collapsible-header\" onclick=\"toggleSection('logControlSection')\">\r\n                                <h3 style=\"font-size:15px;color:#8b949e;margin:0\">📋 操作日志</h3>\r\n                                <span class=\"collapse-icon\">▼</span>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"collapsible-content\">\r\n                                <div style=\"background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:8px;padding:8px;overflow-y:auto;height:270px\" class=\"hide-scrollbar\">\r\n                                    <div id=\"operationLogBox\" style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:monospace;color:#8b949e\">\r\n                                        <div style=\"color:#6e7681\">等待连接...</div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <!-- 画面控制（折叠，移到右侧） -->\r\n                        <div class=\"collapsible-section\" id=\"imageControlSection\" style=\"margin-top:12px\">\r\n                            <div class=\"collapsible-header\" onclick=\"toggleSection('imageControlSection')\">\r\n                                <h3 style=\"font-size:15px;color:#d29922;margin:0\">🎨 画面控制</h3>\r\n                                <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onclick=\"event.stopPropagation();refreshImageControls()\" style=\"margin-left:10px;padding:2px 8px;font-size:12px\">刷新</button>\r\n                                <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onclick=\"event.stopPropagation();resetImageControls()\" style=\"margin-left:5px;padding:2px 8px;font-size:12px\">重置</button>\r\n                                <span class=\"collapse-icon\">▼</span>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"collapsible-content\">\r\n                                <div class=\"card\">\r\n                                    <!-- 基础调节 -->\r\n                                    <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:4px\">\r\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">\r\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">亮度 <span id=\"brightnessVal\" style=\"color:#58a6ff\">50</span></label>\r\n                                            <input type=\"range\" id=\"consoleBrightness\" min=\"0\" max=\"100\" value=\"50\" style=\"width:100%\" oninput=\"document.getElementById('brightnessVal').textContent=this.value\" onchange=\"adjustImage('brightness', this.value)\">\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">\r\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">对比度 <span id=\"contrastVal\" style=\"color:#58a6ff\">50</span></label>\r\n                                            <input type=\"range\" id=\"consoleContrast\" min=\"0\" max=\"100\" value=\"50\" style=\"width:100%\" oninput=\"document.getElementById('contrastVal').textContent=this.value\" onchange=\"adjustImage('contrast', this.value)\">\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- 饱和度 + 锐度 - v6.02: 合并同一行 -->\r\n                                    <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:4px\">\r\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">\r\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">饱和度 <span id=\"saturationVal\" style=\"color:#58a6ff\">50</span></label>\r\n                                            <input type=\"range\" id=\"consoleSaturation\" min=\"0\" max=\"100\" value=\"50\" style=\"width:100%\" oninput=\"document.getElementById('saturationVal').textContent=this.value\" onchange=\"adjustImage('saturation', this.value)\">\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">\r\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">锐度 <span id=\"sharpnessVal\" style=\"color:#58a6ff\">50</span></label>\r\n                                            <input type=\"range\" id=\"consoleSharpness\" min=\"0\" max=\"100\" value=\"50\" style=\"width:100%\" oninput=\"document.getElementById('sharpnessVal').textContent=this.value\" onchange=\"setSharpness(this.value)\">\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- 白平衡 -->\r\n                                    <div class=\"form-group\" style=\"margin-bottom:4px\">\r\n                                        <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">白平衡模式</label>\r\n                                        <select id=\"wbMode\" style=\"width:100%;padding:4px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:12px\" onchange=\"setWhiteBalanceMode(this.value)\">\r\n                                            <option value=\"\">-- 加载中 --</option>\r\n                                        </select>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:4px\">\r\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">\r\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#f85149\">R <span id=\"wbRedVal\" style=\"color:#f85149\">--</span></label>\r\n                                            <input type=\"range\" id=\"wbRed\" min=\"0\" max=\"255\" value=\"50\" style=\"width:100%\" oninput=\"document.getElementById('wbRedVal').textContent=this.value\" onchange=\"setWhiteBalanceGain('red', this.value)\" disabled>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">\r\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#58a6ff\">B <span id=\"wbBlueVal\" style=\"color:#58a6ff\">--</span></label>\r\n                                            <input type=\"range\" id=\"wbBlue\" min=\"0\" max=\"255\" value=\"50\" style=\"width:100%\" oninput=\"document.getElementById('wbBlueVal').textContent=this.value\" onchange=\"setWhiteBalanceGain('blue', this.value)\" disabled>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- 降噪 -->\r\n                                    <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:4px\">\r\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">\r\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">空域降噪 <span id=\"dnrSpatialVal\" style=\"color:#58a6ff\">--</span></label>\r\n                                            <input type=\"range\" id=\"dnrSpatial\" min=\"0\" max=\"100\" value=\"50\" style=\"width:100%\" oninput=\"document.getElementById('dnrSpatialVal').textContent=this.value\" onchange=\"setNoiseReduce('spatial', this.value)\">\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">\r\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">时域降噪 <span id=\"dnrTemporalVal\" style=\"color:#58a6ff\">--</span></label>\r\n                                            <input type=\"range\" id=\"dnrTemporal\" min=\"0\" max=\"100\" value=\"50\" style=\"width:100%\" oninput=\"document.getElementById('dnrTemporalVal').textContent=this.value\" onchange=\"setNoiseReduce('temporal', this.value)\">\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- 曝光模式 + 快门/光圈 (v5.47: 整合到一行) -->\r\n                                    <div class=\"form-group\" style=\"margin-bottom:4px\">\r\n                                        <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">曝光模式</label>\r\n                                        <select id=\"exposureMode\" style=\"width:100%;padding:4px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:12px\" onchange=\"setExposureMode(this.value);updateShutterIrisState()\">\r\n                                            <!-- v7.35: 从 function.json 动态加载 -->\r\n                                        </select>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- 快门/光圈整合一行 -->\r\n                                    <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:4px\">\r\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">\r\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">快门</label>\r\n                                            <select id=\"shutterSpeed\" style=\"width:100%;padding:3px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:11px\" onchange=\"setShutterSpeed(this.value)\" disabled>\r\n                                                <option value=\"\">--</option>\r\n                                            </select>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">\r\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">光圈</label>\r\n                                            <select id=\"irisLevel\" style=\"width:100%;padding:3px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:11px\" onchange=\"setIris(this.value)\" disabled>\r\n                                                <option value=\"\">--</option>\r\n                                            </select>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- v7.03: 增益控制 -->\r\n                                    <div style=\"margin-bottom:8px\">\r\n                                        <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">增益 <span id=\"gainVal\" style=\"color:#58a6ff\">--</span></label>\r\n                                        <input type=\"range\" id=\"gainLevel\" min=\"0\" max=\"100\" value=\"0\" style=\"width:100%\" oninput=\"document.getElementById('gainVal').textContent=this.value\" onchange=\"setGain(this.value)\" disabled>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- OSD 控制 - v6.14: 标题改为“信息” -->\r\n                                    <div class=\"form-group\" style=\"margin-bottom:8px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center\">\r\n                                        <label style=\"font-size:12px;margin:0\">信息</label>\r\n                                        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:16px\">\r\n                                            <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px\">\r\n                                                <span style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">OSD</span>\r\n                                                <label class=\"toggle-switch\">\r\n                                                    <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"infoOsdSwitch\" onchange=\"toggleInfoOsdSwitch(this.checked)\">\r\n                                                    <span class=\"toggle-slider\"></span>\r\n                                                </label>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                            <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px\">\r\n                                                <span style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">PTZ</span>\r\n                                                <label class=\"toggle-switch\">\r\n                                                    <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"ptzOsdSwitch\" onchange=\"togglePtzOsdSwitch(this.checked)\">\r\n                                                    <span class=\"toggle-slider\"></span>\r\n                                                </label>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n/* v7.30: 模块禁用样式 - 保留折叠展开功能 */\r\n.section-disabled .collapsible-content {\r\n    opacity: 0.4;\r\n    pointer-events: none;\r\n}\r\n.section-disabled .collapsible-header {\r\n    opacity: 0.6;\r\n}\r\n.section-disabled .collapsible-header:hover {\r\n    cursor: pointer;\r\n}\r\n\r\n/* v6.02: 拨杆开关样式 */\r\n.toggle-switch {\r\n    position: relative;\r\n    display: inline-block;\r\n    width: 40px;\r\n    height: 22px;\r\n\n[1255 more lines in file. Use offset=331 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783116477484}}
{"type":"message","id":"563ce4e3","parentId":"afa36728","timestamp":"2026-07-03T22:09:33.397Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture of the current layout. Let me plan all the changes needed:\n\n**Current layout (console-right):**\n1. 亮度 | 对比度\n2. 饱和度 | 锐度\n3. 白平衡模式 + R/B sliders\n4. 降噪(空域) | 降噪(时域)\n5. 曝光模式 + 快门/光圈\n6. 增益\n7. OSD控制 (信息/PTZ)\n\n**Target layout:**\n1. 亮度 | 对比度\n2. 饱和度 | 锐度\n3. 降噪(空域) | 降噪(时域)  [moved from below WB]\n4. 白平衡模式 + R/B sliders\n5. 对焦模式 + 焦点移动按钮 (NEW, between WB and exposure)\n6. 曝光模式 + 快门/光圈\n7. 增益\n8. OSD控制 (信息/PTZ)\n\n**Changes to console-left (运动控制):**\n- Remove \"变焦/对焦\" section (焦距 + 对焦按钮 + focusMode select)\n- Add PTZ OSD switch in its place\n\n**White balance changes:**\n- Change dropdown from 3 options (自动官方, 自动, 手动) to 3 options (自动, 手动, 局部)\n- In local mode: show box selection button + timer input (minutes, 0=no schedule)\n- Local pressed → stop button\n\n**Focus mode changes:**\n- Change from 3 options (手动, 自动, 半自动) to 3 options (自动, 手动, 局部)\n- In manual mode: show focus move buttons (远/近)\n- In local mode: same as white balance - box selection + timer\n- Local pressed → stop button\n\nNow let me implement this step by step. I'll use edit operations on console.html.\n\nLet me think about the exact edits needed:\n\n### Step 1: Modify console-left - remove 变焦/对焦 section, add PTZ OSD switch\n\nThe 变焦/对焦 section is at lines ~119-134 (approximately). I need to replace it with a PTZ OSD switch.\n\nLooking at the current code around line 119:\n```html\n<!-- 变焦/对焦 -->\n<div class=\"section-subtitle\">变焦/对焦</div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center;margin-bottom:8px\">\n    <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:13px\">焦距:</span>\n    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onmousedown=\"ptzZoom('in')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" ontouchstart=\"ptzZoom('in')\" ontouchend=\"ptzStop()\">🔍+</button>\n    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onmousedown=\"ptzZoom('out')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" ontouchstart=\"ptzZoom('out')\" ontouchend=\"ptzStop()\">🔍-</button>\n</div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center;margin-bottom:8px\">\n    <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:13px\">对焦:</span>\n    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onmousedown=\"ptzFocus('near')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" ontouchstart=\"ptzFocus('near')\" ontouchend=\"ptzStop()\">远</button>\n    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onmousedown=\"ptzFocus('far')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" ontouchstart=\"ptzFocus('far')\" ontouchend=\"ptzStop()\">近</button>\n    <select id=\"focusMode\" style=\"padding:4px 8px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:12px\" onchange=\"setFocusMode(this.value)\">\n        <option value=\"manual\">手动</option>\n        <option value=\"auto\">自动</option>\n        <option value=\"semiauto\">半自动</option>\n    </select>\n</div>\n```\n\nI need to replace this with:\n```html\n<!-- PTZ OSD 开关 -->\n<div class=\"section-subtitle\">OSD</div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;gap:6px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:8px\">\n    <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">PTZ OSD</span>\n    <label class=\"toggle-switch\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"ptzOsdSwitchInPtz\" checked onchange=\"togglePtzOsdSwitch(this.checked)\">\n        <span class=\"toggle-slider\"></span>\n    </label>\n</div>\n```\n\nWait, but the PTZ OSD switch already exists in the image control section. The user wants to MOVE it from there to the motion control group. So I should:\n1. Remove the existing `ptzOsdSwitch` from the image control section\n2. Add a new `ptzOsdSwitchInPtz` to the motion control section\n\nActually wait, looking more carefully at the requirement: \"把画面控制的PTZ\\OSD显示开关，移动到运动控制的分组，替代现在对焦的这个位置\"\n\nSo the PTZ OSD switch should be moved FROM the right panel TO the left panel, replacing where the focus controls currently are.\n\nThis means:\n1. Remove the PTZ OSD switch from the right panel (imageControlSection)\n2. Add a PTZ OSD switch to the left panel (motion control), replacing the 变焦/对焦 section\n\nBut the toggle-switch CSS class is defined in the style section. Let me check if it's available... Yes, it's defined in the styles.\n\nOK let me now plan all the edits systematically:\n\n### Edit 1: console-left - Replace 变焦/对焦 with PTZ OSD switch\nOld text (lines ~119-134):\n```html\n                                <!-- 变焦/对焦 -->\n                                <div class=\"section-subtitle\">变焦/对焦</div>\n                                <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center;margin-bottom:8px\">\n                                    <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:13px\">焦距:</span>\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onmousedown=\"ptzZoom('in')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" ontouchstart=\"ptzZoom('in')\" ontouchend=\"ptzStop()\">🔍+</button>\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onmousedown=\"ptzZoom('out')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" ontouchstart=\"ptzZoom('out')\" ontouchend=\"ptzStop()\">🔍-</button>\n                                </div>\n                                <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center;margin-bottom:8px\">\n                                    <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:13px\">对焦:</span>\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onmousedown=\"ptzFocus('near')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" ontouchstart=\"ptzFocus('near')\" ontouchend=\"ptzStop()\">远</button>\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onmousedown=\"ptzFocus('far')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" ontouchstart=\"ptzFocus('far')\" ontouchend=\"ptzStop()\">近</button>\n                                    <select id=\"focusMode\" style=\"padding:4px 8px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:12px\" onchange=\"setFocusMode(this.value)\">\n                                        <option value=\"manual\">手动</option>\n                                        <option value=\"auto\">自动</option>\n                                        <option value=\"semiauto\">半自动</option>\n                                    </select>\n                                </div>\n```\n\nNew text:\n```html\n                                <!-- PTZ OSD 开关 -->\n                                <div class=\"section-subtitle\">OSD</div>\n                                <div style=\"display:flex;gap:6px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:8px\">\n                                    <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">PTZ OSD</span>\n                                    <label class=\"toggle-switch\">\n                                        <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"ptzOsdSwitchInPtz\" checked onchange=\"togglePtzOsdSwitch(this.checked)\">\n                                        <span class=\"toggle-slider\"></span>\n                                    </label>\n                                </div>\n```\n\n### Edit 2: console-right - Move noise reduction above white balance, add focus mode\n\nFirst, let me restructure the entire image control section. Currently:\n\n```html\n                                    <!-- 饱和度 + 锐度 -->\n                                    ...\n                                    <!-- 白平衡 -->\n                                    <div class=\"form-group\" style=\"margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                        <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">白平衡模式</label>\n                                        <select id=\"wbMode\" ...onchange=\"setWhiteBalanceMode(this.value)\">\n                                            <option value=\"\">-- 加载中 --</option>\n                                        </select>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">R...</div>\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">B...</div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <!-- 降噪 -->\n                                    <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">空域降噪...</div>\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">时域降噪...</div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <!-- 曝光模式 + 快门/光圈 -->\n                                    ...\n```\n\nNew order:\n```html\n                                    <!-- 饱和度 + 锐度 -->\n                                    ...\n                                    <!-- 降噪 (moved up) -->\n                                    <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">空域降噪...</div>\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">时域降噪...</div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <!-- 白平衡 -->\n                                    <div class=\"form-group\" style=\"margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                        <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">白平衡模式</label>\n                                        <select id=\"wbMode\" ...onchange=\"setWhiteBalanceMode(this.value)\">\n                                            <option value=\"auto\">自动</option>\n                                            <option value=\"manual\">手动</option>\n                                            <option value=\"local\">局部</option>\n                                        </select>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">R...</div>\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">B...</div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <!-- 局部白平衡控制 (hidden by default) -->\n                                    <div id=\"wbLocalControls\" style=\"display:none;margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                            <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" id=\"btnWbRegionSelect\" onclick=\"toggleRegionMode('whitebalance')\">框选</button>\n                                            <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px\">\n                                                <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">定时:</span>\n                                                <input type=\"number\" id=\"wbTimerInput\" value=\"0\" min=\"0\" style=\"width:50px;padding:2px 4px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:11px\">\n                                                <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">分钟</span>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                        <button class=\"btn btn-danger btn-sm\" id=\"btnWbLocalStop\" onclick=\"stopAutoWhiteBalance()\" style=\"display:none\">停止</button>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <!-- 对焦模式 -->\n                                    <div class=\"form-group\" style=\"margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                        <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">对焦模式</label>\n                                        <select id=\"focusMode\" style=\"width:100%;padding:4px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:12px\" onchange=\"setFocusMode(this.value)\">\n                                            <option value=\"auto\">自动</option>\n                                            <option value=\"manual\">手动</option>\n                                            <option value=\"local\">局部</option>\n                                        </select>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <!-- 焦点移动按钮 (only in manual mode) -->\n                                    <div id=\"focusMoveControls\" style=\"display:none;margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                            <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">焦点:</span>\n                                            <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onmousedown=\"ptzFocus('far')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" ontouchstart=\"ptzFocus('far')\" ontouchend=\"ptzStop()\">远</button>\n                                            <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onmousedown=\"ptzFocus('near')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" ontouchstart=\"ptzFocus('near')\" ontouchend=\"ptzStop()\">近</button>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <!-- 局部对焦控制 (hidden by default) -->\n                                    <div id=\"focusLocalControls\" style=\"display:none;margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                            <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" id=\"btnFocusRegionSelect\" onclick=\"toggleRegionMode('focus')\">框选</button>\n                                            <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px\">\n                                                <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">定时:</span>\n                                                <input type=\"number\" id=\"focusTimerInput\" value=\"0\" min=\"0\" style=\"width:50px;padding:2px 4px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:11px\">\n                                                <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">分钟</span>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                        <button class=\"btn btn-danger btn-sm\" id=\"btnFocusLocalStop\" onclick=\"stopAutoFocus()\" style=\"display:none\">停止</button>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <!-- 曝光模式 + 快门/光圈 -->\n                                    ...\n```\n\n### Edit 3: Update JavaScript functions\n\nNeed to update:\n1. `setWhiteBalanceMode` - handle 'local' mode\n2. `setFocusMode` - handle 'local' mode (already in index.html)\n3. Add `stopAutoWhiteBalance()`, `stopAutoFocus()`\n4. Update `toggleRegionMode` to work for both WB and AF\n5. Update `loadWhiteBalance` to set default selected option based on device state\n6. Add event listeners for wbMode/focusMode changes to show/hide controls\n\nLet me also check what `toggleRegionMode` does currently.<tool_call>现在我清楚了整体结构。开始分步执行修改。先处理左侧面板（运动控制），再处理右侧面板（画面控制）。\n\n### 步骤1：左侧面板 — 删除变焦/对焦区，添加PTZ OSD开关<tool_call>edit<arg_key>newText</arg_key><arg_value>                                <!-- PTZ OSD 开关 -->\n                                <div class=\"section-subtitle\">OSD</div>\n                                <div style=\"display:flex;gap:6px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:8px\">\n                                    <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">PTZ OSD</span>\n                                    <label class=\"toggle-switch\">\n                                        <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"ptzOsdSwitchInPtz\" checked onchange=\"togglePtz