{"type":"message","id":"9b84180c","parentId":"8bbf1f4d","timestamp":"2026-07-03T22:35:06.330Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good progress. Now I need to:\n1. Export the new functions to global scope (window.onWbModeChange, window.onFocusModeChange, window.stopAutoWhiteBalance, window.stopAutoFocus)\n2. Update the disable/enable controls list to remove 'ptzOsdSwitch' and add 'ptzOsdSwitchInPtz'\n3. Test if the changes are correct\n\nLet me first find the window exports section and add the new functions.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"### 步骤4：导出新函数到全局作用域"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-64bc806db5d84281a278641d3c883110","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":20,"offset":1583,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":69943,"output":156,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70099,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783118094807,"responseId":"cht000dc8f2@dx19f2a1eeeb32872503"}}
