{"type":"message","id":"a0a504ff","parentId":"13644155","timestamp":"2026-07-03T22:37:32.694Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我需要更新 `loadFocusMode`，以便在加载后触发 `onFocusModeChange` 以更新 UI。另外，旧的 `semiauto` 选项不再存在，所以我应该对其进行映射："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f175df8798254328afe74c85","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"        function loadFocusMode() {\n            var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n            if (!dev) return;\n            apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/focus/mode').then(function(result) {\n                if (result && result.success && result.mode) {\n                    var select = document.getElementById('focusMode');\n                    if (select) {\n                        // 映射旧模式到新选项\n                        var mode = result.mode;\n                        if (mode === 'semiauto') mode = 'auto';\n                        select.value = mode;\n                        // 触发 UI 显示/隐藏\n                        if (typeof onFocusModeChange === 'function') onFocusModeChange(mode);\n                    }\n                }\n            }).catch(function(e) {\n                console.error('获取对焦模式失败:', e);\n            });\n        }","oldText":"        function loadFocusMode() {\n            var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n            if (!dev) return;\n            apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/focus/mode').then(function(result) {\n                if (result && result.success && result.mode) {\n                    var select = document.getElementById('focusMode');\n                    if (select) {\n                        select.value = result.mode;\n                    }\n                }\n            }).catch(function(e) {\n                console.error('获取对焦模式失败:', e);\n            });\n        }"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider