{"type":"message","id":"fe406ee0","parentId":"685ad0ae","timestamp":"2026-07-03T22:40:51.880Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Perfect! The edit was successful. Now the PTZ OSD switch is in the motion control section on the left panel, replacing the old focus controls.Now let me create a summary of all the changes I've made and verify everything is in place:\n\n**Summary of changes:**\n\n1. ✅ Left panel (motion control): Replaced \"变焦/对焦\" section with PTZ OSD toggle switch\n2. ✅ Right panel (image controls): \n   - Moved noise reduction from below white balance to below saturation/sharpness\n   - Changed white balance dropdown to 3 options (自动, 手动, 局部)\n   - Added R/B sliders (only visible in manual mode)\n   - Added local white balance controls (box selection + timer, hidden by default)\n   - Added focus mode dropdown (3 options: 自动, 手动, 局部)\n   - Added focus move buttons (only visible in manual mode)\n   - Added local focus controls (box selection + timer, hidden by default)\n   - Removed PTZ OSD switch from right panel (moved to left)\n3. ✅ JavaScript updates:\n   - Updated `setWhiteBalanceMode` function to handle 'local' mode\n   - Updated `loadWhiteBalance` function to set dropdown directly without recreating options\n   - Added `onWbModeChange` function to show/hide controls based on mode\n   - Added `stopAutoWhiteBalance` function\n   - Added `onFocusModeChange` function to show/hide focus controls based on mode\n   - Added `stopAutoFocus` function\n   - Updated `updatePtzOsdButtons` to sync the new PTZ OSD switch in motion control\n   - Exported new functions to global scope\n   - Updated disable/enable controls list to use 'ptzOsdSwitchInPtz'\n\n\n4. ✅ Updated `index.html`:\n   - Modified `loadFocusMode` to map 'semiauto' to 'auto' and trigger `onFocusModeChange`\n\nI'll verify the white balance dropdown contains the new options: specific test details are still pending.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! The PTZ OSD switch is now in the left panel, replacing the old focus controls. 标准已完成。现在让我汇总所有修改，并确认右侧面板的结构是否正确。让我验证右侧面板（画面控制区的布局顺序）："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_13ab845148b744b48d3c7e01","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":100,"offset":218,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":84039,"output":531,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84570,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783118415620,"responseId":"cht000daa6d@dx19f2a23c8282871503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"9ee93e81","parentId":"fe406ee0","timestamp":"2026-07-03T22:40:51.918Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_13ab845148b744b48d3c7e01","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"                                            <input type=\"range\" id=\"consoleSharpness\" min=\"0\" max=\"100\" value=\"50\" style=\"width:100%\" oninput=\"document.getElementById('sharpnessVal').textContent=this.value\" onchange=\"setSharpness(this.value)\">\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- 降噪（移到饱和度/锐度下方） -->\r\n                                    <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:4px\">\r\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">\r\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">空域降噪 <span id=\"dnrSpatialVal\" style=\"color:#58a6ff\">--</span></label>\r\n                                            <input type=\"range\" id=\"dnrSpatial\" min=\"0\" max=\"100\" value=\"50\" style=\"width:100%\" oninput=\"document.getElementById('dnrSpatialVal').textContent=this.value\" onchange=\"setNoiseReduce('spatial', this.value)\">\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">\r\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">时域降噪 <span id=\"dnrTemporalVal\" style=\"color:#58a6ff\">--</span></label>\r\n                                            <input type=\"range\" id=\"dnrTemporal\" min=\"0\" max=\"100\" value=\"50\" style=\"width:100%\" oninput=\"document.getElementById('dnrTemporalVal').textContent=this.value\" onchange=\"setNoiseReduce('temporal', this.value)\">\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- 白平衡模式 -->\r\n                                    <div class=\"form-group\" style=\"margin-bottom:4px\">\r\n                                        <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">白平衡模式</label>\r\n                                        <select id=\"wbMode\" style=\"width:100%;padding:4px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:12px\" onchange=\"onWbModeChange(this.value)\">\r\n                                            <option value=\"auto\">自动</option>\r\n                                            <option value=\"manual\">手动</option>\r\n                                            <option value=\"local\">局部</option>\r\n                                        </select>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- R/B 滑动条（仅手动模式显示） -->\r\n                                    <div id=\"wbManualControls\" style=\"display:none;flex-direction:row;gap:8px;margin-bottom:4px\">\r\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">\r\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#f85149\">R <span id=\"wbRedVal\" style=\"color:#f85149\">--</span></label>\r\n                                            <input type=\"range\" id=\"wbRed\" min=\"0\" max=\"255\" value=\"50\" style=\"width:100%\" oninput=\"document.getElementById('wbRedVal').textContent=this.value\" onchange=\"setWhiteBalanceGain('red', this.value)\" disabled>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">\r\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#58a6ff\">B <span id=\"wbBlueVal\" style=\"color:#58a6ff\">--</span></label>\r\n                                            <input type=\"range\" id=\"wbBlue\" min=\"0\" max=\"255\" value=\"50\" style=\"width:100%\" oninput=\"document.getElementById('wbBlueVal').textContent=this.value\" onchange=\"setWhiteBalanceGain('blue', this.value)\" disabled>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- 局部白平衡控制（仅局部模式显示） -->\r\n                                    <div id=\"wbLocalControls\" style=\"display:none;margin-bottom:4px\">\r\n                                        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:4px\">\r\n                                            <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" id=\"btnWbRegionSelect\" onclick=\"toggleRegionMode('whitebalance')\">框选</button>\r\n                                            <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px\">\r\n                                                <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">定时:</span>\r\n                                                <input type=\"number\" id=\"wbTimerInput\" value=\"0\" min=\"0\" style=\"width:50px;padding:2px 4px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:11px\">\r\n                                                <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">分钟</span>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <button class=\"btn btn-danger btn-sm\" id=\"btnWbLocalStop\" onclick=\"stopAutoWhiteBalance()\" style=\"display:none;width:100%\">停止</button>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- 对焦模式 -->\r\n                                    <div class=\"form-group\" style=\"margin-bottom:4px\">\r\n                                        <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">对焦模式</label>\r\n                                        <select id=\"focusMode\" style=\"width:100%;padding:4px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:12px\" onchange=\"onFocusModeChange(this.value)\">\r\n                                            <option value=\"auto\">自动</option>\r\n                                            <option value=\"manual\">手动</option>\r\n                                            <option value=\"local\">局部</option>\r\n                                        </select>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- 焦点移动按钮（仅手动模式显示） -->\r\n                                    <div id=\"focusMoveControls\" style=\"display:none;margin-bottom:4px\">\r\n                                        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap\">\r\n                                            <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">焦点:</span>\r\n                                            <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onmousedown=\"ptzFocus('far')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" ontouchstart=\"ptzFocus('far')\" ontouchend=\"ptzStop()\">远</button>\r\n                                            <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onmousedown=\"ptzFocus('near')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" ontouchstart=\"ptzFocus('near')\" ontouchend=\"ptzStop()\">近</button>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- 局部对焦控制（仅局部模式显示） -->\r\n                                    <div id=\"focusLocalControls\" style=\"display:none;margin-bottom:4px\">\r\n                                        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:4px\">\r\n                                            <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" id=\"btnFocusRegionSelect\" onclick=\"toggleRegionMode('focus')\">框选</button>\r\n                                            <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px\">\r\n                                                <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">定时:</span>\r\n                                                <input type=\"number\" id=\"focusTimerInput\" value=\"0\" min=\"0\" style=\"width:50px;padding:2px 4px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:11px\">\r\n                                                <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">分钟</span>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <button class=\"btn btn-danger btn-sm\" id=\"btnFocusLocalStop\" onclick=\"stopAutoFocus()\" style=\"display:none;width:100%\">停止</button>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- 曝光模式 + 快门/光圈 (v5.47: 整合到一行) -->\r\n                                    <div class=\"form-group\" style=\"margin-bottom:4px\">\r\n                                        <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">曝光模式</label>\r\n                                        <select id=\"exposureMode\" style=\"width:100%;padding:4px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:12px\" onchange=\"setExposureMode(this.value);updateShutterIrisState()\">\r\n                                            <!-- v7.35: 从 function.json 动态加载 -->\r\n                                        </select>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- 快门/光圈整合一行 -->\r\n                                    <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:4px\">\r\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">\r\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">快门</label>\r\n                                            <select id=\"shutterSpeed\" style=\"width:100%;padding:3px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:11px\" onchange=\"setShutterSpeed(this.value)\" disabled>\r\n                                                <option value=\"\">--</option>\r\n                                            </select>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">\r\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">光圈</label>\r\n                                            <select id=\"irisLevel\" style=\"width:100%;padding:3px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:11px\" onchange=\"setIris(this.value)\" disabled>\r\n                                                <option value=\"\">--</option>\r\n                                            </select>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- v7.03: 增益控制 -->\r\n                                    <div style=\"margin-bottom:8px\">\r\n                                        <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">增益 <span id=\"gainVal\" style=\"color:#58a6ff\">--</span></label>\r\n\n[1360 more lines in file. Use offset=318 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783118451918}}
