{"type":"message","id":"0597fa01","parentId":"047db4f6","timestamp":"2026-07-03T22:41:58.623Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to continue. Let me check what I was doing - I had just finished all the modifications and updates. Let me provide a summary of what was done.\n\nAll the changes have been completed:\n1. ✅ Left panel (motion control): PTZ OSD switch replaces focus controls\n2. ✅ Right panel (image controls): restructured with noise reduction moved, white balance/focus mode changed to 3 options\n3. ✅ JavaScript updated with new functions\n4. ✅ Version number updated to v8.38\n5. ✅ HEARTBEAT.md updated\n\nI should now provide a summary to the user.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"所有修改已完成。以下是变更摘要：\n\n## v8.38 主控台界面重构（2026-07-04）\n\n### 左侧面板（运动控制）\n- **PTZ OSD开关** → 替代原变焦/对焦区\n\n### 右侧面板（画面控制）布局顺序\n| 位置 | 内容 |\n|------|------|\n| 1 | 亮度 | 对比度 |\n| 2 | 饱和度 | 锐度 |\n| 3 | **空域降噪** | **时域降噪** ← 已从白平衡下方移至此处 |\n| 4 | **白平衡模式**（自动/手动/局部） |\n| 5 | R/B滑动条（仅手动显示） |\n| 6 | 局部白平衡控制（框选+定时，仅局部显示） |\n| 7 | **对焦模式**（自动/手动/局部） |\n| 8 | 焦点移动按钮（远/近，仅手动显示） |\n| 9 | 局部对焦控制（框选+定时，仅局部显示） |\n| 10 | 曝光模式 + 快门/光圈 |\n| 11 | 增益 |\n| 12 | OSD控制（仅信息开关，PTZ已移至左侧） |\n\n### 白平衡/对焦模式逻辑\n- **自动**：隐藏所有附加控件\n- **手动**：显示R/B滑动条或焦点移动按钮\n- **局部**：显示框选按钮 + 定时输入框（分钟），点击\"停止\"可终止自动执行\n\n### 备份位置\n`backup_20260704_0607/console.html`"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":110442,"output":539,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":110981,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783118497270,"responseId":"cht000dca55@dx19f2a251c2e2871503"}}
