{"type":"message","id":"db35b86c","parentId":"6230ba6d","timestamp":"2026-07-03T23:01:12.851Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**22项测试全部通过，0失败。**\n\n```\n============================================================\nPlaywright E2E - v8.38 UI Test\n============================================================\n\nPASS: 22\n  [PASS] 测试1: 左侧面板 PTZ OSD 开关存在\n  [PASS] 测试2: 左侧面板变焦/对焦区已移除（无focusMode select）\n  [PASS] 测试3: 左侧面板焦距按钮已移除\n  [PASS] 测试4: 白平衡下拉选项正确: ['auto', 'manual', 'local']\n  [PASS] 测试5: 白平衡R/B滑动条默认隐藏\n  [PASS] 测试6: 白平衡局部控制默认隐藏\n  [PASS] 测试7: 白平衡手动模式 → R/B滑动条显示\n  [PASS] 测试8: 白平衡局部模式 → 局部控制显示\n  [PASS] 测试9: 白平衡自动模式 → 所有附加控件隐藏\n  [PASS] 测试10: 对焦下拉选项正确: ['auto', 'manual', 'local']\n  [PASS] 测试11: 对焦焦点移动按钮默认隐藏\n  [PASS] 测试12: 对焦手动模式 → 焦点移动按钮显示\n  [PASS] 测试13: 对焦局部模式 → 局部控制显示\n  [PASS] 测试14: 对焦自动模式 → 所有附加控件隐藏\n  [PASS] 测试15: 降噪位于饱和度下方，白平衡位于降噪下方\n  [PASS] 测试16: 画面控制区已移除PTZ OSD开关\n  [PASS] 测试17: 画面控制区保留信息OSD开关\n  [PASS] 测试18: 右侧面板元素顺序正确（亮度→饱和度→降噪→白平衡→对焦→曝光→增益）\n  [PASS] 测试19: 白平衡定时输入框可修改值（0→5）\n  [PASS] 测试20: 白平衡定时输入框 min=0（0=不执行定时）\n  [PASS] 测试21: 对焦定时输入框可修改值且min=0\n  [PASS] 测试22: 所有JS函数已定义\n\nFAIL: 0\nTotal: 22 passed / 0 failed\n============================================================\n```\n\n2个 Console 404 是 WASM SDK 资源未加载（无设备连接时正常），与本次修改无关。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":100212,"output":526,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":100738,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783119661964,"responseId":"cht000d4c1a@dx19f2a36d0f729bb503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2c346875","parentId":"db35b86c","timestamp":"2026-07-04T13:36:41.032Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"45708\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-07-04 21:36 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n你这次修改有很多致命bug，按照以下要求，修复bug，禁止过度开发，备份后迭代版本号，不允许打补丁绕弯子。遍历代码，区分哪些需要前端实现，哪些需要后端\n1. 把运动控制中预置点下方的“归位”按钮，删除，将PTZ的方向按键中间的停止键改成归位，也就是回到10号预置点HOME\n2. 运动控制中的OSD这一栏，标题改成“信息显示”，下方依然需要保留之前移动的两个开关，OSD和PTZ，这两个需要读取真实状态获取开关状态\n3. 媒体操作中的“框选分析”删除\n4. 画面控制中，信息 osd开关删除。\n5. 白平衡模式改成“白平衡”，当点击局部的时候，自动切换到内置的手动挡，并且删除局部框选白平衡之前必须要设置手动模式的前置要求。\n6. 对焦的修改，同白平衡，当点击局部的时候，自动切换到内置的手动挡，并且删除局部框选对焦之前必须要设置手动模式的前置要求。\n7. 定时功能，是需要记忆选区的，保留使用上一次的选区，但是注意，白平衡和对焦，这两个选取是不一样的。"}],"timestamp":1783172201026}}
{"type":"message","id":"25583f87","parentId":"2c346875","timestamp":"2026-07-04T13:37:10.624Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me analyze the requirements carefully:\n\n1. Delete \"归位\" button below presets in motion control, change the center stop button in PTZ direction controls to \"归位\" (go to preset 10 HOME)\n\n2. Change OSD title to \"信息显示\", keep both OSD and PTZ switches, read real status for switch state\n\n3. Delete \"框选分析\" section from media controls\n\n4. Delete info OSD switch from image controls (right panel)\n\n5. White balance: rename to \"白平衡\", when \"局部\" is selected, auto-switch to manual mode internally, remove the prerequisite of setting manual mode before local white balance\n\n6. Focus: same as white balance - auto-switch to manual when local is selected, remove prerequisite\n\n7. Timer function needs to remember the selection region - persist last region for WB and focus separately\n\nLet me first read the current state of the files to understand what needs to change.\n\nI need to:\n1. Read console.html for current structure\n2. Read index.html for ptzHome, toggleRegionMode, and related functions\n3. Read router.py for backend endpoints\n\nLet me start by reading the relevant files.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"先遍历代码，搞清前后端职责。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_eca51afb5d8d4ef3ae213023","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":100,"offset":1,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":101160,"output":297,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":101457,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783172201040,"responseId":"cht000dea5f@dx19f2d58beab29c2503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"23e7156b","parentId":"25583f87","timestamp":"2026-07-04T13:37:10.665Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_eca51afb5d8d4ef3ae213023","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        <div class=\"page\" id=\"page-console\">\r\n            <div id=\"consoleWarning\" style=\"display:none;position:fixed;top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%, -50%);background:#4a3a1a;border:2px solid #d29922;border-radius:12px;padding:32px 48px;color:#d29922;font-size:16px;z-index:10000;text-align:center;width:300px\">\r\n                <strong style=\"font-size:20px\">⚠️ 请连接设备</strong><br><br>\r\n                <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:14px\">在设备管理页面连接设备</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div id=\"ptzControlArea\">\r\n                <!-- 左右布局: 左控制, 中间画面+媒体, 右日志+画面控制 -->\r\n                <div class=\"console-layout\">\r\n                    <!-- 左: PTZ控制(整合:指向+预置点+变焦/对焦) -->\r\n                    <div class=\"console-left\">\r\n                        <!-- PTZ控制(折叠) -->\r\n                        <div class=\"collapsible-section\" id=\"ptzControlSection\">\r\n                            <div class=\"collapsible-header\" onclick=\"toggleSection('ptzControlSection')\">\r\n                                <h3 style=\"font-size:15px;color:#58a6ff;margin:0\">🎯 运动控制</h3>\r\n                                <span class=\"collapse-icon\">▼</span>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"collapsible-content\">\r\n                                <!-- 指向控制 + 信息展示 -->\r\n                                <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:stretch\">\r\n                                    <!-- 左侧:方向控制 + 速度 -->\r\n                                    <div style=\"flex:0 0 auto;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:space-between\">\r\n                                        <div class=\"ptz-controls\">\r\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('up-left')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('up-left')\">↖</button>\r\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('up')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('up')\">↑</button>\r\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('up-right')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('up-right')\">↗</button>\r\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('left')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('left')\">←</button>\r\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn center\">●</button>\r\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('right')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('right')\">→</button>\r\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('down-left')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('down-left')\">↙</button>\r\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('down')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('down')\">↓</button>\r\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('down-right')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('down-right')\">↘</button>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div class=\"ptz-speed\" style=\"width:170px;font-size:11px;margin-top:8px\">\r\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px\">速度:</label>\r\n                                            <input type=\"range\" id=\"ptzSpeed\" min=\"1\" max=\"7\" value=\"4\" style=\"width:90px\">\r\n                                            <span id=\"ptzSpeedVal\" style=\"font-size:11px\">4</span>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- 右侧:光圈快门 + P/T/Z(竖排,宽度减少15%) -->\r\n                                    <div style=\"flex:0 0 110px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0\">\r\n                                        <div class=\"info-block\" style=\"flex:1\">\r\n                                            <div class=\"info-row\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;padding:1px 4px;font-size:12px\"><span class=\"info-label\">光圈</span><span class=\"info-value\" id=\"ptzIris\">--</span></div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"info-row\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;padding:1px 4px;font-size:12px\"><span class=\"info-label\">快门</span><span class=\"info-value\" id=\"ptzShutter\">--</span></div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"info-row\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;padding:1px 4px;font-size:12px\"><span class=\"info-label\">R</span><span class=\"info-value\" id=\"ptzWbR\">--</span></div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"info-row\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;padding:1px 4px;font-size:12px\"><span class=\"info-label\">B</span><span class=\"info-value\" id=\"ptzWbB\">--</span></div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"info-row\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;padding:1px 4px;font-size:12px\"><span class=\"info-label\">空域</span><span class=\"info-value\" id=\"ptzDnrSpatial\">--</span></div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"info-row\" style=\"padding:1px 4px;font-size:12px\"><span class=\"info-label\">时域</span><span class=\"info-value\" id=\"ptzDnrTemporal\">--</span></div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div style=\"border-top:2px solid #30363d;margin-top:2px;padding-top:2px\"></div>\r\n                                        <div class=\"info-block\" style=\"flex:1\">\r\n                                            <div class=\"info-row\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;padding:1px 4px;font-size:12px\"><span class=\"info-label\">Pan</span><span class=\"info-value\" id=\"ptzPan\">--</span></div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"info-row\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;padding:1px 4px;font-size:12px\"><span class=\"info-label\">Tilt</span><span class=\"info-value\" id=\"ptzTilt\">--</span></div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"info-row\" style=\"padding:1px 4px;font-size:12px\"><span class=\"info-label\">Zoom</span><span class=\"info-value\" id=\"ptzZoom\">--</span></div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <!-- 码流控制 -->\r\n                                <div class=\"section-subtitle\">码流</div>\r\n                                <div style=\"display:flex;gap:6px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:8px\">\r\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" id=\"btnStreamMain\" onclick=\"switchAndPlay(1)\" title=\"主码流\">主</button>\r\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" id=\"btnStreamSub\" onclick=\"switchAndPlay(2)\" title=\"子码流\">子</button>\r\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" id=\"btnStreamThird\" onclick=\"switchAndPlay(3)\" title=\"第三码流\">三</button>\r\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" id=\"btnStreamStop\" onclick=\"doStopPreview()\" title=\"停止预览\">⏹</button>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <!-- 预置点 -->\r\n                                <div class=\"section-subtitle\">预置点</div>\r\n                                <div style=\"display:flex;gap:4px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:8px\">\r\n                                    <select id=\"ptzPresetSelect\" style=\"padding:6px 8px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:6px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:13px;min-width:100px\">\r\n                                        <option value=\"\">选择预置点</option>\r\n                                    </select>\r\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" onclick=\"ptzGotoSelectedPreset()\">前往</button>\r\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" onclick=\"ptzWritePreset()\">写入</button>\r\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onclick=\"ptzHome()\">归位</button>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <!-- PTZ OSD 开关 -->\r\n                                <div class=\"section-subtitle\">OSD</div>\r\n                                <div style=\"display:flex;gap:6px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:8px\">\r\n                                    <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">PTZ OSD</span>\r\n                                    <label class=\"toggle-switch\">\r\n                                        <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"ptzOsdSwitchInPtz\" checked onchange=\"togglePtzOsdSwitch(this.checked)\">\r\n                                        <span class=\"toggle-slider\"></span>\r\n                                    </label>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <!-- 媒体信息(折叠,默认展开) -->\r\n                        <div class=\"collapsible-section\" id=\"mediaLogSection\" style=\"margin-top:12px\">\r\n                            <div class=\"collapsible-header\" onclick=\"toggleSection('mediaLogSection')\">\r\n                                <h3 style=\"font-size:15px;color:#58a6ff;margin:0\">📡 媒体信息</h3>\r\n                                <span class=\"collapse-icon\">▼</span>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"collapsible-content\">\r\n                                <div style=\"background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:8px;padding:8px;overflow-y:auto;height:200px\" class=\"hide-scrollbar\">\r\n                                    <div id=\"mediaLogBox\" style=\"font-size:11px;font-family:monospace;color:#8b949e\">\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <!-- 中: 实时画面 + 媒体操作 -->\r\n\n[1577 more lines in file. Use offset=101 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783172230665}}
{"type":"message","id":"36575a65","parentId":"23e7156b","timestamp":"2026-07-04T13:38:51.329Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me understand the current state:\n\n1. **Motion Control (Left Panel)**:\n   - PTZ Direction controls (9 buttons + center stop)\n   - Speed slider\n   - Info block (Iris, Shutter, R/B, Spatial DNR, Temporal DNR, Pan, Tilt, Zoom)\n   - Stream controls (Main/Sub/Third/Stop)\n   - Preset controls (Select + Go + Write + Home)\n   - OSD switch (single, PTZ only)\n\n2. **Media Controls (Center Panel)**:\n   - Region analysis buttons (WB + AF) - NEEDS TO BE DELETED\n\n3. **Image Controls (Right Panel)**:\n   - Brightness/Contrast\n   - Saturation/Sharpness\n   - Noise Reduction (moved up)\n   - WB Mode dropdown + manual/local controls\n   - Focus Mode dropdown + manual/local controls\n   - Exposure + Shutter/Iris\n   - Gain\n   - OSD controls (only Info switch now, PTZ removed)\n\nNow let me understand what needs to change:\n\n### Requirements Analysis:\n\n1. **Delete \"归位\" button below presets, change center stop to \"归位\"**\n   - This is FRONTEND - modify console.html\n   - Need to change the center PTZ button (●) from stop to home (go to preset 10)\n\n2. **Change OSD title to \"信息显示\", keep both OSD and PTZ switches, read real status**\n   - This is FRONTEND - need to check current togglePtzOsd function\n   - The function currently posts to backend to get status, but the switch is controlled by user click\n   - Need to verify this is working correctly\n\n3. **Delete \"框选分析\" from media controls**\n   - This is FRONTEND - delete the section in console.html\n\n4. **Delete info OSD switch from image controls (right panel)**\n   - This is FRONTEND - need to read the right panel code again since it was cut off\n\n5. **White balance change**: external prompt requires renaming \"白平衡模式\" to \"白平衡\", and switching to internal \"手动\" when \"局部\" is clicked, removing the prior requirement to manually set it beforehand.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"让我先备份，然后逐项分析前后端职责。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_994d0a731953473f93569ee4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"$backupDir = \"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\backup_$(Get-Date -Format 'yyyyMMdd_HHmmss')\"; New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $backupDir -Force | Out-Null; Copy-Item \"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html\" \"$backupDir\\console.html\"; Copy-Item \"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html\" \"$backupDir\\index.html\"; Write-Output \"Backup created at: $backupDir\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":103969,"output":627,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104596,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783172230667,"responseId":"cht000d916e@dx19f2d59aea529bb503"}}
