{"type":"message","id":"0baf9c0a","parentId":"529c0e6d","timestamp":"2026-07-04T13:41:10.509Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_3410f42d87ca47c4a946f02b","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[32;1mLineNumber[0m\r\n[32;1m----------[0m\r\n      1642\r\n      2871\r\n      2874\r\n      2879\r\n      2880\r\n      2907\r\n      2921\r\n      2934\r\n      3010\r\n      3027\r\n      3037\r\n      3047"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":364,"aggregated":"[32;1mLineNumber[0m\r\n[32;1m----------[0m\r\n      1642\r\n      2871\r\n      2874\r\n      2879\r\n      2880\r\n      2907\r\n      2921\r\n      2934\r\n      3010\r\n      3027\r\n      3037\r\n      3047","cwd":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1783172470509}}
{"type":"message","id":"d5d144a9","parentId":"0baf9c0a","timestamp":"2026-07-04T13:42:04.378Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8af51d3c122b493083c96170","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":200,"offset":2871,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":108870,"output":47,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":108917,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783172470511,"responseId":"cht000d1d90@dx19f2d5d576029bb503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"10f8264d","parentId":"d5d144a9","timestamp":"2026-07-04T13:42:04.419Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_8af51d3c122b493083c96170","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    var _regionMode = null;\r\n    var _regionStartX = 0, _regionStartY = 0;\r\n\r\n    function toggleRegionMode(mode) {\r\n        var btnWB = document.getElementById('btnRegionWB');\r\n        var btnAF = document.getElementById('btnRegionAF');\r\n        var overlay = document.getElementById('regionOverlay');\r\n        var box = document.getElementById('regionBox');\r\n        if (_regionMode === mode) {\r\n            _regionMode = null;\r\n            btnWB.className = 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n            btnAF.className = 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n            overlay.style.display = 'none';\r\n            box.style.display = 'none';\r\n            return;\r\n        }\r\n        if (!window.connectedDevice || !window.connectedDevice.ip) {\r\n            showToast('warning', '请先连接设备');\r\n            return;\r\n        }\r\n        // v8.10: 模式限制 - 白平衡仅手动模式可用\r\n        if (mode === 'whitebalance') {\r\n            var wbMode = document.getElementById('wbMode');\r\n            if (wbMode && wbMode.value !== 'manual') {\r\n                showToast('warning', '白平衡需切换为\"手动\"模式才能使用框选分析');\r\n                return;\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n        // v8.10: 模式限制 - 对焦仅手动模式可用\r\n        if (mode === 'focus') {\r\n            var fm = document.getElementById('focusMode');\r\n            if (fm && fm.value !== 'manual') {\r\n                showToast('warning', '对焦需切换为\"手动\"模式才能使用反差对焦');\r\n                return;\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n        _regionMode = mode;\r\n        btnWB.className = mode === 'whitebalance' ? 'btn btn-primary btn-sm' : 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n        btnAF.className = mode === 'focus' ? 'btn btn-primary btn-sm' : 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n        overlay.style.display = 'block';\r\n        box.style.display = 'none';\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    function _getOverlayPos(e) {\r\n        var overlay = document.getElementById('regionOverlay');\r\n        var rect = overlay.getBoundingClientRect();\r\n        return { x: e.clientX - rect.left, y: e.clientY - rect.top };\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    // v8.11: 统一 ISAPI 截图 → 后端裁剪 → 迭代搜索 → 操作日志\r\n    function _finishRegion() {\r\n        var overlay = document.getElementById('regionOverlay');\r\n        var box = document.getElementById('regionBox');\r\n        var dev = window.connectedDevice;\r\n        if (!dev || !dev.ip) { showToast('error', '未连接设备'); _resetRegionUI(); return; }\r\n\r\n        var ow = overlay.offsetWidth, oh = overlay.offsetHeight;\r\n        var sx = parseInt(box.style.left) / ow;\r\n        var sy = parseInt(box.style.top) / oh;\r\n        var sw = parseInt(box.style.width) / ow;\r\n        var sh = parseInt(box.style.height) / oh;\r\n        if (sw < 0.01 || sh < 0.01) { showToast('warning', '框选区域太小'); _resetRegionUI(); return; }\r\n\r\n        var mode = _regionMode;\r\n        var endpoint = mode === 'whitebalance' ? '/api/v1/vision/whitebalance-search'\r\n                                               : '/api/v1/vision/focus-search';\r\n        var label = mode === 'whitebalance' ? '白平衡' : '对焦';\r\n\r\n        _resetRegionUI();\r\n        showToast('info', label + '迭代中...');\r\n        operationLog('── ' + label + '迭代开始 ──', 'info');\r\n\r\n        // SSE 流式调用\r\n        var body = JSON.stringify({ x: sx, y: sy, w: sw, h: sh });\r\n        fetch(endpoint, { method: 'POST', headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' }, body: body })\r\n            .then(function(resp) {\r\n                if (!resp.ok) throw new Error('HTTP ' + resp.status);\r\n                var reader = resp.body.getReader();\r\n                var decoder = new TextDecoder();\r\n                var buf = '';\r\n                function pump() {\r\n                    return reader.read().then(function(r) {\r\n                        if (r.done) return;\r\n                        buf += decoder.decode(r.value, { stream: true });\r\n                        // 按 \\n\\n 分割事件\r\n                        var parts = buf.split('\\n\\n');\r\n                        buf = parts.pop();  // 最后一段可能不完整\r\n                        for (var i = 0; i < parts.length; i++) {\r\n                            var line = parts[i];\r\n                            if (!line.startsWith('data: ')) continue;\r\n                            try {\r\n                                var ev = JSON.parse(line.slice(6));\r\n                                if (ev.type === 'start') {\r\n                                    operationLog(label + '开始, ' + ev.crop, 'info');\r\n                                } else if (ev.type === 'wb') {\r\n                                    operationLog('调整 #' + ev.step + ': ' + ev.stage\r\n                                        + ' R=' + ev.red_gain + ' B=' + ev.blue_gain\r\n                                        + ' → R=' + ev.r_avg + ' G=' + ev.g_avg + ' B=' + ev.b_avg\r\n                                        + ' (Δ=' + ev.delta + ')', 'debug');\r\n                                } else if (ev.type === 'focus') {\r\n                                    operationLog('对焦 #' + ev.step + ': ' + ev.stage\r\n                                        + ' ' + ev.action + ' 反差=' + ev.contrast\r\n                                        + ' (' + ev.duration + 's) ' + ev.message, 'debug');\r\n                                } else if (ev.type === 'done') {\r\n                                    if (ev.final_red !== undefined) {\r\n                                        showToast('success', label + '完成 R=' + ev.final_red + ' B=' + ev.final_blue);\r\n                                        operationLog('── ' + label + '完成: R=' + ev.final_red + ' B=' + ev.final_blue + ' (' + ev.total_steps + '步) ──', 'success');\r\n                                        // 刷新主控台白平衡滑动条\r\n                                        var wbRed = document.getElementById('wbRed');\r\n                                        var wbBlue = document.getElementById('wbBlue');\r\n                                        var wbRedVal = document.getElementById('wbRedVal');\r\n                                        var wbBlueVal = document.getElementById('wbBlueVal');\r\n                                        if (wbRed) { wbRed.value = ev.final_red; if (wbRedVal) wbRedVal.textContent = ev.final_red; }\r\n                                        if (wbBlue) { wbBlue.value = ev.final_blue; if (wbBlueVal) wbBlueVal.textContent = ev.final_blue; }\r\n                                    } else {\r\n                                        var rollMsg = ev.rollback_steps ? ' (回滚' + ev.rollback_steps + '步)' : '';\r\n                                        showToast('success', label + '完成 反差=' + ev.final_contrast + rollMsg);\r\n                                        operationLog('── ' + label + '完成: 反差=' + ev.final_contrast + rollMsg + ' (' + ev.total_steps + '步) ──', 'success');\r\n                                    }\r\n                                } else if (ev.type === 'cleanup') {\r\n                                    operationLog('清理完成', 'info');\r\n                                } else if (ev.type === 'error') {\r\n                                    operationLog(label + '失败: ' + ev.message, 'error');\r\n                                    showToast('error', label + '失败');\r\n                                }\r\n                            } catch(e) { /* 跳过损坏的 JSON */ }\r\n                        }\r\n                        return pump();\r\n                    });\r\n                }\r\n                return pump();\r\n            })\r\n            .catch(function(e) {\r\n                operationLog(label + '异常: ' + e.message, 'error');\r\n                showToast('error', '异常: ' + e.message);\r\n            });\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    function _resetRegionUI() {\r\n        _regionMode = null;\r\n        var btnWB = document.getElementById('btnRegionWB');\r\n        var btnAF = document.getElementById('btnRegionAF');\r\n        var overlay = document.getElementById('regionOverlay');\r\n        var box = document.getElementById('regionBox');\r\n        if (btnWB) btnWB.className = 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n        if (btnAF) btnAF.className = 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n        if (overlay) overlay.style.display = 'none';\r\n        if (box) box.style.display = 'none';\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    (function() {\r\n        var overlay = document.getElementById('regionOverlay');\r\n        if (!overlay) return;\r\n        var box = document.getElementById('regionBox');\r\n        var isDragging = false;\r\n        overlay.addEventListener('mousedown', function(e) {\r\n            if (!_regionMode) return;\r\n            var pos = _getOverlayPos(e);\r\n            _regionStartX = pos.x; _regionStartY = pos.y;\r\n            box.style.left = pos.x + 'px'; box.style.top = pos.y + 'px';\r\n            box.style.width = '0px'; box.style.height = '0px';\r\n            box.style.display = 'block';\r\n            isDragging = true;\r\n            e.preventDefault();\r\n        });\r\n        overlay.addEventListener('mousemove', function(e) {\r\n            if (!isDragging || !_regionMode) return;\r\n            var pos = _getOverlayPos(e);\r\n            var x = Math.min(_regionStartX, pos.x);\r\n            var y = Math.min(_regionStartY, pos.y);\r\n            var w = Math.abs(pos.x - _regionStartX);\r\n            var h = Math.abs(pos.y - _regionStartY);\r\n            box.style.left = x + 'px'; box.style.top = y + 'px';\r\n            box.style.width = w + 'px'; box.style.height = h + 'px';\r\n        });\r\n        overlay.addEventListener('mouseup', function(e) {\r\n            if (!isDragging || !_regionMode) return;\r\n            isDragging = false;\r\n            _finishRegion();\r\n        });\r\n        overlay.addEventListener('mouseleave', function() {\r\n            if (isDragging) { isDragging = false; _finishRegion(); }\r\n        });\r\n    })();\r\n\r\n    </script>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783172524419}}
{"type":"message","id":"31a2f2e8","parentId":"10f8264d","timestamp":"2026-07-04T13:42:45.960Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Perfect. Now I understand the current implementation:\n\n1. **toggleRegionMode(mode)** - Frontend function that:\n   - Validates that device is connected\n   - Checks if mode is already active, and if so, disables it\n   - **BUG**: Has mode restrictions - whitebalance/focus only work in manual mode\n   - Shows the overlay for region selection\n   - Sets the active mode\n\n2. **_finishRegion()** - Frontend function that:\n   - Gets the selected region coordinates\n   - POSTs to backend vision endpoints (whitebalance-search or focus-search)\n   - Handles SSE stream from backend\n   - Updates UI based on backend response\n\n3. **Backend endpoints** - Need to check router.py:\n   - `/api/v1/vision/whitebalance-search`\n   - `/api/v1/vision/focus-search`\n\nNow let me check the backend router.py for these endpoints:","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"现在让我查询 `router.py` 中的后端端点："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8e69db31a4944756a7a909b8","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path \"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py\" -Pattern \"_whitebalance_search|_focus_search\" | Select-Object LineNumber"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":111252,"output":259,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111511,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783172524421,"responseId":"cht000d09bf@dx19f2d5d7ddf2872503"}}
