{"type":"message","id":"d64932b6","parentId":"52103cbd","timestamp":"2026-07-04T13:45:04.700Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_2cf5d485ba3a498c81a90cfb","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\r\n    stats = _rgb_stats(bgr)\r\n    contrast = calc_contrast(bgr)\r\n    return {\"success\": True, \"crop\": info, \"rgb\": stats, \"contrast\": round(contrast, 2)}\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.post(\"/vision/whitebalance-search\", summary=\"白平衡迭代搜索 (SSE)\", tags=[\"Vision\"])\r\nasync def whitebalance_search(data: dict):\r\n    \"\"\"白平衡迭代搜索 - SSE流式。路由层只验证输入和调用白平衡模块。\"\"\"\r\n    import json\r\n    from fastapi.responses import StreamingResponse\r\n    from src.controlpanel.whitebalance import WhiteBalanceSearcher\r\n\r\n    mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return StreamingResponse(\r\n            iter([f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'error', 'message': 'PTZ控制器未初始化'})}\\n\\n\"]),\r\n            media_type=\"text/event-stream\"\r\n        )\r\n\r\n    connected = mgr.get_connected_device()\r\n    if not connected:\r\n        return StreamingResponse(\r\n            iter([f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'error', 'message': '无活跃设备'})}\\n\\n\"]),\r\n            media_type=\"text/event-stream\"\r\n        )\r\n\r\n    device_ip = connected[\"ip\"]\r\n    client, err = _get_client_for_device(mgr, device_ip)\r\n    if err:\r\n\n[157 more lines in file. Use offset=3900 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783172704700}}
{"type":"message","id":"c30686a9","parentId":"d64932b6","timestamp":"2026-07-04T13:46:20.075Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a better understanding of the architecture:\n\n**Frontend (index.html/console.html)**:\n- `toggleRegionMode(mode)` - Controls the region selection UI overlay\n- `_finishRegion()` - Posts to backend vision endpoints with region coordinates\n- Handles SSE stream for progress updates\n\n**Backend (router.py)**:\n- `/vision/whitebalance-search` - SSE endpoint for white balance iteration\n- `/vision/focus-search` - SSE endpoint for focus iteration\n- Uses `WhiteBalanceSearcher` and `FocusSearcher` from controlpanel module\n\n**Bug Analysis from User's Requirements**:\n\n1. **Delete \"归位\" button below presets, change center stop to \"归位\"**\n   - FRONTEND: console.html - line 75 has the \"归位\" button, line 19 has the center stop button (●)\n\n2. **Change OSD title to \"信息显示\", keep both OSD and PTZ switches, read real status**\n   - FRONTEND: console.html - current OSD section only has PTZ switch\n   - Need to add Info OSD switch AND read real status from backend\n   - The backend already has `/osd/ptz` and `/osd/info` endpoints\n\n3. **Delete \"框选分析\" from media controls**\n   - FRONTEND: console.html - lines 136-141 have the region selection buttons\n\n4. **Delete info OSD switch from image controls (right panel)**\n   - FRONTEND: console.html - lines 330-336 have the info OSD switch in image control section\n\n5. **White balance**: rename to \"白平衡\", when \"局部\" is clicked, auto-switch to manual internally, remove prerequisite of manual mode before region selection\n   - FRONTEND: index.html `toggleRegionMode` - has validation that wb/focus must be in manual mode (BUG!)\n   - Need to modify the logic: when user clicks \"局部\", automatically set the device to manual mode internally\n   \n6. **Focus**: same as white balance\n   - Same modification needed\n\n7. **Timer function needs to remember region selection**\n   - FRONTEND: Need to add localStorage to save/restore region coordinates for WB and Focus separately\n   - This is new functionality - not currently implemented\n\nWait, looking at requirement 2 more carefully:\n\n\"运动控制中的OSD这一栏，标题改成\"信息显示\"，下方依然需要保留之前移动的两个开关，OSD和PTZ，这两个需要读取真实状态获取开关状态\"\n\nThis means:\n- The OSD section in motion control should have TWO switches: OSD (Info) and PTZ\n- Both should read real status from backend\n\nBut in my previous v8.38 changes, I only moved PTZ OSD to motion control and removed Info OSD from image control. Now I need to:\n- Keep PTZ OSD in motion control\n- Add Info OSD back to motion control\n- Delete Info OSD from image control (already done)\n- Read real status for both\n\nLet me now plan all the changes:\n\n## Frontend Changes (console.html)\n\n1. **Motion Control - Direction Controls Center Button**\n   - Change `<button class=\"ptz-btn center\">●</button>` to `<button class=\"ptz-btn\" onclick=\"ptzHome()\">⏹</button>`\n   - Wait, the user wants \"归位\" not stop. So it should call ptzHome() which goes to preset 10.\n\n2. **Motion Control - Preset Section**\n   - Delete `<button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onclick=\"ptzHome()\">归位</button>`\n\n3. **Motion Control - OSD Section**\n   - Change title from \"OSD\" to \"信息显示\"\n   - Add both Info OSD and PTZ OSD switches\n   - Both should call backend to get real status on load\n\n4. **Media Controls - Delete Region Selection**\n   - Delete the \"框选分析\" section (lines 136-141)\n\n5. **Image Control - Delete Info OSD**\n   - Already deleted in v8.38 (confirmed from read above)\n\n6. **White Balance/Focus Mode Labels**\n   - Change \"白平衡模式\" to \"白平衡\"\n   - Change \"对焦模式\" to \"对焦\"\n\n## Frontend Changes (index.html)\n\n7. **toggleRegionMode - Remove Manual Mode Prerequisite**\n   - Delete the validation that checks wbMode/focusMode must be 'manual'\n   - When user clicks region selection, the backend will handle mode switching internally\n\n8. **Region Memory for Timer**\n   - Add localStorage to save region coordinates (x, y, w, h) separately for WB and Focus\n   - When user selects a region, save it\n   - When user starts timer, use the saved region\n\nWait, looking at requirement 7 more carefully:\n\n\"定时功能，是需要记忆选区的，保留使用上一次的选区，但是注意，白平衡和对焦，这两个选取是不一样的。\"\n\nThis means the timer function (which I added in v8.38 with wbTimerInput and focusTimerInput) needs to remember the region selection. Currently there's no implementation for the timer functionality - it's just an input field. This needs new backend implementation.\n\nActually, let me re-read the current implementation. The timer input was added but there's no actual functionality. The user wants:\n- When user does a region selection (框选), save the region coordinates\n- When user sets a timer value > 0, periodically execute the WB/Focus search using the saved region\n- WB and Focus regions should be stored separately\n\nThis requires both frontend and backend changes:\n- Frontend: Save region to localStorage after selection\n- Backend: New endpoint to handle scheduled/timer-based WB/Focus search\n\nBut wait, the user says \"禁止过度开发\". Let me focus on just the bugs that need fixing and implement the minimum necessary changes.\n\nLet me now make all the changes systematically.\n\nActually, let me re-read requirement 5 and 6:\n\n\"5. 白平衡模式改成\"白平衡\"，当点击局部的时候，自动切换到内置的手动挡，并且删除局部框选白平衡之前必须要设置手动模式的前置要求。\"\n\n\"6. 对焦的修改，同白平衡，当点击局部的时候，自动切换到内置的手动挡，并且删除局部框选对焦之前必须要设置手动模式的前置要求。\"\n\nThis means:\n- When user selects \"局部\" in WB dropdown, the frontend should automatically call setWhiteBalanceMode('manual') internally\n- When user selects \"局部\" in Focus dropdown, the frontend should automatically call setFocusMode('manual') internally\n- Remove the prerequisite check in toggleRegionMode that requires manual mode before region selection\n\nThe idea is that \"局部\" mode is essentially using manual mode internally but with region selection capability. The user doesn't need to manually switch to manual mode first.\n\nLet me now implement all changes.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"现在我理解了架构。让我列出前后端职责分工：\n\n## 前后端职责分析\n\n| 需求 | 前端 | 后端 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 1. 归位按钮移至中心 | console.html 修改按钮 | 无需修改 |\n| 2. OSD标题+双开关 | console.html 添加Info开关+读状态 | 无需修改（已有端点） |\n| 3. 删除框选分析 | console.html 删除区块 | 无需修改 |\n| 4. 删除右侧Info开关 | console.html（已删除） | 无需修改 |\n| 5. 白平衡局部自动手动 | index.html `onWbModeChange` 调用setWhiteBalanceMode('manual') | 无需修改 |\n| 6. 对焦局部自动手动 | index.html `onFocusModeChange` 调用setFocusMode('manual') | 无需修改 |\n| 7. 定时记忆选区 | index.html localStorage 保存选区坐标 | 无需修改（定时功能待后续实现） |\n\n开始修改。先更新版本号："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-70db9e0089d146c9a29eda3d4eac19c7","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"VERSION = \"v8.39\"","oldText":"VERSION = \"v8.38\""}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\main\\constants.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":111982,"output":1740,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":113722,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783172704702,"responseId":"cht000d9458@dx19f2d609a9d29bb503"}}
