{"type":"message","id":"6a5df7e8","parentId":"414b1231","timestamp":"2026-07-04T13:54:55.628Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"控件列表中已包含 'ptzOsdSwitchInPtz'，但还保留旧的 'infoOsdSwitch'。需要改为：'infoOsdSwitchInPtz', 'ptzOsdSwitchInPtz'，并删除右侧 panel 的旧 'ptzOsdSwitch'（页面结构中已无右侧 OSD）。等一下，disableImageControls 中不应包含 info/ptz OSD（因为它们在 Motion Control）。需要从列表中移除。等等，disableImageControls 是“画面控制区禁用”，但 info/ptz OSD 已经移到 motor control group，应该从列表中移除，而不是 disability 相关机制。当前列了 'infoOsdSwitch', 'ptzOsdSwitchInPtz'（无 ptzOsdSwitch）。如果信息 or PTZ OSD 现在不在 imageControlsSection，不应纳入 disableImageControls，而仍需处理 disableImageControls 中只禁用画面控制相关控件。需要：\n- 确认 infoOsdSwitch 有可能是引用同一 ID（site-wide），或是特指某个地方的开关。按需求2，左侧 motion control 应新增 infoOsdSwitchInPtz。\n- 关键依据：updatePtzOsdButtons 中仍在读取旧 ptzOsdSwitch。需要在新函数中同步两个。\n- disableImageControls 的目的：禁用画面控制区的输入控件，不该包含 OSD。考虑到代码整洁，应从列表移除 infoOsdSwitch/ptzOsdSwitchInPtz，并在 enableImageControls/ refreshImageControls 中进行设备初始化与状态读取（已有 loadOsdStatus 调 loadWhiteBalance 等在调用时机上）。\n\n可执行项：\n1. disable/enableImageControls：将 'infoOsdSwitch', 'ptzOsdSwitchInPtz' 从 controls 列表中移除（不引入新的 ID）。\n2. updatePtzOsdButtons：增加本地 infoOsdEnabled 状态变量，同步 ptzOsdSwitch 与 ptzOsdSwitchInPtz。\n3. loadOsdStatus：分别读取后端 /osd/info 与 /osd/ptz，更新两个开关（IDs 为 infoOsdSwitchInPtz / ptzOsdSwitchInPtz）。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"将对 disable/enable 控件列表中的 OSD 条目移除：\n- disableImageControls 与 enableImageControls 的 controls 列表中不再包含 infoOsdSwitch / ptzOsdSwitchInPtz\n- loadOsdStatus 中通过后端端点获取 infoOsd 与 ptzOsd 的真实状态，分别写入 infoOsdSwitchInPtz 与 ptzOsdSwitchInPtz\n- updatePtzOsdButtons 中新增本地 infoOsdEnabled 并同步两个开关\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_bd76aee93fc546e09a5714b6","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"    // v7.11: 禁用画面控制控件（不包括 OSD 开关，它们在运动控制）\n    var controls = [\n        'consoleBrightness', 'consoleContrast', 'consoleSaturation', 'consoleSharpness',\n        'wbMode', 'wbRed', 'wbBlue', 'dnrSpatial', 'dnrTemporal',\n        'exposureMode', 'shutterSpeed', 'irisLevel', 'gainLevel',\n    ];","oldText":"    // v7.11: 禁用画面控制控件（包括增益）\n    var controls = [\n        'consoleBrightness', 'consoleContrast', 'consoleSaturation', 'consoleSharpness',\n        'wbMode', 'wbRed', 'wbBlue', 'dnrSpatial', 'dnrTemporal',\n        'exposureMode', 'shutterSpeed', 'irisLevel', 'gainLevel',  // v7.11: 添加 gainLevel\n        'infoOsdSwitch', 'ptzOsdSwitchInPtz'\n    ];"},{"newText":"    // v7.11: 启用画面控制控件（不包括 OSD 开关，它们在运动控制）\n    var controls = [\n        'consoleBrightness', 'consoleContrast', 'consoleSaturation', 'consoleSharpness',\n        'wbMode', 'wbRed', 'wbBlue', 'dnrSpatial', 'dnrTemporal',\n        'exposureMode', 'shutterSpeed', 'irisLevel', 'gainLevel',\n    ];","oldText":"    // v7.11: 启用画面控制控件（包括增益）\n    var controls = [\n        'consoleBrightness', 'consoleContrast', 'consoleSaturation', 'consoleSharpness',\n        'wbMode', 'wbRed', 'wbBlue', 'dnrSpatial', 'dnrTemporal',\n        'exposureMode', 'shutterSpeed', 'irisLevel', 'gainLevel',  // v7.11: 添加 gainLevel\n        'infoOsdSwitch', 'ptzOsdSwitchInPtz'\n    ];"},{"newText":"// PTZ OSD (ptzOsdEnabled)\nvar ptzOsdEnabled = false;\n// Info OSD (infoOsdEnabled)\nvar infoOsdEnabled = false;\n\nfunction updatePtzOsdButtons(enabled) {\n    var switchEl = document.getElementById('ptzOsdSwitchInPtz');\n    if (switchEl) {\n        switchEl.checked = enabled;\n    }\n    ptzOsdEnabled = enabled;\n}","oldText":"function updatePtzOsdButtons(enabled) {\n    var switchEl = document.getElementById('ptzOsdSwitchInPtz');\n    if (switchEl) {\n        switchEl.checked = enabled;\n    }\n    ptzOsdEnabled = enabled;\n}"},{"newText":"// 加载 OSD 状态\nfunction loadOsdStatus(deviceIp) {\n    // Info OSD\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/osd/info').then(function(r) {\n        if (r && r.success) {\n            var enabled = r.enabled || r.data?.enabled || false;\n            var infoSwitch = document.getElementById('infoOsdSwitchInPtz');\n            if (infoSwitch) {\n                infoSwitch.checked = enabled;\n            }\n            infoOsdEnabled = enabled;\n        }\n    }).catch(function(e) {\n        var saved = localStorage.getItem('osd_info_' + deviceIp);\n        if (saved !== null) {\n            var infoSwitch = document.getElementById('infoOsdSwitchInPtz');\n            if (infoSwitch) infoSwitch.checked = saved === '1';\n        }\n    });\n\n    // PTZ OSD\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/osd/ptz').then(function(r) {\n        if (r && r.success) {\n            var enabled = r.enabled || r.data?.enabled || false;\n            var ptzSwitch = document.getElementById('ptzOsdSwitchInPtz');\n            if (ptzSwitch) {\n                ptzSwitch.checked = enabled;\n            }\n            ptzOsdEnabled = enabled;\n        } else {\n            var saved = localStorage.getItem('osd_ptz_' + deviceIp);\n            if (saved !== null) {\n                var ptzSwitch = document.getElementById('ptzOsdSwitchInPtz');\n                if (ptzSwitch) ptzSwitch.checked = saved === '1';\n            }\n        }\n    }).catch(function(e) {\n        var saved = localStorage.getItem('osd_ptz_' + deviceIp);\n        if (saved !== null) {\n            var ptzSwitch = document.getElementById('ptzOsdSwitchInPtz');\n            if (ptzSwitch) ptzSwitch.checked = saved === '1';\n        }\n    });\n}","oldText":"// 加载 OSD 状态\nfunction loadOsdStatus(deviceIp) {\n    // PTZ OSD\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/osd/ptz').then(function(r) {\n        if (r && r.success) {\n            var enabled = r.enabled || r.data?.enabled || false;\n            updatePtzOsdButtons(enabled);\n            localStorage.setItem('osd_ptz_' + deviceIp, enabled ? '1' : '0');\n        } else {\n            var saved = localStorage.getItem('osd_ptz_' + deviceIp);\n            if (saved !== null) {\n                updatePtzOsdButtons(saved === '1');\n            }\n        }\n    }).catch(function(e) {\n        var saved = localStorage.getItem('osd_ptz_' + deviceIp);\n        if (saved !== null) {\n            updatePtzOsdButtons(saved === '1');\n        }\n    });\n    // Info OSD\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/osd/info').then(function(r) {\n        if (r && r.success) {\n            var enabled = r.enabled || r.data?.enabled || false;\n            updateInfoOsdButtons(enabled);\n            localStorage.setItem('osd_info_' + deviceIp, enabled ? '1' : '0');\n        } else {\n            var saved = localStorage.getItem('osd_info_' + deviceIp);\n            if (saved !== null) {\n                updateInfoOsdButtons(saved === '1');\n            }\n        }\n    }).catch(function(e) {\n        var saved = localStorage.getItem('osd_info_' + deviceIp);\n        if (saved !== null) {\n            updateInfoOsdButtons(saved === '1');\n        }\n    });\n}"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":116930,"output":2156,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":119086,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783173127979,"responseId":"cht000df111@dx19f2d66a84e29c2503"}}
