{"type":"message","id":"337346b6","parentId":"1d7b33b7","timestamp":"2026-07-04T14:26:32.113Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"老板明确说：只是\"OSD这一栏的标题改成信息显示\"，不需要我添加 Info OSD 开关。\n\n让我回顾一下当前的运动控制 OSD 部分：\n```html\n<!-- PTZ OSD 开关 -->\n<div class=\"section-subtitle\">OSD</div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;gap:6px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:8px\">\n    <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">PTZ OSD</span>\n    <label class=\"toggle-switch\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"ptzOsdSwitchInPtz\" checked onchange=\"togglePtzOsdSwitch(this.checked)\">\n        <span class=\"toggle-slider\"></span>\n    </label>\n</div>\n```\n\n老板的要求只是把 `<!-- PTZ OSD 开关 -->` 这行注释和 `<div class=\"section-subtitle\">OSD</div>` 改成\"信息显示\"。\n\n目前的修改状态：\n1. ✅ 中心停止键改为归位（⌂），删除预置点\"归位\"按钮\n2. ✅ 媒体控制删除\"框选分析\"\n3. ✅ 右侧面板 OSD 删除（v8.38 已完成）\n4. ✅ 白平衡/对焦标签改名\n5. ⚠️ 运动控制 OSD 标题只改\"信息显示\"（还未改）\n\n\n6. ❌ loadOsdStatus 和 updatePtzOsdButtons 待确认\n7. ❌ index.html 的模式限制和 auto 切手动待确认\n\n我将按照老板指示，简单调整 OSD 标题。下一步是检查 index.html 中涉及模式限制的代码，确保删除相关限制，并实现 auto 切换到手动模式的功能。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"明白！老板，我现在按你的要求简单修改：\n\n**修改2（仅改标题）**：把运动控制 OSD 这一行标题的 \"OSD\" 改成\"信息显示\"，保持现在的 PTZ OSD 单开关。\n\n让我改这一行："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f927aad7e1174140a0ee959b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path \"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html\" -Pattern \"PTZ OSD 开关|section-subtitle.*OSD\" | Select-Object LineNumber"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":124537,"output":492,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":125029,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783175055453,"responseId":"cht000d905a@dx19f2d84af262872503"}}
