{"type":"message","id":"42416ba6","parentId":"baaebeab","timestamp":"2026-07-04T14:32:09.824Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5d855f2e3763464bbb03a1f8","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    var _regionMode = null;\r\n    var _regionStartX = 0, _regionStartY = 0;\r\n\r\n    function toggleRegionMode(mode) {\r\n        var btnWB = document.getElementById('btnRegionWB');\r\n        var btnAF = document.getElementById('btnRegionAF');\r\n        var overlay = document.getElementById('regionOverlay');\r\n        var box = document.getElementById('regionBox');\r\n        if (_regionMode === mode) {\r\n            _regionMode = null;\r\n            btnWB.className = 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n            btnAF.className = 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n            overlay.style.display = 'none';\r\n            box.style.display = 'none';\r\n            return;\r\n        }\r\n        if (!window.connectedDevice || !window.connectedDevice.ip) {\r\n            showToast('warning', '请先连接设备');\r\n            return;\r\n        }\r\n        // v8.10: 模式限制 - 白平衡仅手动模式可用\r\n        if (mode === 'whitebalance') {\r\n            var wbMode = document.getElementById('wbMode');\r\n            if (wbMode && wbMode.value !== 'manual') {\r\n                showToast('warning', '白平衡需切换为\"手动\"模式才能使用框选分析');\r\n                return;\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n        // v8.10: 模式限制 - 对焦仅手动模式可用\r\n        if (mode === 'focus') {\r\n            var fm = document.getElementById('focusMode');\r\n            if (fm && fm.value !== 'manual') {\r\n                showToast('warning', '对焦需切换为\"手动\"模式才能使用反差对焦');\r\n                return;\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n        _regionMode = mode;\r\n        btnWB.className = mode === 'whitebalance' ? 'btn btn-primary btn-sm' : 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n        btnAF.className = mode === 'focus' ? 'btn btn-primary btn-sm' : 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n        overlay.style.display = 'block';\r\n\n[156 more lines in file. Use offset=2911 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783175529824}}
{"type":"message","id":"7467a22b","parentId":"42416ba6","timestamp":"2026-07-04T14:33:40.286Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到了需要删除的手动模式验证检查。还有 `btnRegionWB` 和 `btnRegionAF` 的引用，但那些按钮已经从 console.html 中删除了。让我也检查一下这些按钮是否还在 index.html 中。\n\n等等，老板要求删除\"框选分析\"部分，那是 `btnRegionWB` 和 `btnRegionAF` 按钮。但 `toggleRegionMode` 函数仍然引用它们。这意味着：\n\n1. 框选分析按钮已从媒体控制区删除\n2. 但白平衡/对焦局部模式仍然有\"框选\"按钮（在右侧面板）\n\n让我再读一下 console.html 中局部模式的框选按钮：\n\n```html\n<!-- 局部白平衡控制（仅局部模式显示） -->\n<div id=\"wbLocalControls\" style=\"display:none;margin-bottom:4px\">\n    <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:4px\">\n        <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" id=\"btnWbRegionSelect\" onclick=\"toggleRegionMode('whitebalance')\">框选</button>\n        ...\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- 局部对焦控制（仅局部模式显示） -->\n<div id=\"focusLocalControls\" style=\"display:none;margin-bottom:4px\">\n    <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:4px\">\n        <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" id=\"btnFocusRegionSelect\" onclick=\"toggleRegionMode('focus')\">框选</button>\n        ...\n    </div>\n</div>\n```\n\n我注意到按钮 ID 与 `toggleRegionMode` 函数中的引用不同。需要调整函数以匹配正确的按钮 ID。主要任务是：\n\n1. 移除手动模式验证\n2. 更新按钮 ID 引用\n3. 确保正确处理白平衡和对焦局部模式\n\n需要修改 `onWbModeChange` 和 `onFocusModeChange` 函数，实现自动模式切换。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"我看到了问题。`toggleRegionMode` 函数引用的是旧按钮 ID（`btnRegionWB`、`btnRegionAF`），但我已经删除了那些按钮。新的按钮 ID 是 `btnWbRegionSelect` 和 `btnFocusRegionSelect`。\n\n我需要：\n1. 更新 `toggleRegionMode` 使用正确的按钮 ID\n2. 移除手动模式先决条件\n3. 当模式为 'whitebalance' 或 'focus' 且不是手动时，自动设置为手动\n\n让我修复 `toggleRegionMode`："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0657eebd4ec94073bb76550f","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"    function toggleRegionMode(mode) {\n        // 新的按钮 ID（在白平衡/对焦局部控制中）\n        var btnWB = document.getElementById('btnWbRegionSelect');\n        var btnAF = document.getElementById('btnFocusRegionSelect');\n        var overlay = document.getElementById('regionOverlay');\n        var box = document.getElementById('regionBox');\n        if (_regionMode === mode) {\n            _regionMode = null;\n            if (btnWB) btnWB.className = 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\n            if (btnAF) btnAF.className = 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\n            overlay.style.display = 'none';\n            box.style.display = 'none';\n            return;\n        }\n        if (!window.connectedDevice || !window.connectedDevice.ip) {\n            showToast('warning', '请先连接设备');\n            return;\n        }\n        // v8.39: 移除手动模式限制 - 局部模式自动切换到手动\n        // 当选择局部框选时，自动切换到手动模式\n        if (mode === 'whitebalance') {\n            var wbMode = document.getElementById('wbMode');\n            if (wbMode && wbMode.value !== 'manual') {\n                // 自动切换到手动模式\n                setWhiteBalanceMode('manual');\n            }\n        }\n        if (mode === 'focus') {\n            var fm = document.getElementById('focusMode');\n            if (fm && fm.value !== 'manual') {\n                // 自动切换到手动模式\n                setFocusMode('manual');\n            }\n        }\n        _regionMode = mode;\n        if (btnWB) btnWB.className = mode === 'whitebalance' ? 'btn btn-primary btn-sm' : 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\n        if (btnAF) btnAF.className = mode === 'focus' ? 'btn btn-primary btn-sm' : 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\n        overlay.style.display = 'block';\n        box.style.display = 'none';\n    }","oldText":"    function toggleRegionMode(mode) {\n        var btnWB = document.getElementById('btnRegionWB');\n        var btnAF = document.getElementById('btnRegionAF');\n        var overlay = document.getElementById('regionOverlay');\n        var box = document.getElementById('regionBox');\n        if (_regionMode === mode) {\n            _regionMode = null;\n            btnWB.className = 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\n            btnAF.className = 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\n            overlay.style.display = 'none';\n            box.style.display = 'none';\n            return;\n        }\n        if (!window.connectedDevice || !window.connectedDevice.ip) {\n            showToast('warning', '请先连接设备');\n            return;\n        }\n        // v8.10: 模式限制 - 白平衡仅手动模式可用\n        if (mode === 'whitebalance') {\n            var wbMode = document.getElementById('wbMode');\n            if (wbMode && wbMode.value !== 'manual') {\n                showToast('warning', '白平衡需切换为\"手动\"模式才能使用框选分析');\n                return;\n            }\n        }\n        // v8.10: 模式限制 - 对焦仅手动模式可用\n        if (mode === 'focus') {\n            var fm = document.getElementById('focusMode');\n            if (fm && fm.value !== 'manual') {\n                showToast('warning', '对焦需切换为\"手动\"模式才能使用反差对焦');\n                return;\n            }\n        }\n        _regionMode = mode;\n        btnWB.className = mode === 'whitebalance' ? 'btn btn-primary btn-sm' : 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\n        btnAF.className = mode === 'focus' ? 'btn btn-primary btn-sm' : 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\n        overlay.style.display = 'block';\n        box.style.display = 'none';\n    }"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":127353,"output":1484,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":128837,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783175529826,"responseId":"cht000d5218@dx19f2d8c27b229bb503"}}
