{"type":"message","id":"1997b4eb","parentId":"b6db42de","timestamp":"2026-07-04T15:19:41.633Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"之后， PTZ OSD 开关在运动控制区，文本现在应该长成：\n```html\n<!-- PTZ OSD 开关 -->\n<div class=\"section-subtitle\">OSD</div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;gap:6px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:8px\">\n    <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">PTZ OSD</span>\n    <label class=\"toggle-switch\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"ptzOsdSwitchInPtz\" checked onchange=\"togglePtzOsdSwitch(this.checked)\">\n        <span class=\"toggle-slider\"></span>\n    </label>\n</div>\n```\n\n改为：\n\n```html\n<!-- 信息显示开关 -->\n<div class=\"section-subtitle\">信息显示</div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;gap:16px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:8px\">\n    <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px\">\n        <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">OSD</span>\n        <label class=\"toggle-switch\">\n            <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"infoOsdSwitch\" onchange=\"toggleInfoOsdSwitch(this.checked)\">\n            <span class=\"toggle-slider\"></span>\n        </label>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px\">\n        <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">PTZ</span>\n        <label class=\"toggle-switch\">\n            <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"ptzOsdSwitch\" onchange=\"togglePtzOsdSwitch(this.checked)\">\n            <span class=\"toggle-slider\"></span>\n        </label>\n    </div>\n</div>\n```\n\n注意： \n- `ptzOsdSwitchInPtz` 改为 `ptzOsdSwitch` (因为右侧不再有ptzOsdSwitch， \n- 新增 `infoOsdSwitch` (原右侧的Info OSD开关ID)\n\n修改 `loadOsdStatus` 函数:两处读取改为写两个开关的真实状态。\n\n修改 `disableImageControls/enableImageControls`: OSD开关不在画面控制区,不应被禁用.\n\n修改 `updateInfoOsdButtons/updatePtzOsdButtons`: 只更新运动控制区的开关状态.\n\n修改 `toggleInfoOsdSwitch/togglePtzOsdSwitch`: 只更新运动控制区的开关.\n\n修改 `index.html` `toggleRegionMode`:删除手动模式前置检查.\n修改 `index.html` 或 `console.html` `onWbModeChange/onFocusModeChange`:局部时自动切换到手动模式.\n\n修改版本号和HEARTBEAT.错误理解：\n\n- 需求2说\"下方依然需要保留之前移动的两个开关\" - 意思是v8.38时我把画面控制区的两个开关(Info OSD + PTZ OSD)移动到运动控制区，而不是新增开关.\n- 我在v8.38里误解了，在运动控制区新增了一个\"PTZ OSD\"开关(inPtz), 同时右侧保留了Info OSD开关. 这是过度开发.\n- 正确做法: 移动(不是新增) - 把右侧的两个开关移动到左侧运动控制区.\n\n- 开关ID保持不变: `infoOsdSwitch` 和 `ptzOsdSwitch` (不需要InPtz后缀)\n\n让我执行正确的修改:","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-0dcfa2ad3cdd491e950261a32c04889b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path \"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html\" -Pattern \"section-subtitle.*OSD|PTZ OSD|infoOsdSwitch|ptzOsdSwitch\" -Context 0,2 | Select-Object LineNumber, Line"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":138127,"output":806,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":138933,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783178352525,"responseId":"cht000d0432@dx19f2db668792871503"}}
