{"type":"message","id":"3724afba","parentId":"d58a46e8","timestamp":"2026-07-04T16:26:21.904Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user's request is for me to write lasting notes to memory/2026-07-05.md. Let me check what needs to be recorded from this session.\n\nThis was a very long and complex session involving multiple UI changes to the AstroHub web interface. The key work done:\n\n1. Modified main console layout (console.html)\n2. PTZ direction center button changed to \"归位\" (home) function\n3. OSD section moved from right panel to left panel (motion control)\n4. \"框选分析\" section removed from media controls\n5. White balance and focus mode changes:\n   - Labels changed from \"白平衡模式\" to \"白平衡\"\n   - 3 options: 自动, 手动, 局部\n   - Local mode auto-switches to manual mode\n   - Removed manual mode prerequisite for region selection\n6. Region selection memory to localStorage (for white balance and focus separately)\n\nThe session had many issues:\n- I repeatedly misunderstood requirements\n- Made multiple incorrect edits\n- Had to be corrected multiple times by the boss\n- The final state of the test showed some failures that need follow-up\n\nKey lessons learned:\n1. Always verify the exact HTML structure before making edits\n2. Don't over-engineer solutions - stick to what was explicitly requested\n3. When moving elements, preserve their exact structure and IDs\n4. Run tests after changes to verify correctness\n\nI should write this to memory/2026-07-05.md as a durable note.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7f23d9e7b6014a3aa35613e9","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\memory\\2026-07-05.md","content":"# 2026-07-05 记忆\n\n## 主控台界面重构 v8.39\n\n### 完成的修改\n1. **运动控制 - 中心按钮改为归位**\n   - PTZ方向键中心按钮从停止(●)改为归位(⌂)\n   - 调用 `ptzHome()` 回到10号预置点HOME\n   - 删除预置点下方的\"归位\"按钮\n\n2. **运动控制 - OSD模块移动**\n   - 标题改为\"信息显示\"\n   - 保留两个开关：OSD(Info OSD) + PTZ\n   - 从右侧画面控制区完整移动到左侧运动控制区\n   - 统一ID：`infoOsdSwitch` / `ptzOsdSwitch`\n\n3. **媒体操作 - 删除框选分析**\n   - 移除\"框选分析\"section（白平衡/对焦按钮）\n   - 框选功能现集成到白平衡/对焦的\"局部\"模式\n\n4. **画面控制 - 删除Info OSD**\n   - 右侧面板不再有OSD控制区\n   - 所有OSD开关都在运动控制区\n\n5. **白平衡/对焦模式重构**\n   - 标签从\"白平衡模式\"改为\"白平衡\"\n   - 3个选项：自动、手动、局部\n   - 局部模式：自动切换到内置手动模式\n   - 删除手动模式前置要求\n   - 框选按钮 + 定时输入框（分钟，0=不执行）\n   - 点击框选后显示停止按钮\n\n6. **选区记忆功能**\n   - 白平衡和对焦选区分别存储到localStorage\n   - key: `wb_region` / `focus_region`\n   - 存储格式: `{x, y, w, h}` (归一化坐标)\n   - 下次框选时恢复上次的选区\n\n### 教训\n1. 移动UI模块时要完整保留原有结构，不要重新实现\n2. 需求理解要精确 - \"移动\"不是\"删除后重建\"\n3. ID统一很重要，避免出现多个不同ID指向同一功能\n\n### 待验证\n- Playwright测试有2个失败（测试脚本引用旧ID）\n- 需要实际设备连接后验证功能正确性\n\n---\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":142644,"output":856,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":143500,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783182348083,"responseId":"cht000dd881@dx19f2df36ad729c2503"}}
