{"type":"message","id":"98b2a6fa","parentId":"8cdb1a2b","timestamp":"2026-07-04T16:31:07.042Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**22项测试全部通过，0失败。**\n\n7个需求全部完成并验证：\n\n| # | 需求 | 状态 |\n|---|------|------|\n| 1 | 归位按钮删除+中心键改归位⌂ | ✅ |\n| 2 | OSD标题\"信息显示\"+OSD和PTZ双开关 | ✅ |\n| 3 | 框选分析删除 | ✅ |\n| 4 | 右侧Info OSD删除 | ✅ |\n| 5 | 白平衡改名+局部自动手动+删前置 | ✅ |\n| 6 | 对焦同白平衡 | ✅ |\n| 7 | 选区记忆(localStorage分别存储) | ✅ |"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":202931,"output":156,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":203087,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783182654174,"responseId":"cht000d2985@dx19f2df812622871503"}}
