{"type":"message","id":"80937036","parentId":"e87b950a","timestamp":"2026-07-04T16:35:36.059Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to check if all their requirements have been completed. Let me recall what the original requirements were and verify each one systematically.\n\nFrom the conversation history, the requirements were:\n\n1. 把运动控制中预置点下方的\"归位\"按钮，删除，将PTZ的方向按键中间的停止键改成归位，也就是回到10号预置点HOME\n2. 运动控制中的OSD这一栏，标题改成\"信息显示\"，下方依然需要保留之前移动的两个开关，OSD和PTZ，这两个需要读取真实状态获取开关状态\n3. 媒体操作中的\"框选分析\"删除\n4. 画面控制中，信息 osd开关删除。\n5. 白平衡模式改成\"白平衡\"，当点击局部的时候，自动切换到内置的手动挡，并且删除局部框选白平衡之前必须要设置手动模式的前置要求。\n6. 对焦的修改，同白平衡，当点击局部的时候，自动切换到内置的手动挡，并且删除局部框选对焦之前必须要设置手动模式的前置要求。\n7. 定时功能，是需要记忆选区的，保留使用上一次的选区，但是注意，白平衡和对焦，这两个选取是不一样的。\n\nI already ran a verification check that showed:\n- 需求1: ✅ (center button is home, \"归位\" button deleted)\n- 需求2: ✅ (title is \"信息显示\", two switches present)\n- 需求3: ✅ (框选分析 section deleted, Count=0)\n- 需求4: ✅ (右侧Info OSD deleted, Count=0)\n- 需求5: ✅ (setWhiteBalanceMode('manual') called)\n- 需求6: ✅ (setFocusMode('manual') called)\n- 需求7: ✅ (localStorage stores region coordinates separately for WB and focus)\n\nNow I need to check if there's any additional work needed. Let me look at what the test results showed:\n\nThe test run just completed with 22 passed / 0 failed. All tests are passing now.\n\nBut I should double-check the actual implementation details to make sure everything is truly complete. Let me examine the current state of the code to ensure all requirements are met.\n\nI need to check:\n1. PTZ center button - should call ptzHome()\n2. \"归位\" button below presets - should be deleted\n3. OSD section title - should be \"信息显示\"\n4. Two OSD switches (OSD and PTZ) - should exist in motion control area\n5. 框选分析 section - should be deleted from media operations\n6. Info OSD switch in right panel - should be deleted\n7. White balance - should auto-switch to manual when local mode selected\n8. Focus - should auto-switch to manual when local mode selected\n9. Region memory - should use localStorage for both WB and focus separately\n\nLet me read the relevant files to verify each requirement in detail.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"让我逐项检查所有需求的实际代码状态，确保真正完成。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_e9eb79c60f694e7e9079ec38","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":15,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":3517,"output":716,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":220459,"totalTokens":224692,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783182816172,"responseId":"msg_b7b1a359-9e42-42fc-be0d-4ccb99e3fa55"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d259f909","parentId":"80937036","timestamp":"2026-07-04T16:35:36.098Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_e9eb79c60f694e7e9079ec38","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"                                <span class=\"collapse-icon\">▼</span>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"collapsible-content\">\r\n                                <!-- 指向控制 + 信息展示 -->\r\n                                <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:stretch\">\r\n                                    <!-- 左侧:方向控制 + 速度 -->\r\n                                    <div style=\"flex:0 0 auto;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:space-between\">\r\n                                        <div class=\"ptz-controls\">\r\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('up-left')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('up-left')\">↖</button>\r\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('up')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('up')\">↑</button>\r\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('up-right')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('up-right')\">↗</button>\r\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('left')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('left')\">←</button>\r\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onclick=\"ptzHome()\" title=\"归位\">⌂</button>\r\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('right')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('right')\">→</button>\r\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('down-left')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('down-left')\">↙</button>\r\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('down')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('down')\">↓</button>\r\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('down-right')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('down-right')\">↘</button>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div class=\"ptz-speed\" style=\"width:170px;font-size:11px;margin-top:8px\">\r\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px\">速度:</label>\r\n                                            <input type=\"range\" id=\"ptzSpeed\" min=\"1\" max=\"7\" value=\"4\" style=\"width:90px\">\r\n                                            <span id=\"ptzSpeedVal\" style=\"font-size:11px\">4</span>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- 右侧:光圈快门 + P/T/Z(竖排,宽度减少15%) -->\r\n                                    <div style=\"flex:0 0 110px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0\">\r\n                                        <div class=\"info-block\" style=\"flex:1\">\r\n                                            <div class=\"info-row\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;padding:1px 4px;font-size:12px\"><span class=\"info-label\">光圈</span><span class=\"info-value\" id=\"ptzIris\">--</span></div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"info-row\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;padding:1px 4px;font-size:12px\"><span class=\"info-label\">快门</span><span class=\"info-value\" id=\"ptzShutter\">--</span></div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"info-row\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;padding:1px 4px;font-size:12px\"><span class=\"info-label\">R</span><span class=\"info-value\" id=\"ptzWbR\">--</span></div>\r\n\n[1626 more lines in file. Use offset=45 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783182936098}}
{"type":"message","id":"33abf67b","parentId":"d259f909","timestamp":"2026-07-04T16:35:59.303Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to check if all their requirements have been completed. Let me read through the current state of the code and verify each requirement one by one.\n\nLet me check each requirement systematically:\n\n1. \"把运动控制中预置点下方的\"归位\"按钮，删除，将PTZ的方向按键中间的停止键改成归位，也就是回到10号预置点HOME\" - ✅ Confirmed: Center button is now ⌂ with onclick=\"ptzHome()\"\n\n2. \"运动控制中的OSD这一栏，标题改成\"信息显示\"，下方依然需要保留之前移动的两个开关，OSD和PTZ，这两个需要读取真实状态获取开关状态\" - Need to check this\n\n3. \"媒体操作中的\"框选分析\"删除\" - ✅ Count=0 means it's deleted\n\n4. \"画面控制中，信息 osd开关删除\" - ✅ Count=0 means it's deleted\n\n5. \"白平衡模式改成\"白平衡\"，当点击局部的时候，自动切换到内置的手动挡，并且删除局部框选白平衡之前必须要设置手动模式的前置要求。\" - Need to check this\n\n6. \"对焦的修改，同白平衡，当点击局部的时候，自动切换到内置的手动挡，并且删除局部框选对焦之前必须要设置手动模式的前置要求。\" - Need to check this\n\n7. \"定时功能，是需要记忆选区的，保留使用上一次的选区，但是注意，白平衡和对焦，这两个选取是不一样的。\" - Need to check this\n\nLet me read more of the console.html to verify requirements 2, 5, 6, and 7.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_6f898afc604a4ba4a15c3368","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":50,"offset":70,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":4336,"output":426,"cacheRead":220459,"cacheWrite":722,"totalTokens":225943,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783182936102,"responseId":"msg_f9b79bad-6027-44f2-98d5-f6e86d9c3046"}}
{"type":"message","id":"26c979b3","parentId":"33abf67b","timestamp":"2026-07-04T16:35:59.343Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_6f898afc604a4ba4a15c3368","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"                                    </select>\r\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" onclick=\"ptzGotoSelectedPreset()\">前往</button>\r\n                                    <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" onclick=\"ptzWritePreset()\">写入</button>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <!-- 信息显示开关 -->\r\n                                <div class=\"section-subtitle\">信息显示</div>\r\n                                <div style=\"display:flex;gap:16px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:8px\">\r\n                                    <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px\">\r\n                                        <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">OSD</span>\r\n                                        <label class=\"toggle-switch\">\r\n                                            <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"infoOsdSwitch\" onchange=\"toggleInfoOsdSwitch(this.checked)\">\r\n                                            <span class=\"toggle-slider\"></span>\r\n                                        </label>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px\">\r\n                                        <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">PTZ</span>\r\n                                        <label class=\"toggle-switch\">\r\n                                            <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"ptzOsdSwitch\" checked onchange=\"togglePtzOsdSwitch(this.checked)\">\r\n                                            <span class=\"toggle-slider\"></span>\r\n                                        </label>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <!-- 媒体信息(折叠,默认展开) -->\r\n                        <div class=\"collapsible-section\" id=\"mediaLogSection\" style=\"margin-top:12px\">\r\n                            <div class=\"collapsible-header\" onclick=\"toggleSection('mediaLogSection')\">\r\n                                <h3 style=\"font-size:15px;color:#58a6ff;margin:0\">📡 媒体信息</h3>\r\n                                <span class=\"collapse-icon\">▼</span>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"collapsible-content\">\r\n                                <div style=\"background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:8px;padding:8px;overflow-y:auto;height:200px\" class=\"hide-scrollbar\">\r\n                                    <div id=\"mediaLogBox\" style=\"font-size:11px;font-family:monospace;color:#8b949e\">\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <!-- 中: 实时画面 + 媒体操作 -->\r\n                    <div class=\"console-center\">\r\n                        <div class=\"console-video-wrap\" style=\"background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:12px;overflow:hidden;position:relative;width:100%;\">\r\n                            <!-- v7.98: WASM 播放器占位区域,保留16:9比例 -->\r\n                            <div id=\"divPlugin\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;display:block;margin:0 auto\"></div>\r\n                            <!-- v8.10: 框选区域 overlay(默认隐藏) -->\r\n                            <div id=\"regionOverlay\" style=\"display:none;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;cursor:crosshair;z-index:100\">\r\n                                <div id=\"regionBox\" style=\"position:absolute;border:2px dashed #3f