{"type":"message","id":"9aeebb22","parentId":"2752228d","timestamp":"2026-07-04T16:36:10.924Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_60c3796267c440aaaa723b5b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"                                    <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:4px\">\r\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">\r\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">空域降噪 <span id=\"dnrSpatialVal\" style=\"color:#58a6ff\">--</span></label>\r\n                                            <input type=\"range\" id=\"dnrSpatial\" min=\"0\" max=\"100\" value=\"50\" style=\"width:100%\" oninput=\"document.getElementById('dnrSpatialVal').textContent=this.value\" onchange=\"setNoiseReduce('spatial', this.value)\">\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">\r\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">时域降噪 <span id=\"dnrTemporalVal\" style=\"color:#58a6ff\">--</span></label>\r\n                                            <input type=\"range\" id=\"dnrTemporal\" min=\"0\" max=\"100\" value=\"50\" style=\"width:100%\" oninput=\"document.getElementById('dnrTemporalVal').textContent=this.value\" onchange=\"setNoiseReduce('temporal', this.value)\">\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- 白平衡 -->\r\n                                    <div class=\"form-group\" style=\"margin-bottom:4px\">\r\n                                        <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">白平衡</label>\r\n                                        <select id=\"wbMode\" style=\"width:100%;padding:4px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:12px\" onchange=\"onWbModeChange(this.value)\">\r\n                                            <option value=\"auto\">自动</option>\r\n                                            <option value=\"manual\">手动</option>\r\n                                            <option value=\"local\">局部</option>\r\n                                        </select>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- R/B 滑动条(仅手动模式显示) -->\r\n                                    <div id=\"wbManualControls\" style=\"display:none;flex-direction:row;gap:8px;margin-bottom:4px\">\r\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">\r\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#f85149\">R <span id=\"wbRedVal\" style=\"color:#f85149\">--</span></label>\r\n                                            <input type=\"range\" id=\"wbRed\" min=\"0\" max=\"255\" value=\"50\" style=\"width:100%\" oninput=\"document.getElementById('wbRedVal').textContent=this.value\" onchange=\"setWhiteBalanceGain('red', this.value)\" disabled>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div style=\"flex:1\">\r\n                                            <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#58a6ff\">B <span id=\"wbBlueVal\" style=\"color:#58a6ff\">--</span></label>\r\n                                            <input type=\"range\" id=\"wbBlue\" min=\"0\" max=\"255\" value=\"50\" style=\"width:100%\" oninput=\"document.getElementById('wbBlueVal').textContent=this.value\" onchange=\"setWhiteBalanceGain('blue', this.value)\" disabled>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- 局部白平衡控制(仅局部模式显示) -->\r\n                                    <div id=\"wbLocalControls\" style=\"display:none;margin-bottom:4px\">\r\n                                        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:4px\">\r\n                                            <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" id=\"btnWbRegionSelect\" onclick=\"toggleRegionMode('whitebalance')\">框选</button>\r\n                                            <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px\">\r\n                                                <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">定时:</span>\r\n                                                <input type=\"number\" id=\"wbTimerInput\" value=\"0\" min=\"0\" style=\"width:50px;padding:2px 4px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:11px\">\r\n                                                <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">分钟</span>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <button class=\"btn btn-danger btn-sm\" id=\"btnWbLocalStop\" onclick=\"stopAutoWhiteBalance()\" style=\"display:none;width:100%\">停止</button>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- 对焦 -->\r\n                                    <div class=\"form-group\" style=\"margin-bottom:4px\">\r\n                                        <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">对焦</label>\r\n                                        <select id=\"focusMode\" style=\"width:100%;padding:4px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:12px\" onchange=\"onFocusModeChange(this.value)\">\r\n                                            <option value=\"auto\">自动</option>\r\n                                            <option value=\"manual\">手动</option>\r\n                                            <option value=\"local\">局部</option>\r\n                                        </select>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- 焦点移动按钮(仅手动模式显示) -->\r\n                                    <div id=\"focusMoveControls\" style=\"display:none;margin-bottom:4px\">\r\n                                        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap\">\r\n                                            <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">焦点:</span>\r\n                                            <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onmousedown=\"ptzFocus('far')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" ontouchstart=\"ptzFocus('far')\" ontouchend=\"ptzStop()\">远</button>\r\n                                            <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onmousedown=\"ptzFocus('near')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" ontouchstart=\"ptzFocus('near')\" ontouchend=\"ptzStop()\">近</button>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- 局部对焦控制(仅局部模式显示) -->\r\n\n[1386 more lines in file. Use offset=285 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783182970924}}
{"type":"message","id":"71e77729","parentId":"9aeebb22","timestamp":"2026-07-04T16:36:28.946Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to verify if all their requirements have been completed. Let me review what they asked for:\n\n1. Delete the \"归位\" button below presets, change the center PTZ direction button to \"归位\" (go to preset 10 HOME) - ✅ Confirmed: Line 25 shows `<button class=\"ptz-btn\" onclick=\"ptzHome()\" title=\"归位\">⌂</button>`\n\n2. Change the OSD title to \"信息显示\", keep two switches (OSD and PTZ), read real status for switch state - ✅ Confirmed: Lines 75-92 show the \"信息显示\" section with both OSD and PTZ switches\n\n3. Delete \"框选分析\" from media operations - ✅ Already confirmed earlier (Count=0)\n\n4. Delete Info OSD switch from image controls - ✅ Already confirmed earlier (Count=0)\n\n5. Change white balance mode to \"白平衡\", when clicking \"local\", auto-switch to manual mode internally, remove the prerequisite of setting manual mode before local region selection - ✅ Confirmed: Line 237 shows label is \"白平衡\", and lines 250-258 show the local controls with region selection and timer\n\n6. Same for focus - change label to \"对焦\", when clicking \"local\", auto-switch to manual mode internally, remove prerequisite - ✅ Confirmed: Line 282 shows label is \"对焦\", and lines 285+ show the local controls\n\n7. Timer function needs to remember the region selection, use the last selected region, and white balance and focus regions are different - Need to verify this\n\nLet me check the JavaScript implementation to confirm:\n- onWbModeChange and onFocusModeChange functions auto-switch to manual when \"local\" is selected\n- localStorage saves regions separately for white balance and focus\n- toggleRegionMode removed the manual mode prerequisite check","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Let me check the JavaScript functions to verify requirements 5, 6, and 7:\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_6495d80b3b5c4d938702fd2a","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":80,"offset":1158,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":6045,"output":496,"cacheRead":221181,"cacheWrite":1121,"totalTokens":228843,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783182970928,"responseId":"msg_e9462117-4e48-43da-9c13-0cca5254d74e"}}
{"type":"message","id":"7e5b9d00","parentId":"71e77729","timestamp":"2026-07-04T16:36:28.988Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_6495d80b3b5c4d938702fd2a","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"function setSharpness(value) {\r\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\r\n    if (!dev) return;\r\n    apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/sharpness', { level: parseInt(value) })\r\n        .then(function(r) { if (r && r.success && typeof operationLog === 'function' && !_isInitializingImageParams) operationLog('锐度: ' + value, 'success'); });\r\n}\r\n\r\n// 设置白平衡模式\r\n// 白平衡模式切换:显示/隐藏对应控件\r\nfunction onWbModeChange(mode) {\r\n    var manualControls = document.getElementById('wbManualControls');\r\n    var localControls = document.getElementById('wbLocalControls');\r\n    var wbRed = document.getElementById('wbRed');\r\n    var wbBlue = document.getElementById('wbBlue');\r\n\r\n    if (mode === 'manual') {\r\n        if (manualControls) manualControls.style.display = 'flex';\r\n        if (localControls) localControls.style.display = 'none';\r\n        if (wbRed) wbRed.disabled = false;\r\n        if (wbBlue) wbBlue.disabled = false;\r\n        setWhiteBalanceMode('manual');\r\n    } else if (mode === 'local') {\r\n        if (manualControls) manualControls.style.display = 'none';\r\n        if (localControls) localControls.style.display = 'block';\r\n        if (wbRed) wbRed.disabled = true;\r\n        if (wbBlue) wbBlue.disabled = true;\r\n        // v8.39: 局部模式自动切换到手动模式\r\n        setWhiteBalanceMode('manual');\r\n    } else {\r\n        // 自动\r\n        if (manualControls) manualControls.style.display = 'none';\r\n        if (localControls) localControls.style.display = 'none';\r\n        if (wbRed) wbRed.disabled = true;\r\n        if (wbBlue) wbBlue.disabled = true;\r\n        setWhiteBalanceMode('auto');\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n// 停止自动白平衡\r\nfunction stopAutoWhiteBalance() {\r\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\r\n    if (!dev) return;\r\n    // 调用后端停止接口\r\n    apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/whitebalance/stop', {}).then(function(r) {\r\n        if (r && r.success) {\r\n            showToast('success', '已停止自动白平衡');\r\n            if (typeof operationLog === 'function') operationLog('停止自动白平衡', 'success');\r\n        }\r\n    }).catch(function(e) {\r\n        showToast('error', '停止失败');\r\n    });\r\n    // 恢复按钮状态\r\n    var stopBtn = document.getElementById('btnWbLocalStop');\r\n    var selectBtn = document.getElementById('btnWbRegionSelect');\r\n    if (stopBtn) stopBtn.style.display = 'none';\r\n    if (selectBtn) { selectBtn.textContent = '框选'; selectBtn.classList.remove('btn-danger'); selectBtn.classList.add('btn-secondary'); }\r\n}\r\n\r\n// 对焦模式切换:显示/隐藏对应控件\r\nfunction onFocusModeChange(mode) {\r\n    var moveControls = document.getElementById('focusMoveControls');\r\n    var localControls = document.getElementById('focusLocalControls');\r\n\r\n    if (mode === 'manual') {\r\n        if (moveControls) moveControls.style.display = 'block';\r\n        if (localControls) localControls.style.display = 'none';\r\n        setFocusMode('manual');\r\n    } else if (mode === 'local') {\r\n        if (moveControls) moveControls.style.display = 'none';\r\n        if (localControls) localControls.style.display = 'block';\r\n        // v8.39: 局部模式自动切换到手动模式\r\n        setFocusMode('manual');\r\n    } else {\r\n        // 自动\r\n        if (moveControls) moveControls.style.display = 'none';\r\n        if (localControls) localControls.style.display = 'none';\r\n        setFocusMode('auto');\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n\n[433 more lines in file. Use offset=1238 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783182988988}}
{"type":"message","id":"0b7d58df","parentId":"7e5b9d00","timestamp":"2026-07-04T16:36:58.534Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_766f0f8bbd634cb88282b5ef","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":20,"offset":2920,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":208458,"output":47,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":208505,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783182988993,"responseId":"cht000daeb3@dx19f2dfd31da2871503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"9c0f0bf2","parentId":"0b7d58df","timestamp":"2026-07-04T16:36:58.575Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_766f0f8bbd634cb88282b5ef","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\r\n    // v8.11: 统一 ISAPI 截图 → 后端裁剪 → 迭代搜索 → 操作日志\r\n    function _finishRegion() {\r\n        var overlay = document.getElementById('regionOverlay');\r\n        var box = document.getElementById('regionBox');\r\n        var dev = window.connectedDevice;\r\n        if (!dev || !dev.ip) { showToast('error', '未连接设备'); _resetRegionUI(); return; }\r\n\r\n        var ow = overlay.offsetWidth, oh = overlay.offsetHeight;\r\n        var sx = parseInt(box.style.left) / ow;\r\n        var sy = parseInt(box.style.top) / oh;\r\n        var sw = parseInt(box.style.width) / ow;\r\n        var sh = parseInt(box.style.height) / oh;\r\n        if (sw < 0.01 || sh < 0.01) { showToast('warning', '框选区域太小'); _resetRegionUI(); return; }\r\n\r\n        // v8.39: 保存选区到 localStorage（白平衡和对焦分别保存）\r\n        var regionKey = 'region_' + mode;\r\n        localStorage.setItem(regionKey, JSON.stringify({ x: sx, y: sy, w: sw, h: sh }));\r\n\r\n        var mode = _regionMode;\r\n\n[132 more lines in file. Use offset=2940 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783183018575}}
{"type":"message","id":"e3634c1a","parentId":"9c0f0bf2","timestamp":"2026-07-04T16:38:14.255Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I need to check the JavaScript implementation to see if:\n\n1. `onWbModeChange` auto-switches to manual when local is selected - ✅ confirmed at line 1195\n2. `onFocusModeChange` auto-switches to manual when local is selected - ✅ confirmed at line 1236\n3. `toggleRegionMode` removed manual mode prerequisite - need to check\n4. Region selection is saved to localStorage separately for WB and focus - ✅ confirmed at lines 2937-2938\n\nLet me check toggleRegionMode in index.html:\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n......\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_c5887b54cb35445b8159280a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path \"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html\" -Pattern \"function toggleRegionMode\" | Select-Object LineNumber"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usag