{"type":"message","id":"01760e9d","parentId":"f143f0f2","timestamp":"2026-07-04T16:38:42.774Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_cd4e5aa880774bd0903e25da","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    function toggleRegionMode(mode) {\r\n        // 新的按钮 ID（在白平衡/对焦局部控制中）\r\n        var btnWB = document.getElementById('btnWbRegionSelect');\r\n        var btnAF = document.getElementById('btnFocusRegionSelect');\r\n        var overlay = document.getElementById('regionOverlay');\r\n        var box = document.getElementById('regionBox');\r\n        if (_regionMode === mode) {\r\n            _regionMode = null;\r\n            if (btnWB) btnWB.className = 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n            if (btnAF) btnAF.className = 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n            overlay.style.display = 'none';\r\n            box.style.display = 'none';\r\n            return;\r\n        }\r\n        if (!window.connectedDevice || !window.connectedDevice.ip) {\r\n            showToast('warning', '请先连接设备');\r\n            return;\r\n        }\r\n        // v8.39: 移除手动模式限制 - 局部模式自动切换到手动\r\n        // 当选择局部框选时，自动切换到手动模式\r\n        if (mode === 'whitebalance') {\r\n            var wbMode = document.getElementById('wbMode');\r\n            if (wbMode && wbMode.value !== 'manual') {\r\n                // 自动切换到手动模式\r\n                setWhiteBalanceMode('manual');\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n        if (mode === 'focus') {\r\n            var fm = document.getElementById('focusMode');\r\n            if (fm && fm.value !== 'manual') {\r\n                // 自动切换到手动模式\r\n                setFocusMode('manual');\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n        _regionMode = mode;\r\n        if (btnWB) btnWB.className = mode === 'whitebalance' ? 'btn btn-primary btn-sm' : 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n        if (btnAF) btnAF.className = mode === 'focus' ? 'btn btn-primary btn-sm' : 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n        overlay.style.display = 'block';\r\n        box.style.display = 'none';\r\n    }\r\n\n[158 more lines in file. Use offset=2914 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783183122773}}
{"type":"message","id":"ef1c802b","parentId":"01760e9d","timestamp":"2026-07-04T16:39:30.491Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to verify if all their requirements have been completed. Let me review what they asked for and what I've found:\n\n1. **Delete \"归位\" button from presets section, change center PTZ button to \"归位\" (home/preset 10)** \n   - ✅ Confirmed at line 25: `<button class=\"ptz-btn\" onclick=\"ptzHome()\" title=\"归位\">⌂</button>`\n\n2. **Change OSD section title to \"信息显示\", keep both OSD and PTZ switches, read real status for switch states**\n   - ✅ Confirmed at lines 75-92: Section has \"信息显示\" title with both OSD and PTZ toggle switches\n   - Need to verify if the switches read real status from backend\n\n3. **Delete \"框选分析\" from media operations**\n   - ✅ Confirmed: Count=0 in earlier check\n\n4. **Delete Info OSD switch from image controls (right panel)**\n   - ✅ Confirmed: Count=0 in earlier check\n\n5. **White balance: change to \"白平衡\", when clicking \"local\" mode, auto-switch to manual mode internally, remove manual mode prerequisite for region selection**\n   - ✅ Confirmed at lines 1178-1179: When mode === 'local', calls `setWhiteBalanceMode('manual')`\n   - ✅ Confirmed at lines 2897-2904: toggleRegionMode removed manual mode prerequisite check\n\n6. **Focus: same as white balance - auto-switch to manual when local selected, remove manual mode prerequisite**\n   - ✅ Confirmed at lines 1235-1236: When mode === 'local', calls `setFocusMode('manual')`\n   - ✅ Confirmed at lines 2906-2912: toggleRegionMode removed manual mode prerequisite check\n\n7. **Timer function needs to remember region selection, use last selected region separately for white balance and focus**\n   - ✅ Confirmed at lines 2937-2938: Saves region to localStorage with key 'region_' + mode (separate for WB and focus)\n   \nLet me double-check the localStorage implementation to ensure it's correctly implemented.\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n......","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Let me verify the localStorage implementation and check if the region selection is properly loaded when entering local mode:\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_9334927e380a43339c683aec","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":50,"offset":2914,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":7796,"output":1082,"cacheRead":223624,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":232502,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783183122777,"responseId":"msg_27722d09-5e02-4853-b61c-05e8245dc49e"}}
{"type":"message","id":"94b2d320","parentId":"ef1c802b","timestamp":"2026-07-04T16:39:30.533Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_9334927e380a43339c683aec","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\r\n    function _getOverlayPos(e) {\r\n        var overlay = document.getElementById('regionOverlay');\r\n        var rect = overlay.getBoundingClientRect();\r\n        return { x: e.clientX - rect.left, y: e.clientY - rect.top };\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    // v8.11: 统一 ISAPI 截图 → 后端裁剪 → 迭代搜索 → 操作日志\r\n    function _finishRegion() {\r\n        var overlay = document.getElementById('regionOverlay');\r\n        var box = document.getElementById('regionBox');\r\n        var dev = window.connectedDevice;\r\n        if (!dev || !dev.ip) { showToast('error', '未连接设备'); _resetRegionUI(); return; }\r\n\r\n        var ow = overlay.offsetWidth, oh = overlay.offsetHeight;\r\n        var sx = parseInt(box.style.left) / ow;\r\n        var sy = parseInt(box.style.top) / oh;\r\n        var sw = parseInt(box.style.width) / ow;\r\n        var sh = parseInt(box.style.height) / oh;\r\n        if (sw < 0.01 || sh < 0.01) { showToast('warning', '框选区域太小'); _resetRegionUI(); return; }\r\n\r\n        // v8.39: 保存选区到 localStorage（白平衡和对焦分别保存）\r\n        var regionKey = 'region_' + mode;\r\n        localStorage.setItem(regionKey, JSON.stringify({ x: sx, y: sy, w: sw, h: sh }));\r\n\r\n        var mode = _regionMode;\r\n        var endpoint = mode === 'whitebalance' ? '/api/v1/vision/whitebalance-search'\r\n                                               : '/api/v1/vision/focus-search';\r\n        var label = mode === 'whitebalance' ? '白平衡' : '对焦';\r\n\r\n        _resetRegionUI();\r\n        showToast('info', label + '迭代中...');\r\n        operationLog('── ' + label + '迭代开始 ──', 'info');\r\n\r\n        // SSE 流式调用\r\n        var body = JSON.stringify({ x: sx, y: sy, w: sw, h: sh });\r\n        fetch(endpoint, { method: 'POST', headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' }, body: body })\r\n            .then(function(resp) {\r\n                if (!resp.ok) throw new Error('HTTP ' + resp.status);\r\n                var reader = resp.body.getReader();\r\n                var decoder = new TextDecoder();\r\n                var buf = '';\r\n                function pump() {\r\n                    return reader.read().then(function(r) {\r\n                        if (r.done) return;\r\n                        buf += decoder.decode(r.value, { stream: true });\r\n                        // 按 \\n\\n 分割事件\r\n                        var parts = buf.split('\\n\\n');\r\n                        buf = parts.pop();  // 最后一段可能不完整\r\n                        for (var i = 0; i < parts.length; i++) {\r\n\n[108 more lines in file. Use offset=2964 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783183170533}}
{"type":"message","id":"b381572c","parentId":"94b2d320","timestamp":"2026-07-04T16:40:29.474Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I've verified all the code changes. Let me summarize what was done:\n\n1. **归位按钮修改** ✅\n   - 删除了预置点下方的\"归位\"按钮（line 70-72只剩\"前往\"和\"写入\"）\n   - PTZ方向键中心按钮改为归位（line 25: `<button class=\"ptz-btn\" onclick=\"ptzHome()\" title=\"归位\">⌂</button>`）\n\n2. **OSD标题改为\"信息显示\"** ✅\n   - line 75: `<div class=\"section-subtitle\">信息显示</div>`\n   - 保留两个开关：OSD和PTZ（lines 80, 87）\n   - 两个开关都读取真实状态（通过toggleInfoOsdSwitch和togglePtzOsdSwitch）\n\n3. **删除框选分析** ✅\n   - 之前检查Count=0，已确认删除\n\n4. **删除右侧Info OSD** ✅\n   - 之前检查Count=0，已确认删除\n\n5. **白平衡模式改为\"白平衡\"** ✅\n   - line 234: `<label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">白平衡</label>`\n   - 点击局部时自动切换到手动（lines 1178-1179: `setWhiteBalanceMode('manual')`）\n   - 删除手动模式前置要求（toggleRegionMode函数中没有检查）\n\n6. **对焦模式改为\"对焦\"** ✅\n   - line 277: `<label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">对焦</label>`\n   - 点击局部时自动切换到手动（lines 1235-1236: `setFocusMode('manual')`）\n   - 删除手动模式前置要求（toggleRegionMode函数中没有检查）\n\n7. **定时功能记忆选区** ✅\n   - line 2937: `localStorage.setItem(regionKey, JSON.stringify({ x: sx, y: sy, w: sw, h: sh }));`\n   - regionKey = 'region_' + mode，白平衡和对焦分别保存为'region_whitebalance'和'region_focus'\n\n所有7个需求都已完成！\n\n不过，我注意到line 2937有一个bug：\n```javascript\nvar regionKey = 'region_' + mode;\nlocalStorage.setItem(regionKey, JSON.stringify({ x: sx, y: sy, w: sw, h: sh }));\n\nvar mode = _regionMode;\n```\n\n这里`mode`在使用前还没有定义！`var mode = _regionMode;`在`regionKey = 'region_' + mode;`之后才定义。这会导致regionKey变成'undefined'。\n\n这是一个bug，需要修复。让我检查并修复它。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"我发现了一个bug！在 `_finishRegion` 函数中，`mode` 变量在使用前还没有定义：\n\n```javascript\nvar regionKey = 'region_' + mode;  // 这里mode还未定义！\nlocalStorage.setItem(regionKey, JSON.stringify({ x: sx, y: sy, w: sw, h: sh }));\n\nvar mode = _regionMode;  // 这行在后面才定义mode\n```\n\n这会导致localStorage的key变成`'region_undefined'`，而不是`'region_whitebalance'`或`'region_focus'`。\n\n让我修复这个bug：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_57b05bd0717646fb81affd48","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"        var mode = _regionMode;\n        \n        // v8.39: 保存选区到 localStorage（白平衡和对焦分别保存）\n        var regionKey = 'region_' + mode;\n        localStorage.setItem(regionKey, JSON.stringify({ x: sx, y: sy, w: sw, h: sh }));\n        \n        var endpoint = mode === 'whitebalance' ? '/api/v1/vision/whitebalance-search'","oldText":"        // v8.39: 保存选区到 localStorage（白平衡和对焦分别保存）\n        var regionKey = 'region_' + mode;\n        localStorage.setItem(regionKey, JSON.stringify({ x: sx, y: sy, w: sw, h: sh }));\n\n        var mode = _regionMode;\n        var endpoint = mode === 'whitebalance' ? '/api/v1/vision/whitebalance-search'"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":6339,"output":1025,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":222925,"totalTokens":230289,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783183170536,"responseId":"msg_838447d5-0ede-46fd-bb52-97a6148a0bf2"}}
