{"type":"message","id":"eca5b8aa","parentId":"22835285","timestamp":"2026-07-04T16:52:05.323Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问精调的逻辑是什么。让我从代码中解释清楚精调（fine stage）的具体逻辑。\n\n从 whitebalance.py 代码中：\n\n精调是 stage 2，分为两个子阶段：\n- sub=0：同时调整R和B\n- sub=1：独立调整R或B\n\n让我详细解释这个逻辑。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"精调逻辑（stage 2）分为两个子阶段：\n\n## 精调流程图\n\n```\n进入精调（stage=2, step=±1）\n│\n├─► sub=0（同时调整R/B）\n│    │\n│    ├─ 计算候选：(cr, cb, \"both\"), (cr, current_blue, \"red\"), (current_red, cb, \"blue\")\n│    │\n│    ├─ 选delta最小者，应用到设备\n│    │\n│    ├─ 无改善计数：actual >= prev_best * 0.95 → no_improve++\n│    │\n│    └─ 停止条件：no_improve >= 2 或 fine_steps >= 5\n│         │\n│         └─► 进入 sub=1\n│\n├─► sub=1（独立调整）\n│    │\n│    ├─ 只算2个候选：(cr, current_blue, \"red\"), (current_red, cb, \"blue\")\n│    │   （不再同时调both）\n│    │\n│    ├─ 选delta最小者，应用\n│    │\n│    ├─ 停止条件：no_improve >= 3 或 fine_steps >= 5\n│         │\n│         └─► 停止，回滚到_best_red/_best_blue\n│              输出 \"done\"，切换locked模式\n│\n└─ 全程追踪：best_red, best_blue, best_delta\n```\n\n## 你的日志解读\n\n```\n#13: fine R=29 B=76 (sub=0阶段)\n#14: fine R=28 B=76 (sub=0阶段，进入sub=1)\n#15: done R=29 B=80 (sub=1结束，回滚到最佳)\n```\n\n**问题：sub=1只执行了1步就停止了？**\n\n代码逻辑：\n```python\nif self._no_improve >= 3 or self._fine_steps >= 5:\n    # 停止并回滚\n```\n\n你的日志显示 #14 → #15 只用了1步，这说明可能是 `no_improve >= 3` 条件触发了（之前累积的无改善次数）。\n\n**核心问题**：精调的停止条件可能触发过早，导致没有充分迭代。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":189763,"output":570,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":190333,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783183855553,"responseId":"cht000d676e@dx19f2e0afaa529c2503"}}
