{"type":"message","id":"5e2b9a55","parentId":"aa10e022","timestamp":"2026-07-04T17:20:22.289Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好，现在代码修改完成，死代码已清理。让我验证修改：\n\n1. ✅ 候选列表：精调阶段全部R/B独立，无\"both\"候选\n2. ✅ 进入精调时重置best\n3. ✅ 删除sub相关逻辑：`_fine_sub` 变量已删除，sub的if-else逻辑已简化为单一路径\n4. ✅ 精调停止条件：简化为单一条件 `no_improve >= 3 or fine_steps >= 10`（从5步增加到10步，允许更多迭代）\n\n现在需要更新版本号，从 v8.38 升级到 v8.40（跳过 v8.39 因为精调逻辑是v8.40修复的，v8.39主控台UI）。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"代码修改完成。现在更新版本号到 v8.40："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c8a9f857899a4441bf3720e4","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":10,"offset":1,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\main\\constants.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":55131,"output":234,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55365,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783185556347,"responseId":"cht000dfe06@dx19f2e25131029bb503"}}
