p\" onclick=\"stopAutoFocus()\" style=\"display:none;width:100%\">停止</button>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- 曝光模式 + 快门/光圈 (v5.47: 整合到一行) -->\r\n                                    <div class=\"form-group\" style=\"margin-bottom:4px\">\r\n                                        <label style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e\">曝光模式</label>\r\n                                        <select id=\"exposureMode\" style=\"width:100%;padding:4px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:12px\" onchange=\"setExposureMode(this.value);updateShutterIrisState()\">\r\n\n[1371 more lines in file. Use offset=300 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783186209564}}
{"type":"message","id":"92796d7e","parentId":"bfdaf83b","timestamp":"2026-07-04T17:30:16.617Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8d737300632b4c978d1e0d25","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":50,"offset":2920,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":59224,"output":47,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59271,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783186209565,"responseId":"cht000d7364@dx19f2e2e4c2d29c2503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a9d954db","parentId":"92796d7e","timestamp":"2026-07-04T17:30:16.659Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_8d737300632b4c978d1e0d25","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\r\n    // v8.11: 统一 ISAPI 截图 → 后端裁剪 → 迭代搜索 → 操作日志\r\n    function _finishRegion() {\r\n        var overlay = document.getElementById('regionOverlay');\r\n        var box = document.getElementById('regionBox');\r\n        var dev = window.connectedDevice;\r\n        if (!dev || !dev.ip) { showToast('error', '未连接设备'); _resetRegionUI(); return; }\r\n\r\n        var ow = overlay.offsetWidth, oh = overlay.offsetHeight;\r\n        var sx = parseInt(box.style.left) / ow;\r\n        var sy = parseInt(box.style.top) / oh;\r\n        var sw = parseInt(box.style.width) / ow;\r\n        var sh = parseInt(box.style.height) / oh;\r\n        if (sw < 0.01 || sh < 0.01) { showToast('warning', '框选区域太小'); _resetRegionUI(); return; }\r\n\r\n        var mode = _regionMode;\r\n        \r\n        // v8.39: 保存选区到 localStorage（白平衡和对焦分别保存）\r\n        var regionKey = 'region_' + mode;\r\n        localStorage.setItem(regionKey, JSON.stringify({ x: sx, y: sy, w: sw, h: sh }));\r\n        \r\n        var endpoint = mode === 'whitebalance' ? '/api/v1/vision/whitebalance-search'\r\n                                               : '/api/v1/vision/focus-search';\r\n        var label = mode === 'whitebalance' ? '白平衡' : '对焦';\r\n\r\n        _resetRegionUI();\r\n        showToast('info', label + '迭代中...');\r\n        operationLog('── ' + label + '迭代开始 ──', 'info');\r\n\r\n        // SSE 流式调用\r\n        var body = JSON.stringify({ x: sx, y: sy, w: sw, h: sh });\r\n        fetch(endpoint, { method: 'POST', headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' }, body: body })\r\n            .then(function(resp) {\r\n                if (!resp.ok) throw new Error('HTTP ' + resp.status);\r\n                var reader = resp.body.getReader();\r\n                var decoder = new TextDecoder();\r\n                var buf = '';\r\n                function pump() {\r\n                    return reader.read().then(function(r) {\r\n                        if (r.done) return;\r\n                        buf += decoder.decode(r.value, { stream: true });\r\n                        // 按 \\n\\n 分割事件\r\n                        var parts = buf.split('\\n\\n');\r\n                        buf = parts.pop();  // 最后一段可能不完整\r\n                        for (var i = 0; i < parts.length; i++) {\r\n                            var line = parts[i];\r\n                            if (!line.startsWith('data: ')) continue;\r\n                            try {\r\n                                var ev = JSON.parse(line.slice(6));\r\n                                if (ev.type === 'start') {\r\n\n[103 more lines in file. Use offset=2970 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783186216659}}
{"type":"message","id":"cd14b665","parentId":"a9d954db","timestamp":"2026-07-04T17:31:11.935Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好，现在我看到：\n\n1. `wbTimerInput` 和 `focusTimerInput` 都存在（lines 261, 290）\n2. `_finishRegion()` 函数保存选区到 localStorage（lines 2937-2938）\n3. 使用 `_regionMode` 作为 mode，调用对应的API endpoint\n\n现在我需要检查是否有定时器的逻辑。让我搜索一下是否有timer相关的代码。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_aaeac6d0134c431a919570e0","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path \"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\" -Pattern \"timer.*setInterval|setInterval.*timer|setTimeout\" -Context 0,2 | Select-Object -First 20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":60190,"output":150,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60340,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783186216660,"responseId":"cht000de5fd@dx19f2e2e6bb52872503"}}
