"0\" max=\"100\" value=\"0\" style=\"width:100%\" oninput=\"document.getElementById('gainVal').textContent=this.value\" onchange=\"setGain(this.value)\" disabled>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n\n[1338 more lines in file. Use offset=333 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783186750632}}
{"type":"message","id":"3d1c698a","parentId":"30e8b6f9","timestamp":"2026-07-04T17:40:08.208Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好，现在我需要：\n1. 看曝光模式的切换逻辑（setExposureMode函数）\n2. 看白平衡的UI更新逻辑（onWbModeChange函数）\n\n让我先修改UI部分，然后添加确认按钮。\n\n### 修改1：白平衡局部控制区域 - 添加确认按钮，移除上下箭头\n\n当前HTML：\n```html\n<button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" id=\"btnWbRegionSelect\" onclick=\"toggleRegionMode('whitebalance')\">框选</button>\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px\">\n    <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">定时:</span>\n    <input type=\"number\" id=\"wbTimerInput\" value=\"0\" min=\"0\" style=\"width:50px;padding:2px 4px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:11px\">\n    <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">分钟</span>\n</div>\n```\n\n修改为：\n```html\n<button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" id=\"btnWbRegionSelect\" onclick=\"toggleRegionMode('whitebalance')\">框选</button>\n<div style=\"display:flex;gap:4px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap\">\n    <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">定时:</span>\n    <input type=\"text\" id=\"wbTimerInput\" value=\"0\" style=\"width:50px;padding:2px 4px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:11px\" oninput=\"this.value=this.value.replace(/[^0-9]/g,'')\">\n    <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">分钟</span>\n    <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" onclick=\"confirmWbTimer()\">确认</button>\n</div>\n```\n\nI'll focus on modifying the HTML to add a confirm button and remove the number input arrows. The key changes include replacing `type=\"number\"` with `type=\"text\"` and using a regular expression to restrict input to numbers only.\n\nThe region component will have a step-based input mechanism with overflow handling. When the arrow is clicked, it increments or decrements the input value within a reachable range. The visibility of controls is dynamically managed based on the current mode through CSS classes. The current white balance mode is set to manual, and I'm preparing to verify the details in the `onWbModeChange` function.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"先读取相关的JS函数来了解当前逻辑。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_97fe68681163475b8385aaa8","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path \"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html\" -Pattern \"function setExposureMode|function onWbModeChange\" | Select-Object LineNumber"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":64555,"output":651,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65206,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783186750634,"responseId":"cht000dd754@dx19f2e368fd62872503"}}
