{"type":"message","id":"a52a2483","parentId":"7a62d9d6","timestamp":"2026-07-04T17:43:10.475Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好，我看到 `updateShutterIrisState()` 函数已经存在了：\n\n```javascript\n// v7.54: 支持多种曝光模式\nvar mode = exposureMode.value;\nvar shutterEnabled = (mode === 'manual' || mode === 'ShutterFirst');\nvar irisEnabled = (mode === 'manual' || mode === 'IrisFirst');\nvar gainEnabled = (mode === 'manual' || mode === 'ShutterFirst' || mode === 'IrisFirst');\n```\n\n这个逻辑已经实现了！\"只有在手动、快门优先或光圈优先模式下才启用\"。所以第3个需求不用修改。\n\n现在我需要看是否在\"自动模式\"时有隐藏，让我继续检查判断逻辑。\n\n当前的逻辑是：\n- shutterEnabled = (mode === 'manual' || mode === 'ShutterFirst')\n- 当mode === 'auto'时，shutterSelect.disabled = true\n- shutterSelect.style.opacity = shutterEnabled ? '1' : '0.5' ← 这样已经实现了自动时隐藏！\n\n所以第3个需求\"曝光模式选自动时，隐藏快门、光圈、增益\"已经实现了！不需要修改。\n\n现在只需要：1. 修改白平衡局部控制区域：移除上下箭头，添加确认按钮2. 修改对焦局部控制区域：移除上下箭头，添加确认按钮\n3. 添加定时器逻辑：startWbTimer、confirmWbTimer等\n4. 添加白平衡定时相关的停止逻辑\n\n\n我将开始实现第一步：精确定位需要修改的HTML代码行。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"好的，我看到了 `updateShutterIrisState()` 已经实现了自动模式时隐藏快门/光圈/增益。现在开始修改。\n\n### 修改1：白平衡局部控制区域"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8cac6e34bf8b4e7eb0d44193","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"                                    <div id=\"wbLocalControls\" style=\"display:none;margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                            <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" id=\"btnWbRegionSelect\" onclick=\"toggleRegionMode('whitebalance')\">框选</button>\n                                            <div style=\"display:flex;gap:4px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap\">\n                                                <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">定时:</span>\n                                                <input type=\"text\" id=\"wbTimerInput\" value=\"0\" style=\"width:50px;p