{"type":"message","id":"3e0e1f5b","parentId":"359c0778","timestamp":"2026-07-04T19:33:05.121Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我需要在 whitebalance_search 端点之前添加全局变量。让我找到合适的位置插入全局变量的定义。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"在现有代码中添加全局变量。我需要在 `whitebalance_search` 之前添加全局变量："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_33409381945842e7bb5594e7","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"\n# v8.41: 搜索器全局变量\n_wb_searcher = None\n_focus_searcher = None\n\n\n@api_router.post(\"/vision/whitebalance-search\", summary=\"白平衡迭代搜索 (SSE)\", tags=[\"Vision\"])","oldText":"@api_router.post(\"/vision/whitebalance-search\", summary=\"白平衡迭代搜索 (SSE)\", tags=[\"Vision\"])"},{"newText":"    searcher = WhiteBalanceSearcher(\n        mgr=mgr, device_ip=device_ip, client=client,\n        x=x, y=y, w=w, h=h,\n        capture_func=_capture_and_crop,\n        cleanup_func=_cleanup_temp\n    )\n    \n    # v8.41: 保存搜索器到全局变量\n    global _wb_searcher\n    _wb_searcher = searcher\n    \n    return StreamingResponse(\n        searcher.run(),\n        media_type=\"text/event-stream\",\n        headers={\"Cache-Control\": \"no-cache\", \"X-Accel-Buffering\": \"no\"}\n    )\n\n\n@api_router.post(\"/vision/whitebalance-stop\", summary=\"停止白平衡搜索 (SSE)\", tags=[\"Vision\"])\nasync def whitebalance_stop():\n    \"\"\"停止当前白平衡搜索并写入最佳值到设备\"\"\"\n    global _wb_searcher\n    if not _wb_searcher:\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"无活跃的白平衡搜索\"}\n    \n    # v8.41: 调用中断方法\n    _wb_searcher._interrupt()\n    \n    # 清除全局引用\n    _wb_searcher = None\n    \n    return {\"success\": True, \"message\": \"白平衡搜索已停止\"}","oldText":"    searcher = WhiteBalanceSearcher(\n        mgr=mgr, device_ip=device_ip, client=client,\n        x=x, y=y, w=w, h=h,\n        capture_func=_capture_and_crop,\n        cleanup_func=_cleanup_temp\n    )\n    \n    return StreamingResponse(\n        searcher.run(),\n        media_type=\"text/event-stream\",\n        headers={\"Cache-Contr