{"type":"message","id":"72315b4f","parentId":"4b2a6b4c","timestamp":"2026-07-04T19:48:04.039Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在添加按钮状态管理函数，并修改 confirmWbTimer/confirmFocusTimer 以在定时器启动后更新按钮状态："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b0c2f0e515e84665aa43a798","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":50,"offset":1270,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":51051,"output":75,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51126,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783194473255,"responseId":"cht000d40bb@dx19f2eac6d6429c2503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6221987e","parentId":"72315b4f","timestamp":"2026-07-04T19:48:04.085Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_b0c2f0e515e84665aa43a798","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    selectBtn.style.opacity = '1';\r\n    stopFocusTimer();\r\n}\r\n\r\n// v8.40: 白平衡定时器\r\nfunction confirmWbTimer() {\r\n    var input = document.getElementById('wbTimerInput');\r\n    if (!input) return;\r\n    var minutes = parseInt(input.value) || 0;\r\n    if (minutes <= 0) {\r\n        stopWbTimer();\r\n        showToast('warning', '请输入大于0的分钟数');\r\n        return;\r\n    }\r\n    var region = localStorage.getItem('region_whitebalance');\r\n    if (!region) {\r\n        showToast('warning', '请先框选区域');\r\n        return;\r\n    }\r\n    stopWbTimer();\r\n    wbTimerSeconds = minutes * 60;\r\n    updateWbTimerDisplay();\r\n    wbTimerId = setInterval(function() {\r\n        wbTimerSeconds--;\r\n        updateWbTimerDisplay();\r\n        if (wbTimerSeconds <= 0) {\r\n            clearInterval(wbTimerId);\r\n            wbTimerId = null;\r\n            executeScheduledSearch('whitebalance');\r\n        }\r\n    }, 1000);\r\n    showToast('success', '白平衡定时已启动: ' + minutes + '分钟');\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction stopWbTimer() {\r\n    if (wbTimerId) { clearInterval(wbTimerId); wbTimerId = null; }\r\n    wbTimerSeconds = 0;\r\n    var display = document.getElementById('wbTimerDisplay');\r\n    if (display) display.textContent = '';\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction updateWbTimerDisplay() {\r\n    var display = document.getElementById('wbTimerDisplay');\r\n    if (!display) return;\r\n    if (wbTimerSeconds <= 0) { display.textContent = ''; return; }\r\n    var m = Math.floor(wbTimerSeconds / 60);\r\n    var s = wbTimerSeconds % 60;\r\n    display.textContent = '(' + m + ':' + (s < 10 ? '0' : '') + s + ')';\r\n}\r\n\r\n\n[554 more lines in file. Use offset=1320 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783194484085}}
{"type":"message","id":"f65219af","parentId":"6221987e","timestamp":"2026-07-04T19:48:38.982Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我需要：\n1. 添加 `updateWbConfirmBtn()` 函数：根据定时值更新确认按钮状态\n2. 添加 `updateFocusConfirmBtn()` 函数：根据定时值更新确认按钮状态\n3. 在 `confirmWbTimer()` 中，启动定时器后调用 `updateWbConfirmBtn()`\n4. 在 `confirmFocusTimer()` 中，启动定时器后调用 `updateFocusConfirmBtn()`\n5. 修改 `onWbModeChange()` 和 `onFocusModeChange()` 以在模式切换后调用按钮状态更新\n6. 在 index.html 中监听 interrupt 事件\n\n让我先添加按钮状态管理函数。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8df895f39ca74225b17f1ebd","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"function updateWbConfirmBtn() {\n    var btn = document.getElementById('btnWbTimerConfirm');\n    var stopBtn = document.getElementById('btnWbLocalStop');\n    var input = document.getElementById('wbTimerInput');\n    var isSearching = stopBtn.disabled === false;\n    var minutes = parseInt(input.value) || 0;\n    \n    if (!btn) return;\n    // 定时值>0且搜索未运行时，按钮可用，否则灰色\n    if (minutes > 0 && !isSearching) {\n        btn.disabled = false;\n        btn.style.opacity = '1';\n    } else {\n        btn.disabled = true;\n        btn.style.opacity = '0.5';\n    }\n}\n\nfunction updateFocusConfirmBtn() {\n    var btn = document.getElementById('btnFocusTimerConfirm');\n    var stopBtn = document.getElementById('btnFocusLocalStop');\n    var input = document.getElementById('focusTimerInput');\n    var isSearching = stopBtn.disabled === false;\n    var minutes = parseInt(input.value) || 0;\n    \n    if (!btn) return;\n    if (minutes > 0 && !isSearching) {\n        btn.disabled = false;\n        btn.style.opacity = '1';\n    } else {\n        btn.disabled = true;\n        btn.style.opacity = '0.5';\n    }\n}\n\n// v8.40: 白平衡定时器\nfunction confirmWbTimer() {\n    updateWbConfirmBtn();  // 确认按钮状态\n    var input = document.getElementById('wbTimerInput');\n    if (!input) return;\n    var minutes = parseInt(input.value) || 0;\n    if (minutes <= 0) {\n        stopWbTimer();\n        showToast('warning', '请输入大于0的分钟数');\n        return;\n    }\n    var region = localStorage.getItem('region_whitebalance');\n    if (!region) {\n        showToast('warning', '请先框选区域');\n        return;\n    }\n    stopWbTimer();\n    wbTimerSeconds = minutes * 60;\n    updateWbTimerDisplay();\n    wbTimerId = setInterval(function() {\n        wbTimerSeconds--;\n        updateWbTimerDisplay();\n        if (wbTimerSeconds <= 0) {\n            clearInterval(wbTimerId);\n            wbTimerId = null;\n            executeScheduledSearch('whitebalance');\n        }\n    }, 1000);\n    updateWbConfirmBtn();  // 重置按钮状态\n    showToast('success', '白平衡定时已启动: ' + minutes + '分钟');\n}","oldText":"function confirmWbTimer() {\n    var input = document.getElementById('wbTimerInput');\n    if (!input) return;\n    var minutes = parseInt(input.value) || 0;\n    if (minutes <= 0) {\n        stopWbTimer();\n        showToast('warning', '请输入大于0的分钟数');\n        return;\n    }\n    var region = localStorage.getItem('region_whitebalance');\n    if (!region) {\n        showToast('warning', '请先框选区域');\n        return;\n    }\n    stopWbTimer();\n    wbTimerSeconds = minutes * 60;\n    updateWbTimerDisplay();\n    wbTimerId = setInterval(function() {\n        wbTimerSeconds--;\n        updateWbTimerDisplay();\n        if (wbTimerSeconds <= 0) {\n            clearInterval(wbTimerId);\n            wbTimerId = null;\n            executeScheduledSearch('whitebalance');\n        }\n    }, 1000);\n    showToast('success', '白平衡定时已启动: ' + minutes + '分钟');\n}"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":51860,"output":1047,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52907,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783194484086,"responseId":"cht000dc5f2@dx19f2eac7d6d29bb50