{"type":"message","id":"44c3c2cb","parentId":"c6569cf0","timestamp":"2026-07-04T19:52:21.985Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_cc5868729b1f4a2a83b3a71f","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"                            var ev = JSON.parse(line.slice(6));\r\n                            if (ev.type === 'wb' || ev.type === 'focus') {\r\n                                operationLog('调整 #' + ev.step + ': ' + ev.stage + ' R=' + ev.red_gain + ' B=' + ev.blue_gain + ' Δ=' + ev.delta, 'info');\r\n                            } else if (ev.type === 'done') {\r\n                                operationLog('── ' + label + '完成: R=' + ev.final_red + ' B=' + ev.final_blue + ' (' + ev.total_steps + '步) ──', 'success');\r\n                            } else if (ev.type === 'error') {\r\n                                operationLog(label + '错误: ' + ev.message, 'error');\r\n                            }\r\n                        } catch (e) {}\r\n                    }\r\n                    return pump();\r\n                });\r\n            }\r\n            return pump();\r\n        })\r\n        .then(function() {\r\n            // 执行完成后，重新启动定时器\r\n            if (mode === 'whitebalance' && wbTimerId === null) {\r\n                var minutes = parseInt(document.getElementById('wbTimerInput').value) || 0;\r\n                if (minutes > 0) {\r\n                    wbTimerSeconds = minutes * 60;\r\n                    updateWbTimerDisplay();\r\n                    wbTimerId = setInterval(function() {\r\n                        wbTimerSeconds--;\r\n                        updateWbTimerDisplay();\r\n                        if (wbTimerSeconds <= 0) {\r\n                            clearInterval(wbTimerId);\r\n                            wbTimerId = null;\r\n                            executeScheduledSearch('whitebalance');\r\n                        }\r\n                    }, 1000);\r\n                }\r\n            }\r\n            if (mode === 'focus' && focusTimerId === null) {\r\n                var minutes = parseInt(document.getElementById('focusTimerInput').value) || 0;\r\n                if (minutes > 0) {\r\n                    focusTimerSeconds = minutes * 60;\r\n                    updateFocusTimerDisplay();\r\n                    focusTimerId = setInterval(function() {\r\n                        focusTimerSeconds--;\r\n                        updateFocusTimerDisplay();\r\n                        if (focusTimerSeconds <= 0) {\r\n                            clearInterval(focusTimerId);\r\n                            focusTimerId = null;\r\n                            executeScheduledSearch('focus');\r\n                        }\r\n                    }, 1000);\r\n                }\r\n            }\r\n        })\r\n\n[427 more lines in file. Use offset=1487 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783194741985}}
{"type":"message","id":"ce4dd6ec","parentId":"44c3c2cb","timestamp":"2026-07-04T19:52:36.097Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我看到了 `executeScheduledSearch` 函数。这个函数处理定时器调度。在定时执行时也应该有停止按钮逻辑。但由于这是一个简化的SSE处理（只显示事件日志，不处理所有的UI状态），我应该确保在定时执行时停止按钮应该处于可用状态。\n\n不过，由于 `executeScheduledSearch` 调用的是与 `_finishRegion` 相同的 API 端点，而 `_finishRegion` 已经处理了停止按钮的启用（在搜索启动时），所以 `executeScheduledSearch` 不需要额外处理按钮状态。\n\n现在让我检查是否所有的修改都已完成。已完成的修改：\n\n1. whitebalance.py - 添加 `_interrupted` 和 `_interrupt` 方法，修改 `run()` 循环中断逻辑\n2. autofocus.py - 添加 `_interrupted` 和 `_interrupt` 方法，修改 `run()` 循环中断逻辑\n3. router.py - 添加全局变量 `_wb_searcher` 和 `_focus_searcher`，修改白平衡和对焦搜索端点保存 searcher 实例，添加 `/api/v1/vision/whitebalance-stop` 和 `/api/v1/vision/focus-stop` 规则\n4. console.html - 修改白平衡和对焦局部控制UI为emoji按钮，停止按钮移到确认按钮右侧，修改停止函数调用新端点，添加按钮状态管理函数 `updateWbConfirmBtn` 和 `updateFocusConfirmBtn`，修改 `confirmWbTimer` 和 `confirmFocusTimer` 在启动定时器后更新按钮状态\n\n\n5. index.html - 在 `_finishRegion` 中搜索启动时启用停止按钮，SSE 事件处理中监听 `interrupt` 事件，在 done 事件、error 事件、interrupt 事件、catch 中恢复停止按钮为灰色\n\n我已经完成了对白平衡和定时调度流程的全面改进。关键操作包括添加全局变量、实现中断逻辑、优化UI交互和事件处理。这将提升系统的灵活性和用户体验。\n\n接下来需要仔细核查 `onWbModeChange` 和 `onFocusModeChange` 函数，确保按钮状态能按预期更新，为新功能做好准备。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"所有前端修改已完成。现在启动 AstroHub 服务器进行功能测试。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_862d9c4bb9184a7aa7a784ca","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub && tasklist | findstr python.exe"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":63035,"output":497,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63532,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783194741988,"responseId":"cht000dff18@dx19f2eb06ed22872503"}}
