{"type":"message","id":"e47418a2","parentId":"ab801d5b","timestamp":"2026-07-04T20:16:30.168Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"老板要求：\n1. 当选择局部对焦、局部白平衡时，时间输入窗口、停止、确认按钮需要并列在一排\n2. 减小按钮大小 -15%\n3. 时间输入框缩短20%\n\n当前的布局是：\n```html\n<button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\">🔲</button>\n<div style=\"display:flex;gap:4px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap\">\n    <span>定时:</span>\n    <input type=\"text\" ... width:50px ...>\n    <span>分钟</span>\n    <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\">✅</button>\n    <button class=\"btn btn-danger btn-sm\">🛑</button>\n    <span>倒计时</span>\n</div>\n```\n\n老板要求：\n1. 确认、停止、定时输入框要并列在一排\n2. 按钮缩小15%\n\n我需要修改 CSS，给按钮添加 `transform: scale(0.85)` 或调整 `padding` 和 `width`。\n按钮大小 -15% 可以通过调整 `font-size` -15%、`padding` -15%\n或给按钮类添加 `transform: scale(0.85)` 或者调整 CSS 的宽度。\n\n实际上 `btn btn-sm` 是 Tailwind 类，我需要检查是否可以通过调整类来缩小按钮。\n或者我可以通过内联样式直接调整按钮的大小。\n\n时间输入框需要减少 20% 的宽度，当前是 `width:50px`，改为 `width:40px`。\n\n让我修改代码：\n\n```html\n<button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" style=\"transform: scale(0.85);\">🔲</button>\n<div style=\"display:flex;gap:4px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n    <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:10px\">定时:</span>\n    <input type=\"text\" ... width:40px style=\"transform: scale(0.85);\" ...>\n    <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:10px\">分钟</span>\n    <button id=\"btnWbTimerConfirm\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" style=\"transform: scale(0.85);\" onclick=\"confirmWbTimer()\" disabled style=\"opacity:0.5\">✅</button>\n    <button id=\"btnWbLocalStop\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-sm\" style=\"transform: scale(0.85);\" onclick=\"stopAutoWhiteBalance()\" disabled style=\"opacity:0.5\">🛑</button>\n</div>\n```\n\n我将在定时和停止按钮上应用缩放变换，使其视觉大小减少 15%。具体实现是通过 `transform: scale(0.85)` 来调整按钮的显示尺寸。\n\n对于输入框，我选择直接修改宽度属性为 40px，以实现 20% 的宽度缩减。这样可以更精确地控制布局变化。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"老板要求修改布局：\n1. 定时、确认、停止按钮并列在一排\n2. 按钮缩小15%\n3. 定时输入框缩短20%\n\n开始修改："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fad3ff8a9cfc4994b73e9c47","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"                                    <div id=\"wbLocalControls\" style=\"display:none;margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                            <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onclick=\"toggleRegionMode('whitebalance')\">🔲</button>\n                                            <div style=\"display:flex;gap:3px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;transform: scale(0.85);\">\n                                                <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">定时:</span>\n                                                <input type=\"text\" id=\"wbTimerInput\" value=\"0\" style=\"width:40px;padding:2px 4px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:4px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:11px\" oninput=\"this.value=this.value.replace(/[^0-9]/g,'');updateWbConfirmBtn()\">\n                                                <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:11px\">分钟</span>\n                                                <button id=\"btnWbTimerConfirm\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" onclick=\"confirmWbTimer()\" disabled style=\"opacity:0.5\">✅</button>\n                                                <button id=\"btnWbLocalStop\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-sm\" onclick=\"stopAutoWhiteBalance()\" disabled style=\"opacity:0.5\">🛑</button>\n                                                <span id=\"wbTimerDisplay\" style=\"color:#f85149;font-size:11px\"></span>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>","oldText":"                                    <div id=\"wbLocalControls\" style=\"display:none;margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-