{"type":"compaction","id":"80db398f","parentId":"572e9827","timestamp":"2026-07-04T20:21:55.860Z","summary":"## Decisions\n- **方案B (Searcher中断)**: 用户确认采用方案B，在 `WhiteBalanceSearcher` 和 `FocusSearcher` 中增加 `_interrupt()` 方法，router.py 注册新端点\n- **停止端点路径**: 新增 `/api/v1/vision/whitebalance-stop` 和 `/api/v1/vision/focus-stop`，在白平衡和对焦脚本中实现，不在PTZ中\n- **白平衡停止逻辑**: 中断搜索 + 写入当前R/B值到设备 + 切换到锁定白平衡模式\n- **对焦停止逻辑**: 中断搜索流程\n- **操作日志**: 停止按钮按下后在 index 操作日志中提示\"用户停止\"，实现方式与其他信息提示一致，禁止过度开发\n- **按钮emoji化**: 框选→🔲, 确认→✅, 停止→🛑\n- **按钮状态管理**: 定时时间未变化时确认按钮灰色不可用；框选未启动时停止按钮灰色不可用\n- v8.40已完成: 精调全R/B独立、定时局部白平衡/对焦、曝光模式自动隐藏、定时器UI\n\n## Open TODOs\n1. `whitebalance.py`: 增加 `_interrupt()` 方法 + 修改 `run()` 支持中断\n2. `autofocus.py`: 增加 `_interrupt()` 方法 + 修改 `run()` 支持中断（已有 `_stop_focus()` 在 line 343）\n3. `router.py`: 新增 `/api/v1/vision/whitebalance-stop` 和 `/api/v1/vision/focus-stop` \n\n[Compaction summary truncated to fit budget]\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Goal\nImplement user-interruptible luminance and focus auto-adjustment with proper backend and frontend integration.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Execute changes automatically without requiring continuous user interaction\n- Use new `/api/v1/vision/whitebalance-stop` and `/api/v1/vision/focus-stop` endpoints\n- Override old PTZ endpoints\n- Only use built-in AstroHub commands (e.g., `taskkill`, background execution)\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- **Backend (whitebalance.py):** Added `_interrupted` property and `_interrupt()` method; modified `run()` loop to break on `self._interrupted`\n- **Backend (autofocus.py):** Added `_interrupted` property and `_interrupt()` method; modified `run()` loop to break on `self._interrupted`\n- **Backend (router.py):** Added global variables `_wb_searcher` and `_focus_searcher` to store searcher instances; added route `/api/v1/vision/whitebalance-stop` to call `wb_searcher._interrupt()`; added route `/api/v1/vision/focus-stop` to call `focus_searcher._interrupt()`\n- **Frontend (console.html):**\n  - Changed button text from \"框选\" to emoji (🔲) for local controls\n  - Moved \"停止\" button from separate block to right of \"确认\" button\n  - Modified `stopAutoWhiteBalance()` to call `/api/v1/vision/whitebalance-stop`, log \"用户停止\", and disable buttons\n  - Modified `stopAutoFocus()` to call `/api/v1/vision/focus-stop`, log \"用户停止\", and disable buttons\n  - Added `updateWbConfirmBtn()` and `updateFocusConfirmBtn()` to toggle confirm button disabled state based on timer input value\n  - Modified `confirmWbTimer()` to call `updateWbConfirmBtn()` before starting and after starting timer\n  - Modified `confirmFocusTimer()` to call `updateFocusConfirmBtn()` before starting and after starting timer\n- **Frontend (index.html):**\n  - In `_finishRegion()`: add code to enable stop button at search start\n  - In SSE event handlers: added logic to restore buttons to disabled/grayed state on `done`, `error`, and `interrupt` events\n  - In `catch`: added logic to restore buttons to disabled/grayed state\n- **Server:** Restarted AstroHub\n\n### In Progress\n- Server is starting and may need final verification that HTTP listener is ready and all routes are loaded\n\n### Blocked\n- None. Changes are complete and server is restarting.\n\n## Decisions\n- revert to pure vision API endpoints (`/api/v1/vision/...`) instead of PTZ (`/api/v1/ptz/...`) to separate concerns\n- maintain backward compatibility by only changing frontend stop button placement and text to show visual changes to `toggleRegionMode` logic\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Wait for AstroHub startup to complete (listening on port 10280)\n2. Verify that the Web UI loads with updated buttons/controls\n3. Test the interrupt flow by:\n   - Selecting a region for whitebalance/focus\n   - Enabling search\n   - Clicking \"停止\" button\n   - Confirming that backend interrupt is logged and buttons reset\n4. Optionally test manual mode changes to `onWbModeChange()`/`onFocusModeChange()` for button state updates (not yet modified)\n\n## Critical Context\n- Server running at `http://localhost:10280` (port 10280)\n- Process ID: 35920 (previous), restarting (current session: batch task)\n- Device: 192.168.5.72 (iDS-2DF8C832IXS-A)\n- Modified files:\n  - `whitebalance.py`\n  - `autofocus.py`\n  - `src/web/main.py` (router)\n  - `src/web/includes/console.html`\n  - `src/web/index.html`\n\n## Decisions\n- Use emoji symbols for UI buttons to reduce text clutter\n- Centralize button disabled style management via `disabled` attribute and `opacity: 0.5`\n\n## Open TODOs\n- Test the actual interrupt functionality once server is ready\n- (Optional) Update `onWbModeChange()` and `onFocusModeChange()` to call `updateWbConfirmBtn()` and `updateFocusConfirmBtn()` respectively\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- Automatic execution mode: \"别让我一直盯着你\"\n- Must use new vision endpoints\n\n## Pending user asks\n- \"继续，自动执行\" (Continue, run automatically)\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- Ports: `10280`\n- Paths: `C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html`, `C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html`\n- Functions: `stopAutoWhiteBalance()`, `stopAutoFocus()`, `confirmWbTimer()`, `confirmFocusTimer()`, `updateWbConfirmBtn()`, `updateFocusConfirmBtn()`\n- API routes: `/api/v1/vision/whitebalance-stop`, `/api/v1/vision/focus-stop`\n- Device IP: `192.168.5.72`\n- Device Model: `iDS-2DF8C832IXS-A`\n- SADP message: `[SADP] [DLL Alias] libcrypto-1_1.dll 已存在且大小一致 (2969600 bytes)`\n- Timestamps: `Sun 2026-07-05 03:52:48 GMT+8`\n\n## Recent turns preserved verbatim\n- User: Note: The previous agent run was aborted by the user. Resume carefully or ask for clarification.\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"45891\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-07-05 03:20 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n