{"type":"message","id":"11652a77","parentId":"6aeef6a7","timestamp":"2026-07-04T20:45:42.278Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"45973\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-07-05 04:45 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n现在调整：\n1. 台哦正变焦- 变焦+的宽度，两者加起来的整体宽度等于PTZ方向控制的总宽度。\n2. 白平衡、对焦的局部选项打开后，下方出现的框选按钮、定时、应用、取消按钮，统一高度，按钮统一大小。定时的字体也需要统一大小，文本输入框要和下拉菜单一样的高度。这一排的总宽度等于上方下拉菜单的宽度\n3. 修改4按钮，框选使用文字，应用使用对勾emoji，不是现在的复选框+对勾。停止使用和码流停止相同的emoji。"}],"timestamp":1783197942269}}
{"type":"message","id":"1511cd4f","parentId":"11652a77","timestamp":"2026-07-04T20:46:10.875Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"老板提出了三个需求：\n\n1. 变焦-和变焦+按钮宽度调整：\n   - 两者加起来的整体宽度 = PTZ方向控制的总宽度\n\n让我先看看PTZ方向控制的总宽度。从之前的代码可以看到，PTZ方向控制容器宽度是宽加载lot的。\n\n从console.html中：\n- 左侧：方向控制 + 速度滑动条\n- 方向控制是9个按钮：\n```\n<button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('up-left')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('up-left')\">↖</button>\n<button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('up')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('up')\">↑</button>\n<button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('up-right')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('up-right')\">↗</button>\n<button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('left')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('left')\">←</button>\n<button class=\"ptz-btn\" onclick=\"ptzHome()\" title=\"归位\">🏠</button>\n<button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('right')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('right')\">→</button>\n<button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('down-left')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('down-left')\">↙</button>\n<button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('down')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('down')\">↓</button>\n<button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('down-right')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('down-right')\">↘</button>\n\n\n```\n\n宽度需要调整为170px，可以通过flex:1、padding或inline-style设置。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"收到，调整三个问题：\n\n1. 变焦按钮宽度 = PTZ方向控制总宽度（方向9个按钮容器）\n2. 白平衡/对焦局部选项：框选、定时、应用、取消4按钮统一高度 + 按钮统一大小 + 定时输入框高度=下拉菜单高度 + 整体宽度=上方面拉菜单宽度\n3. 按钮文字/emoji：\n   - 框选 → 框选\n   - 应用 → ❎\n   - 停止 → ⏹️\n\n开始修改："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c5fd75323bef444d8a534baf","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":25,"offset":20,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":81626,"output":552,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82178,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"sto