{"type":"message","id":"d866ece9","parentId":"740323b4","timestamp":"2026-07-04T20:49:35.033Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_6c39d39cfe8e4b9f9d80b467","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":".collapsible-section {\r\n    background: #161b22;\r\n    border: 1px solid #21262d;\r\n    border-radius: 8px;\r\n    margin-bottom: 12px;\r\n    overflow: hidden;\r\n}\r\n.collapsible-header {\r\n    display: flex;\r\n    justify-content: space-between;\r\n    align-items: center;\r\n    padding: 10px 12px;\r\n    cursor: pointer;\r\n    background: #0d1117;\r\n    transition: background 0.2s;\r\n}\r\n.collapsible-header:hover {\r\n    background: #161b22;\r\n}\r\n.collapse-icon {\r\n    color: #8b949e;\r\n    font-size: 12px;\r\n    transition: transform 0.2s;\r\n}\r\n.collapsible-section.collapsed .collapse-icon {\r\n    transform: rotate(-90deg);\r\n}\r\n.collapsible-content {\r\n    padding: 12px;\r\n    max-height: 1000px;\r\n    overflow: hidden;\r\n    transition: max-height 0.3s ease-out, padding 0.3s;\r\n}\r\n.collapsible-section.collapsed .collapsible-content {\r\n    max-height: 0;\r\n    padding: 0 12px;\r\n}\r\n.section-subtitle {\r\n    font-size: 12px;\r\n    color: #6e7681;\r\n    margin: 8px 0 4px;\r\n    padding-top: 8px;\r\n    border-top: 1px solid #21262d;\r\n}\r\n.section-subtitle:first-child {\r\n    border-top: none;\r\n    padding-top: 0;\r\n}\r\n\r\n/* v7.55: PTZ信息方块样式 */\r\n.info-block {\r\n    background: #0d1117;\r\n    border: 1px solid #30363d;\r\n    border-radius: 6px;\r\n    padding: 6px;\r\n    display: flex;\r\n    flex-direction: column;\r\n    gap: 4px;\r\n}\r\n.info-row {\r\n    display: flex;\r\n    justify-content: space-between;\r\n    align-items: center;\r\n    padding: 4px 8px;\r\n    font-size: 13px;\r\n}\r\n.info-row-2val {\r\n    display: flex;\r\n    justify-content: space-between;\r\n    gap: 8px;\r\n}\r\n.info-row-2val > div {\r\n    flex: 1;\r\n    display: flex;\r\n    justify-content: space-between;\r\n    align-items: center;\r\n    padding: 3px 6px;\r\n    font-size: 11px;\r\n}\r\n.info-label {\r\n    color: #8b949e;\r\n    font-weight: 500;\r\n}\r\n.info-value {\r\n    color: #58a6ff;\r\n    font-weight: 600;\r\n}\r\n.info-label-sm {\r\n    color: #8b949e;\r\n    font-size: 10px;\r\n}\r\n.info-value-sm {\r\n    color: #58a6ff;\r\n    font-size: 10px;\r\n}\r\n/* v7.57: PTZ信息横向一行 */\r\n.info-row-h {\r\n    display: flex;\r\n    align-items: center;\r\n    justify-content: center;\r\n\n[1423 more lines in file. Use offset=495 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783198175033}}
{"type":"message","id":"1251038d","parentId":"d866ece9","timestamp":"2026-07-04T20:50:44.351Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，现在我知道了：\n- `.collapsible-content` padding: 12px\n- `.console-left` 宽度 320px\n\n所以白平衡/对焦下拉菜单的可用宽度是：320px - 双边padding 24px = 296px\n\n等等，下拉菜单宽度100%，在collapsible-content中，collapsible-content的padding是12px，所以下拉菜单宽度是：\n320px - 12px * 2 = 296px\n\n现在开始修改：\n\n修改1：变焦按钮宽度 170px → 154px（PTZ方向控制总宽度：3×48 + 2×5 = 154px）\n\n修改2：白平衡/对焦局部控制区域\n- 框选、定时、应用、取消4按钮统一高度（高度需要和下拉菜单一样，但按钮是按钮，下拉菜单有padding）\n- 我理解成：按钮高度统一，且高度要和下拉菜单高度一致\n- 按钮统一大小（.btn-sm 的 padding: 6px 12px, font-size: 12px）\n- 定时输入框高度 = 下拉菜单高度（padding: 10px 12px, font-size: 13px - 等等，input没有font-size设置，默认16px会覆盖）\n- 整体宽度需要设置，应该和上方的白平衡/对焦下拉菜单宽度一致\n\n\n- 对齐方式：按钮和输入框需要垂直居中对齐\n\n我需要仔细对齐元素，确保视觉上统一协调。容器宽度设置为约296px，让四个按钮和输入框在同一行显示，并保持垂直居中。按钮高度、padding和font-size都要统一，定时的输入框要调整高度以匹配下拉菜单。\n\n码流停止按钮现在用波形符号表示，新增停止功能也需要类似的emoji样式。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"好的，现在开始修改。我需要理解完整的需求：\n\n**需求1**：变焦-和变焦+总宽度 = PTZ方向控制总宽度\n- PTZ方向控制：3列×48px + 2个gap=5px = 154px\n\n**需求2**：白平衡/对焦局部控制区域\n- 4个按钮（框选、定时文字、应用❎、停止码流停止⏹）统一高度\n- 按钮统一大小（.btn-sm）\n- 定时输入框高度 = 下拉菜单高度\n- 整体宽度 = 上方下拉菜单宽度\n\n让我开始修改console.html。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2467278f125241289b267cbe","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"                                        <div style=\"width:154px;display:flex;gap:4px;margin-top:4px\">\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" style=\"flex:1;width:auto;height:24px;padding:1px;font-size:11px;line-height:1.2\" onmousedown=\"ptzZoom('out')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzZoom('out')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" onmouseleave=\"ptzStop()\" title=\"变焦-\">变焦-</button>\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" style=\"flex:1;width:auto;height:24px;padding:1px;font-size:11px;line-height:1.2\" onmousedown=\"ptzZoom('in')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzZoom('in')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" onmouseleave=\"ptzStop()\" title=\"变焦+\">变焦+</button>\n                                        </div>","oldText":"                                        <div style=\"width:170px;display:flex;gap:4px;margin-top:4px\">\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" style=\"flex:1;width:auto;height:24px;padding:1px;font-size:11px;line-height:1.2\" onmousedown=\"ptzZoom('out')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzZoom('out')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" onmouseleave=\"ptzStop()\" title=\"变焦-\">变焦-</button>\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" style=\"flex:1;width:auto;height:24px;padding:1px;font-size:11px;line-height:1.2\" onmousedown=\"ptzZoom('in')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzZoom('in')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" onmouseleave=\"ptzStop()\" title=\"变焦+\">变焦+</button>\n                                        </div>"},{"newText":"                                    <!-- 局部白平衡控制(仅局部模式显示) -->\n                                    <div id=\"wbLocalControls\" style=\"display:none;margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                        <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px\">\n                                            <div style=\"display:flex;gap:6px;justify-content:center;width:100%\">\n                                                <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onclick=\"toggleRegionMode('whitebalance')\">框选</button>\n                                                <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:3px;width:calc(100% - 80px);flex:1\">\n                                                    <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:12px\">定时:</span>\n                                                    <input type=\"text\" id=\"wbTimerInput\" value=\"0\" style=\"flex:1;padding:10px 12px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:6px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:13px\" oninput=\"this.value=this.value.replace(/[^0-9]/g,'');updateWbConfirmBtn()\">\n                                                    <span style=\"color:#8b949e