{"type":"message","id":"9113fcc7","parentId":"bd6afa6d","timestamp":"2026-07-04T21:05:36.240Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f9218401bef245f79e4fce69","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"                                            <span id=\"ptzSpeedVal\" style=\"font-size:11px\">4</span>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div style=\"width:154px;display:flex;gap:4px;margin-top:4px\">\r\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" style=\"flex:1;width:auto;height:24px;padding:1px;font-size:11px;line-height:1.2\" onmousedown=\"ptzZoom('out')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzZoom('out')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" onmouseleave=\"ptzStop()\" title=\"变焦-\">变焦-</button>\r\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" style=\"flex:1;width:auto;height:24px;padding:1px;font-size:11px;line-height:1.2\" onmousedown=\"ptzZoom('in')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzZoom('in')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" onmouseleave=\"ptzStop()\" title=\"变焦+\">变焦+</button>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <!-- 右侧:光圈快门 + P/T/Z(竖排,宽度减少15%) -->\r\n                                    <div style=\"flex:0 0 110px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0\">\r\n                                        <div class=\"info-block\" style=\"flex:1\">\r\n                                            <div class=\"info-row\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;padding:1px 4px;font-size:12px\"><span class=\"info-label\">光圈</span><span class=\"info-value\" id=\"ptzIris\">--</span></div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"info-row\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;padding:1px 4px;font-size:12px\"><span class=\"info-label\">快门</span><span class=\"info-value\" id=\"ptzShutter\">--</span></div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"info-row\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;padding:1px 4px;font-size:12px\"><span class=\"info-label\">R</span><span class=\"info-value\" id=\"ptzWbR\">--</span></div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"info-row\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;padding:1px 4px;font-size:12px\"><span class=\"info-label\">B</span><span class=\"info-value\" id=\"ptzWbB\">--</span></div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"info-row\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #30363d;padding:1px 4px;font-size:12px\"><span class=\"info-label\">空域</span><span class=\"info-value\" id=\"ptzDnrSpatial\">--</span></div>\r\n\n[1869 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783199136240}}
{"type":"message","id":"e73056fc","parentId":"9113fcc7","timestamp":"2026-07-04T21:06:55.168Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"需求1：变焦-和变焦+与PTZ方向控制的按钮矩阵居中对齐\n\n从代码看：\n- PTZ方向控制是 `.ptz-controls`，有 display:grid，auto,高度自动\n- 当前变焦按钮容器是 `width:154px; display:flex`\n\n问题是居中对齐。`.ptz-controls` 是grid布局，9个按钮3列布局。变焦按钮容器需要和这个grid居中对齐。\n\nstyled的header padding和collapsible spacing可能导致margin。`.ptz-controls` 的父容器是 `<div style=\"flex:0 0 auto;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:space-between\">`，变焦按钮也在同一个父容器内。\n\n问题是 `.ptz-controls` 已经居中对齐了（grid默认居中）。所以变焦按钮容器需要水平居中。可以给变焦按钮容器添加 `margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;` 或者给父容器添加某种布局。\n\n看当前结构：\n```\n<div style=\"flex:0 0 auto;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:space-between\">\n    <div class=\"ptz-controls\">...</div>\n    <div class=\"ptz-speed\">...速度...</div>\n    <div style=\"width:154px...\">变焦...</div>\n</div>\n```\n\n问题是整个父容器左对齐，所以变焦按钮也左对齐。\n需要给变焦按钮容器添加 `margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;` 使其居中。\n\n我需要将变焦按钮容器包裹在居中对齐的容器中。具体实现可以是给容器添加 Flexbox 布局，使用 `justify-content: center;` 来确保变焦按钮与 PTZ 导航按钮水平对齐。\n\n通过嵌套一个居中布局的 `div`，可以精确控制变焦按钮的位置，使其与 PTZ 方向控制区域完美匹配。这个方案既简单又精确，能完美解决对齐问题。\n\n简单直接的居中方法是使用 `margin: 0 auto`，或者选择更现代的 Flexbox 方法：给父容器添加 `display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start;`，然后在按钮容器上应用 `margin-left: auto`。这种方法不改变整个大块布局，而是精准定位目标元素。\n\n两种方案各有优势，需要根据具体使用场景选择最合适的实现方式。\n\n最小侵入的更改是直接在变焦按钮容器上添加 `margin-left: auto`。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"备份完成。现在逐条修改：\n\n### 修改1：变压按钮居中对齐"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7c090e6629ee499bb6099a32","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"                                        <div style=\"width:154px;display:flex;gap:4px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;margin-top:4px\">\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" style=\"flex:1;width:auto;height:24px;padding:1px;font-size:11px;line-height:1.2\" onmousedown=\"ptzZoom('out')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzZoom('out')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" onmouseleave=\"ptzStop()\" title=\"变焦-\">变焦-</button>\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" style=\"flex:1;width:auto;height:24px;padding:1px;font-size:11px;line-height:1.2\" onmousedown=\"ptzZoom('in')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzZoom('in')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" onmouseleave=\"ptzStop()\" title=\"变焦+\">变焦+</button>\n                                        </div>","oldText":"                                        <div style=\"width:154px;display:flex;gap:4px;margin-top:4px\">\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" style=\"flex:1;width:auto;height:24px;padding:1px;font-size:11px;line-height:1.2\" onmousedown=\"ptzZoom('out')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzZoom('out')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" onmouseleave=\"ptzStop()\" title=\"变焦-\">变焦-</button>\n                                            <button class=\"ptz-btn\" style=\"flex:1;width:auto;height:24px;padding:1px;font-size:11px;line-height:1.2\" onmousedown=\"ptzZoom('in')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzZoom('in')\" onmouseup=\"ptzStop()\" onmouseleave=\"ptzStop()\" title=\"变焦+\">变焦+</button>\n                                        </div>"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":99706,"output":999,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":100705,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783199136242,"responseId":"cht000d9811@dx19f2ef380fe29c2503"}}
