{"type":"message","id":"de8bf957","parentId":"2a723f12","timestamp":"2026-07-04T21:07:18.876Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在理解了需求：\n\n**需求2**：去掉\"分钟\"文字，将（定时文字+文本框+应用+停止）视作一个整体，总宽度=上方下拉菜单宽度\n\n**需求3**：应用按钮改为开关按钮（toggle switch），按下=打开（应用定时），关闭=不应用。定时为0时即使打开也不应用\n\n布局思路：\n- 框选按钮单独一行（或和定时整体在同一行）\n- 定时文字 + 文本框 + 开关 + 停止 = 一个整体，宽度=下拉菜单宽度\n\n重新设计布局：\n```\n[框选]\n[定时: [输入框] [开关] [停止]]\n```\n或者：\n```\n[框选] [定时: [输入框] [开关] [停止]]\n```\n\n老板说\"将（定时文字+文本框+应用+停止）视作一个整体\"，说明框选按钮不在这个整体内。所以框选按钮单独一行或单独位置。\n\n但老板又说\"总宽度等于上方下拉菜单的宽度\"，这个\"整体\"指的是定时+文本框+应用+停止。\n\n让我用flex布局，让框选按钮在上方，定时整体在下方，宽度=下拉菜单宽度：\n\n```html\n<div id=\"wbLocalControls\" style=\"display:none;margin-bottom:4px\">\n    <div style=\"display:flex;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:4px\">\n        <button id=\"btnWbRegionSelect\" class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onclick=\"toggleRegionMode('whitebalance')\">框选</button>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;width:100%\">\n        <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:12px;white-space:nowrap\">定时:</span>\n        <input type=\"text\" id=\"wbTimerInput\" value=\"0\" style=\"flex:1;padding:6px 8px;...\" oninput=\"...\">\n        <label class=\"switch\" style=\"flex-shrink:0\">\n            <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"wbTimerToggle\" onchange=\"toggleWbTimer()\">\n            <span class=\"slider\"></span>\n        </label>\n        <button id=\"btnWbLocalStop\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-sm\" onclick=\"stopAutoWhiteBalance()\" disabled style=\"opacity:0.5\">⏹️</button>\n    </div>\n</div>\n```\n\n使用已有的 `.switch` CSS 样式（在index.html中定义的开关按钮）。\n\n现在需要确认：\n1. 去掉\"分钟\"文字 ✅\n2. 定时+文本框+开关+停止总宽度=下拉菜单宽度 ✅（width:100%）\n3. 应用改为开关按钮 ✅\n4. 定时0时即使打开也不应用 ✅（JS中判断）\n\n需要修改：\n- console.html：HTML布局\n- console.html 或 index.html：JS函数 `toggleWbTimer()` 和 `toggleFocusTimer()`\n- 移除 `confirmWbTimer()` 和 `confirmFocusTimer()` 中的旧逻辑\n\n先看看现有的 `confirmWbTimer()` 和 `updateWbConfirmBtn()` 函数："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_12749107c0ba463ea24a4e34","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":40,"offset":1278,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":101368,"output":722,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102090,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783199225854,"responseId":"cht000d288c@dx19f2ef4da9b2872503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1a6ae2eb","parentId":"de8bf957","timestamp":"2026-07-04T21:07:18.935Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_12749107c0ba463ea24a4e34","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"}\r\n\r\n// v8.40: 白平衡定时器\r\nfunction updateWbConfirmBtn() {\r\n    var btn = document.getElementById('btnWbTimerConfirm');\r\n    var stopBtn = document.getElementById('btnWbLocalStop');\r\n    var input = document.getElementById('wbTimerInput');\r\n    var isSearching = stopBtn.disabled === false;\r\n    var minutes = parseInt(input.value) || 0;\r\n    \r\n    if (!btn) return;\r\n    // 定时值>0且搜索未运行时，按钮可用，否则灰色\r\n    if (minutes > 0 && !isSearching) {\r\n        btn.disabled = false;\r\n        btn.style.opacity = '1';\r\n    } else {\r\n        btn.disabled = true;\r\n        btn.style.opacity = '0.5';\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction updateFocusConfirmBtn() {\r\n    var btn = document.getElementById('btnFocusTimerConfirm');\r\n    var stopBtn = document.getElementById('btnFocusLocalStop');\r\n    var input = document.getElementById('focusTimerInput');\r\n    var isSearching = stopBtn.disabled === false;\r\n    var minutes = parseInt(input.value) || 0;\r\n    \r\n    if (!btn) return;\r\n    if (minutes > 0 && !isSearching) {\r\n        btn.disabled = false;\r\n        btn.style.opacity = '1';\r\n    } else {\r\n        btn.disabled = true;\r\n        btn.style.opacity = '0.5';\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n// v8.40: 白平衡定时器\r\nfunction confirmWbTimer() {\r\n\n[602 more lines in file. Use offset=1318 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783199238935}}
{"type":"message","id":"138b1936","parentId":"1a6ae2eb","timestamp":"2026-07-04T21:07:23.288Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b95df821b42548f683eba7d9","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":60,"offset":1318,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":102411,"output":48,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102459,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783199238937,"responseId":"cht000dbed1@dx19f2ef50dd229c2503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"210e3b9a","parentId":"138b1936","timestamp":"2026-07-04T21:07:23.321Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_b95df821b42548f683eba7d9","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    updateWbConfirmBtn();  // 确认按钮状态\r\n    var input = document.getElementById('wbTimerInput');\r\n    if (!input) return;\r\n    var minutes = parseInt(input.value) || 0;\r\n    if (minutes <= 0) {\r\n        stopWbTimer();\r\n        showToast('warning', '请输入大于0的分钟数');\r\n        return;\r\n    }\r\n    var region = localStorage.getItem('region_whitebalance');\r\n    if (!region) {\r\n        showToast('warning', '请先框选区域');\r\n        return;\r\n    }\r\n    stopWbTimer();\r\n    wbTimerSeconds = minutes * 60;\r\n    updateWbTimerDisplay();\r\n    wbTimerId = setInterval(function() {\r\n        wbTimerSeconds--;\r\n        updateWbTimerDisplay();\r\n        if (wbTimerSeconds <= 0) {\r\n            clearInterval(wbTimerId);\r\n            wbTimerId = null;\r\n            executeScheduledSearch('whitebalance');\r\n        }\r\n    }, 1000);\r\n    updateWbConfirmBtn();  // 重置按钮状态\r\n    showToast('success', '白平衡定时已启动: ' + minutes + '分钟');\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction stopWbTimer() {\r\n    if (wbTimerId) { clearInterval(wbTimerId); wbTimerId = null; }\r\n    wbTimerSeconds = 0;\r\n    var display = document.getElementById('wbTimerDisplay');\r\n    if (display) display.textContent = '';\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction updateWbTimerDisplay() {\r\n    var display = document.getElementById('wbTimerDisplay');\r\n    if (!display) return;\r\n    if (wbTimerSeconds <= 0) { display.textContent = ''; return; }\r\n    var m = Math.floor(wbTimerSeconds / 60);\r\n    var s = wbTimerSeconds % 60;\r\n    display.textContent = '(' + m + ':' + (s < 10 ? '0' : '') + s + ')';\r\n}\r\n\r\n// v8.40: 对焦定时器\r\nfunction confirmFocusTimer() {\r\n    updateFocusConfirmBtn();  // 确认按钮状态\r\n    var input = document.getElementById('focusTimerInput');\r\n    if (!input) return;\r\n    var minutes = parseInt(input.value) || 0;\r\n    if (minutes <= 0) {\r\n        stopFocusTimer();\r\n        showToast('warning', '请输入大于0的分钟数');\r\n        return;\r\n    }\r\n    var region = localStorage.getItem('region_focus');\r\n    if (!region) {\r\n        showToast('warning', '请先框选区域');\r\n\n[542 more lines in file. Use offset=1378 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783199243321}}
