{"type":"message","id":"4d77bc30","parentId":"da91e5f8","timestamp":"2026-07-04T21:07:49.173Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在理解了完整逻辑。修改计划：\n\n**HTML修改**：\n- 去掉\"分钟\"文字\n- 去掉 `❎` 按钮（应用按钮）\n- 添加开关按钮（使用 `.switch` CSS）\n- 布局：框选按钮单独一行，定时+文本框+开关+停止一行\n\n**JS修改**：\n- `confirmWbTimer()` → 改为 `toggleWbTimer()`\n- `confirmFocusTimer()` → 改为 `toggleFocusTimer()`\n- `updateWbConfirmBtn()` → 改为更新开关状态\n- `updateFocusConfirmBtn()` → 改为更新开关状态\n\n开始修改："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f3e74eabd8d94c38b1a79901","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"                                    <div id=\"wbLocalControls\" style=\"display:none;margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                        <div style=\"display:flex;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                            <button id=\"btnWbRegionSelect\" class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onclick=\"toggleRegionMode('whitebalance')\">框选</button>\n                                        </div>\n                                        <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%\">\n                                            <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:12px;white-space:nowrap\">定时</span>\n                                            <input type=\"text\" id=\"wbTimerInput\" value=\"0\" style=\"flex:1;padding:6px 8px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:6px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:12px\" oninput=\"this.value=this.value.replace(/[^0-9]/g,'');updateWbToggle()\">\n                                            <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:12px;white-space:nowrap\">分钟</span>\n                                            <label class=\"switch\" style=\"flex-shrink:0\" title=\"打开应用定时\">\n                                                <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"wbTimerToggle\" onchange=\"toggleWbTimer()\">\n                                                <span class=\"slider\"></span>\n                                            </label>\n                                            <button id=\"btnWbLocalStop\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-sm\" onclick=\"stopAutoWhiteBalance()\" disabled style=\"opacity:0.5\">⏹️</button>\n                                        </div>\n                                        <div id=\"wbTimerDisplay\" style=\"color:#f85149;font-size:11px;text-align:center;margin-top:2px\"></div>\n                                    </div>","oldText":"                                    <div id=\"wbLocalControls\" style=\"display:none;margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                        <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px\">\n                                            <div style=\"display:flex;gap:6px;justify-content:center;width:100%\">\n                                                <button id=\"btnWbRegionSelect\" class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onclick=\"toggleRegionMode('whitebalance')\">框选</button>\n                                                <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:3px;width:calc(100% - 80px);flex:1\">\n                                                    <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:12px\">定时:</span>\n                                                    <input type=\"text\" id=\"wbTimerInput\" value=\"0\" style=\"flex:1;padding:10px 12px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:6px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:13px\" oninput=\"this.value=this.value.replace(/[^0-9]/g,'');updateWbConfirmBtn()\">\n                                                    <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:12px\">分钟</span>\n                                                </div>\n                                                <button id=\"btnWbTimerConfirm\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" onclick=\"confirmWbTimer()\" disabled style=\"opacity:0.5\">❎</button>\n                                                <button id=\"btnWbLocalStop\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-sm\" onclick=\"stopAutoWhiteBalance()\" disabled style=\"opacity:0.5;min-width:72px\">⏹️</button>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>"},{"newText":"                                    <div id=\"focusLocalControls\" style=\"display:none;margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                        <div style=\"display:flex;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                            <button id=\"btnFocusRegionSelect\" class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onclick=\"toggleRegionMode('focus')\">框选</button>\n                                        </div>\n                                        <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%\">\n                                            <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:12px;white-space:nowrap\">定时</span>\n                                            <input type=\"text\" id=\"focusTimerInput\" value=\"0\" style=\"flex:1;padding:6px 8px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:6px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:12px\" oninput=\"this.value=this.value.replace(/[^0-9]/g,'');updateFocusToggle()\">\n                                            <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:12px;white-space:nowrap\">分钟</span>\n                                            <label class=\"switch\" style=\"flex-shrink:0\" title=\"打开应用定时\">\n                                                <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"focusTimerToggle\" onchange=\"toggleFocusTimer()\">\n                                                <span class=\"slider\"></span>\n                                            </label>\n                                            <button id=\"btnFocusLocalStop\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-sm\" onclick=\"stopAutoFocus()\" disabled style=\"opacity:0.5\">⏹️</button>\n                                        </div>\n                                        <div id=\"focusTimerDisplay\" style=\"color:#f85149;font-size:11px;text-align:center;margin-top:2px\"></div>\n                                    </div>","oldText":"                                    <div id=\"focusLocalControls\" style=\"display:none;margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                        <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px\">\n                                            <div style=\"display:flex;gap:6px;justify-content:center;width:100%\">\n                                                <button id=\"btnFocusRegionSelect\" class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onclick=\"toggleRegionMode('focus')\">框选</button>\n                                                <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:3px;width:calc(100% - 80px);flex:1\">\n                                                    <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:12px\">定时:</span>\n                                                    <input type=\"text\" id=\"focusTimerInput\" value=\"0\" style=\"flex:1;padding:10px 12px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:6px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:13px\" oninput=\"this.value=this.value.replace(/[^0-9]/g,'');updateFocusConfirmBtn()\">\n                                                    <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:12px\">分钟</span>\n                                                </div>\n                                                <button id=\"btnFocusTimerConfirm\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" onclick=\"confirmFocusTimer()\" disabled style=\"opacity:0.5\">❎</button>\n                                                <button id=\"btnFocusLocalStop\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-sm\" onclick=\"stopAutoFocus()\" disabled style=\"opacity:0.5;min-width:72px\">⏹️</button>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"anthropi