{"type":"custom","customType":"openclaw:prompt-error","data":{"timestamp":1783199339436,"runId":"6d4c4786-0ee3-4cc3-bf7b-20c1d8a5fad1","sessionId":"6d5d7d18-d08b-473a-a3fa-de91625dc012","provider":"hp","model":"glm-5.2","api":"anthropic-messages","error":"Reply operation aborted by user | Reply operation aborted by user"},"id":"8c330e2b","parentId":"b764c025","timestamp":"2026-07-04T21:08:59.436Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"d4833926","parentId":"8c330e2b","timestamp":"2026-07-04T21:08:59.443Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，HTML部分已经修改完成。现在需要修改JS函数。\n\n当前需要修改的JS函数：\n1. `updateWbConfirmBtn()` → 改为 `updateWbToggle()` - 根据定时值更新开关状态\n2. `updateFocusConfirmBtn()` → 改为 `updateFocusToggle()` - 根据定时值更新开关状态\n3. `confirmWbTimer()` → 移除，不再需要\n4. `confirmFocusTimer()` → 移除，不再需要\n\n新增的JS函数：\n1. `toggleWbTimer()` - 切换白平衡定时开关\n2. `toggleFocusTimer()` - 切换对焦定时开关\n\n根据需求：定时值>0且开关打开时才应用定时。定时值=0时即使开关打开也不应用。\n\n还需要为每个搜索器添加 `_isTimerEnabled` 属性来跟踪定时开关状态。\n\n现在修改JS函数。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"现在修改JS函数："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ba8d8710709540f6b85adb9f","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"// v8.41: 定时开关 - 根据定时值更新开关状态\nfunction updateWbToggle() {\n    var checkbox = document.getElementById('wbTimerToggle');\n    var input = document.getElementById('wbTimerInput');\n    if (!checkbox || !input) return;\n    var minutes = parseInt(input.value) || 0;\n    // 定时值=0时，即使开关打开也不应用（需要手动输入并打开开关时才应用）\n    if (minutes > 0 && checkbox.checked) {\n        checkbox.checked = true;\n    } else {\n        // 定时值=0或开关关闭，禁用定时\n        checkbox.checked = false;\n    }\n}\n\nfunction updateFocusToggle() {\n    var checkbox = document.getElementById('focusTimerToggle');\n    var input = document.getElementById('focusTimerInput');\n    if (!checkbox || !input) return;\n    var minutes = parseInt(input.value) || 0;\n    if (minutes > 0 && checkbox.checked) {\n        checkbox.checked = true;\n    } else {\n        checkbox.checked = false;\n    }\n}\n\n// v8.41: 切换白平衡定时\nfunction toggleWbTimer() {\n    updateWbToggle();  // 确保开关状态正确\n    var checkbox = document.getElementById('wbTimerToggle');\n    var input = document.getElementById('wbTimerInput');\n    var stopBtn = document.getElementById('btnWbLocalStop');\n    if (!checkbox || !input || !stopBtn) return;\n    var minutes = parseInt(input.value) || 0;\n    var isSearching = stopBtn.disabled === false;\n    \n    if (checkbox.checked && minutes > 0 && !isSearching) {\n        // 开关打开，开始定时\n        runWbTimer();\n        showToast('success', '白平衡定时已启动: ' + minutes + '分钟');\n    } else {\n        // 开关关闭，停止定时\n        stopWbTimer();\n        if (isSearching) {\n            showToast('info', '停止定时，恢复手动使用');\n        } else if (minutes > 0) {\n            showToast('info', '定时已关闭');\n        }\n    }\n}\n\n// v8.41: 切换对焦定时\nfunction toggleFocusTimer() {\n    updateFocusToggle();\n    var checkbox = document.getElementById('focusTimerToggle');\n    var input = document.getElementById('focusTimerInput');\n    var stopBtn = document.getElementById('btnFocusLocalStop');\n    if (!checkbox || !input || !stopBtn) return;\n    var minutes = parseInt(input.value) || 0;\n    var isSearching = stopBtn.disabled === false;\n    \n    if (checkbox.checked && minutes > 0 && !isSearching) {\n        runFocusTimer();\n        showToast('success', '对焦定时已启动: ' + minutes + '分钟');\n    } else {\n        stopFocusTimer();\n        if (isSearching) {\n            showToast('info', '停止定时，恢复手动使用');\n        } else if (minutes > 0) {\n            showToast('info', '定时已关闭');\n        }\n    }\n}\n\n// v8.41: 运行白平衡定时器\nfunction runWbTimer() {\n    var input = document.getElementById('wbTimerInput');\n    if (!input) return;\n    var minutes = parseInt(input.value) || 0;\n    if (minutes <= 0) {\n        stopWbTimer();\n        showToast('warning', '请输入大于0的分钟数');\n        return;\n    }\n    var region = localStorage.getItem('region_whitebalance');\n    if (!region) {\n        showToast('warning', '请先框选区域');\n        return;\n    }\n    stopWbTimer();\n    wbTimerSeconds = minutes * 60;\n    updateWbTimerDisplay();\n    wbTimerId = setInterval(function() {\n        wbTimerSeconds--;\n        updateWbTimerDisplay();\n        if (wbTimerSeconds <= 0) {\n            clearInterval(wbTimerId);\n            wbTimerId = null;\n            executeScheduledSearch('whitebalance');\n        }\n    }, 1000);\n}\n\nfunction stopWbTimer() {\n    if (wbTimerId) { clearInterval(wbTimerId); wbTimerId = null; }\n    wbTimerSeconds = 0;\n    var display = document.getElementById('wbTimerDisplay');\n    if (display) display.textContent = '';\n}\n\nfunction updateWbTimerDisplay() {\n    var display = document.getElementById('wbTimerDisplay');\n    if (!display) return;\n    if (wbTimerSeconds <= 0) { display.textContent = ''; return; }\n    var m = Math.floor(wbTimerSeconds / 60);\n    var s = wbTimerSeconds % 60;\n    display.textContent = '(' + m + ':' + (s < 10 ? '0' : '') + s + ')';\n}\n\n// v8.41: 运行对焦定时器\nfunction runFocusTimer() {\n    var input = document.getElementById('focusTimerInput');\n    if (!input) return;\n    var minutes = parseInt(input.value) || 0;\n    if (minutes <= 0) {\n        stopFocusTimer();\n        showToast('warning', '请输入大于0的分钟数');\n        return;\n    }\n    var region = localStorage.getItem('region_focus');\n    if (!region) {\n        showToast('warning', '请先框选区域');\n        return;\n    }\n    stopFocusTimer();\n    focusTimerSeconds = minutes * 60;\n    updateFocusTimerDisplay();\n    focusTimerId = setInterval(function() {\n        focusTimerSeconds--;\n        updateFocusTimerDisplay();\n        if (focusTimerSeconds <= 0) {\n            clearInterval(focusTimerId);\n            focusTimerId = null;\n            executeScheduledSearch('focus');\n        }\n    }, 1000);\n}\n\nfunction stopFocusTimer() {\n    if (focusTimerId) { clearInterval(focusTimerId); focusTimerId = null; }\n    focusTimerSeconds = 0;\n    var display = document.getElementById('focusTimerDisplay');\n    if (display) display.textContent = '';\n}\n\nfunction updateFocusTimerDisplay() {\n    var display = document.getElementById('focusTimerDisplay');\n    if (!display) return;\n    if (focusTimerSeconds <= 0) { display.textContent = ''; return; }\n    var m = Math.floor(focusTimerSeconds / 60);\n    var s = focusTimerSeconds % 60;\n    display.textContent = '(' + m + ':' + (s < 10 ? '0' : '') + s + ')';\n}","oldText":"// v8.40: 白平衡定时器\nfunction updateWbConfirmBtn() {\n    var btn = document.getElementById('btnWbTimerConfirm');\n    var stopBtn = document.getElementById('btnWbLocalStop');\n    var input = document.getElementById('wbTimerInput');\n    var isSearchTreeBtnDisabled = stopBtn.disabled === false;\n    var minutes = parseInt(input.value) || 0;\n    \n    if (!btn) return;\n    if (minutes > 0 && !isSearchTreeBtnDisabled) {\n        btn.disabled = false;\n        btn.style.opacity = '1';\n    } else {\n        btn.disabled = true;\n        btn.style.opacity = '0.5';\n"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"aborted","timestamp":1783199269224,"responseId":"cht000d50cb@dx19f2ef5a3d229bb503","errorMessage":"This operation was aborted"}}
{"type":"message","id":"39ea3c14","parentId":"d4833926","timestamp":"2026-07-04T21:10:45.550Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Note: The previous agent run was aborted by the user. Resume carefully or ask for clarification.\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"46005\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-07-05 05:10 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n布局：框选按钮单独一行，定时+文本框+开关+停止一行\n以上设计是错误的，以上这些都是同一行\n去掉“定时”字样，文本框在没有输入文字前，里面的默认文字是“定时”，文本框必须要求输入数字，文本框后方加入\"min\"的字样。重新设计，重新修改"}],"timestamp":1783199445542}}
{"type":"message","id":"85faf8d2","parentId":"39ea3c14","timestamp":"2026-07-04T21:12:19.538Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"老板指出我理解错了布局。三个需求：\n1. 所有元素都在同一行：框选按钮、定时文字+文本框、开关、停止按钮\n2. 去掉\"定时\"字样，文本框默认文字是\"定时\"，输入后变成数字，框框后方加入\"min\"字样\n3. 应用按钮改为开关按钮\n\n重新设计：\n- 框选按钮 + 定时 + 文本框 + min + 开关 + 停止 = 一行\n\n关键点：\n- 文本框默认文字是\"定时\"，但只能输入数字\n- 输入后显示数字 + \"min\"\n- 如果时间是0，开关是灰色的（disabled），即使打开开关也不应用\n\n让我重新修改HTML和JS代码。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7d64266628664751a9bbe692","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"                                    <div id=\"wbLocalControls\" style=\"display:none;margin-bottom:4px\">\n                                        <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%\">\n                                            <button id=\"btnWbRegionSelect\" class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" onclick=\"toggleRegionMode('whitebalance')\">框选</button>\n                                            <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:12px;white-space:nowrap\">定时</span>\n                                            <input type=\"text\" id=\"wbTimerInput\" value=\"\" placeholder=\"定时\" style=\"flex:1;max-width:60px;padding:6px 8px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:6px;color:#e0e6f0;font-size:12px\" oninput=\"updateWbTimerInput(this)\">\n                                            <span style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:12px;white-space:nowrap\">min</span>\n                                            <label class=\"switch\" style=\"flex-shrink:0\" title=\"打开应用定时\">\n                                                <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"wbTimerToggle\" onchange=\"toggleWbTimer()\">\n                                                <span class=\"slider\"></span>\n                                            </label>\n                                            <button id=\"btnWbLocalStop\" class=\"btn btn-danger btn-sm\" onclick=\"stopAutoWhiteBal