{"type":"message","id":"2902e7f8","parentId":"6e41788e","timestamp":"2026-07-04T21:14:20.128Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"当前的 confirmWbTimer 和 confirmFocusTimer 函数负责启动定时器。我需要修改开关按钮的逻辑：\n1. 去掉 confirmWbTimer 和 confirmFocusTimer 这两个函数\n2. 添加一个新的 toggleWbTimer 和 toggleFocusTimer 函数\n3. toggleWbTimer 的逻辑：\n   - 检查输入框是否有值，没有值则是0\n   - 如果值为0，开关是灰色的，点击无效\n   - 如果值>0，根据开关状态：\n     - 打开开关：启动定时器\n     - 关闭开关：停止定时器\n\n文本框输入逻辑 updateWbTimerInput：\n- 只允许输入数字\n- 入空白时显示 placeholder \"定时\"\n- 输入后显示数字\n\n需要删除旧的 updateWbConfirmBtn 和 updateFocusConfirmBtn（因为不再需要按钮，只用开关）。\n\n现在需要：\n1. 删除 confirmWbTimer、confirmFocusTimer、updateWbConfirmBtn、updateFocusConfirmBtn\n2. 添加 updateWbTimerInput、updateFocusTimerInput\n3. 添加 toggleWbTimer、toggleFocusTimer\n\n让我先找到这些函数的具体位置和内容。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"现在需要修改JS函数。先删除旧的按钮相关函数，添加新的开关逻辑。让我先找到这些函数的完整内容："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c0817f6603df403eaa11c770","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":20,"offset":1278,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":110705,"output":323,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111028,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783199631552,"responseId":"cht000dc2fa@dx19f2efb15ee2872503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"98c3689e","parentId":"2902e7f8","timestamp":"2026-07-04T21:14:20.190Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_c0817f6603df403eaa11c770","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"}\r\n\r\n// v8.40: 白平衡定时器\r\nfunction updateWbConfirmBtn() {\r\n    var btn = document.getElementById('btnWbTimerConfirm');\r\n    var stopBtn = document.getElementById('btnWbLocalStop');\r\n    var input = document.getElementById('wbTimerInput');\r\n    var isSearching = stopBtn.disabled === false;\r\n    var minutes = parseInt(input.value) || 0;\r\n    \r\n    if (!btn) return;\r\n    // 定时值>0且搜索未运行时，按钮可用，否则灰色\r\n    if (minutes > 0 && !isSearching) {\r\n        btn.disabled = false;\r\n        btn.style.opacity = '1';\r\n    } else {\r\n        btn.disabled = true;\r\n        btn.style.opacity = '0.5';\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\n[622 more lines in file. Use offset=1298 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783199660190}}
{"type":"message","id":"8e078c81","parentId":"98c3689e","timestamp":"2026-07-04T21:14:23.409Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f5a9c4049cbc4bccad5ef429","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":100,"offset":1278,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":110953,"output":48,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111001,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783199660192,"responseId":"cht000de54c@dx19f2efb7b6929bb503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f518f828","parentId":"8e078c81","timestamp":"2026-07-04T21:14:23.440Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f5a9c4049cbc4bccad5ef429","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"}\r\n\r\n// v8.40: 白平衡定时器\r\nfunction updateWbConfirmBtn() {\r\n    var btn = document.getElementById('btnWbTimerConfirm');\r\n    var stopBtn = document.getElementById('btnWbLocalStop');\r\n    var input = document.getElementById('wbTimerInput');\r\n    var isSearching = stopBtn.disabled === false;\r\n    var minutes = parseInt(input.value) || 0;\r\n    \r\n    if (!btn) return;\r\n    // 定时值>0且搜索未运行时，按钮可用，否则灰色\r\n    if (minutes > 0 && !isSearching) {\r\n        btn.disabled = false;\r\n        btn.style.opacity = '1';\r\n    } else {\r\n        btn.disabled = true;\r\n        btn.style.opacity = '0.5';\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction updateFocusConfirmBtn() {\r\n    var btn = document.getElementById('btnFocusTimerConfirm');\r\n    var stopBtn = document.getElementById('btnFocusLocalStop');\r\n    var input = document.getElementById('focusTimerInput');\r\n    var isSearching = stopBtn.disabled === false;\r\n    var minutes = parseInt(input.value) || 0;\r\n    \r\n    if (!btn) return;\r\n    if (minutes > 0 && !isSearching) {\r\n        btn.disabled = false;\r\n        btn.style.opacity = '1';\r\n    } else {\r\n        btn.disabled = true;\r\n        btn.style.opacity = '0.5';\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n// v8.40: 白平衡定时器\r\nfunction confirmWbTimer() {\r\n    updateWbConfirmBtn();  // 确认按钮状态\r\n    var input = document.getElementById('wbTimerInput');\r\n    if (!input) return;\r\n    var minutes = parseInt(input.value) || 0;\r\n    if (minutes <= 0) {\r\n        stopWbTimer();\r\n        showToast('warning', '请输入大于0的分钟数');\r\n        return;\r\n    }\r\n    var region = localStorage.getItem('region_whitebalance');\r\n    if (!region) {\r\n        showToast('warning', '请先框选区域');\r\n        return;\r\n    }\r\n    stopWbTimer();\r\n    wbTimerSeconds = minutes * 60;\r\n    updateWbTimerDisplay();\r\n    wbTimerId = setInterval(function() {\r\n        wbTimerSeconds--;\r\n        updateWbTimerDisplay();\r\n        if (wbTimerSeconds <= 0) {\r\n            clearInterval(wbTimerId);\r\n            wbTimerId = null;\r\n            executeScheduledSearch('whitebalance');\r\n        }\r\n    }, 1000);\r\n    updateWbConfirmBtn();  // 重置按钮状态\r\n    showToast('success', '白平衡定时已启动: ' + minutes + '分钟');\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction stopWbTimer() {\r\n    if (wbTimerId) { clearInterval(wbTimerId); wbTimerId = null; }\r\n    wbTimerSeconds = 0;\r\n    var display = document.getElementById('wbTimerDisplay');\r\n    if (display) display.textContent = '';\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction updateWbTimerDisplay() {\r\n    var display = document.getElementById('wbTimerDisplay');\r\n    if (!display) return;\r\n    if (wbTimerSeconds <= 0) { display.textContent = ''; return; }\r\n    var m = Math.floor(wbTimerSeconds / 60);\r\n    var s = wbTimerSeconds % 60;\r\n    display.textContent = '(' + m + ':' + (s < 10 ? '0' : '') + s + ')';\r\n}\r\n\r\n// v8.40: 对焦定时器\r\nfunction confirmFocusTimer() {\r\n    updateFocusConfirmBtn();  // 确认按钮状态\r\n    var input = document.getElementById('focusTimerInput');\r\n    if (!input) return;\r\n    var minutes = parseInt(input.value) || 0;\r\n    if (minutes <= 0) {\r\n        stopFocusTimer();\r\n        showToast('warning', '请输入大于0的分钟数');\r\n        return;\r\n    }\r\n    var region = localStorage.getItem('region_focus');\r\n    if (!region) {\r\n        showToast('warning', '请先框选区域');\r\n\n[542 more lines in file. Use offset=1378 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783199663440}}
